quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,"Qaaf (Mashoko aya ndemamwe ezvishamiso zviri muQur’aan, uye hapana anoziva zvaanoreva kunze kwaAllah). (Ndinopika) neQur’aan dzvene"
  50,2,"Vanoshamiswa kuti kwakauya muyambiri kwavari (Muhammad (SAW)) kubva mukati mavo. Naizvozvo avo vasingatendi vanoti: “Ichi ndicho chishamiso!”"
  50,3,“Kana tichinge tafa tave huruva (tichave tinomutswa here)? Ndiko kudzoka kuri kure.”
  50,4,"Tinoziva izvo zvinotorwa nevhu kubva kwavari (vafi), uye tine gwaro rakachengetedzwa (gwaro remirairo)"
  50,5,"Asi vakaramba chokwadi (Qur’aan) apo chakange chauya kwavari, nokudaro vakave vanokanganisika (havakwanisi kuona chakaipa nechakanaka)"
  50,6,"Havana here kutarisa matenga ari pamusoro pavo, magadziriro atakaaiita uye kushongedza kwatakaaiita, uye haana kutsemuka"
  50,7,"Uye pasi rino takariparadzira, uye tikadzika mariri makomo akamira zvakasimba, uye tikaburitsa mariri zvirimwa zvose zvakanaka"
  50,8,Simba rekuona uye yeuchidzo kune muranda wose uyo anocheuka kuna Allah achikumbira ruregerero
  50,9,"Uye tinodzikisa mvura yakakomborerwa kubva kudenga, zvadaro toburitsa mapindu uye zvirimwa zvikohwewa"
  50,10,"Uye miti yemadheti yakareba, ine bumburudzi dzakarongedzwa, dzimwe pamusoro pedzimwe"
  50,11,Raramo yevaranda (vaAllah). Uye tinopa raramo nayo kunyika yakanga yaparara. Kudaro kuchave kumutswa (kuchaiitwa vakafa)
  50,12,"Vaivepo ivo vasati vavepo (vasingatendi vekuMakkah) vakaramba, vanhu vaNowa, uye vagari vemuRassi, uye maThamood"
  50,13,"Uye Aad, uye Farawo, uye madzikoma aLoti"
  50,14,"Uye vagari vemusango, uye vanhu vekuTubba’. Vose vakaramba vatumwa (vavo), nokudaro vakapiwa chirango changu"
  50,15,Takaneta here nezvisikwa zvokutanga? Asi vari mukusagutsikana maererano nezvisikwa zvitsva (Kumutswa kubva kuvafi)
  50,16,"Uye zvirokwazvo takasika munhu, uye tinoziva zvaanozevezera. Uye tiri padyo naye kukunda tsinga dzake dzepahuro (neruzivo rwedu)"
  50,17,"(Rangarirai) kuti avo vagashiri vaviri (ngirozi dzinonyora) vanogashira (munhu wese), imwe yakagara kurudyi imwe kuruboshwe (dzichinyora mabasa ese emunhu)"
  50,18,Hapana izwi raanotaura asi kuti pane mutariri akamirira (kunyora pasi)
  50,19,"Uye kudhaka kwerufu kuchauya muchokwadi. Zvichanzi: “Izvi ndizvo zvawaidzivirira!”"
  50,20,"Uye hwamanda icharidzwa, ndiro richava zuva rakayambirwa (zuva rekumutswa)"
  50,21,Uye munhu wose achauya mberi pamwechete (nengirozi) ichimutinha uye (nengirozi) kuti igopa uchapupu
  50,22,"(Zvichanzi kumutadzi): “Zvirokwazvo, waive usingazvizivi izvi. Zvino takubvisa zvakanga zvakakupfukidza, uye meso ako ajeka nhasi!”"
  50,23,"Uye shamwari yake yepedyo (ngirozi) ichati: “Izvi ndizvo zvatakanyora zvatinazvo!”"
  50,24,"(Allah vachati kune ngirozi): “Imi muri vaviri, kandai mumoto, wese aive nemukonyo asingatendi (muhumwechete waAllah nemuvatumwa vavo).”"
  50,25,"“Muwomesi wezvakanaka, mupfurikidzi, uyo asingagutsikani.”"
  50,26,“Aisanganisa vamwe vanamwari naAllah. Nokudaro mukandei muri vaviri mumutongo wakaomarara.”
  50,27,"Wepedyo pake (Satani) achati: “Tenzi vedu! Handina kumumanikidza kuti atadze, asi ndiye akanga akarasika zvakanyanya.”"
  50,28,"Allah vachati: “Musava munopikisana pamberi pangu, ndakatokutumidzirai yambiro kare.”"
  50,29,“Mashoko abva kwandiri haashanduki uye handidzvanyiriri varanda.”
  50,30,"Iro zuva ratichati kuGehena: “Wazara here?” Richati: “Pane vamwe here (vari kuuya)?”"
  50,31,Uye Paradhiso richaunzwa padyo nevatendi vanotya Allah kwete kure navo
  50,32,"(Zvichanzi): “Izvi ndizvo zvamakanga mavimbiswa, kune avo vanokumbira ruregerero kuna Allah, uye vanochengetedza chitsidzo chavo kuna Allah (kuti vachatevera chitendero chaAllah, Islaam).”"
  50,33,“Uyo aitya avo vane tsitsi dzakawanda (Allah) mune izvo zvisingaoneki uye ouya nemoyo wekukumbira ruregerero (kubva kuzvitadzo zvese).”
  50,34,“Pinda mariri nerunyararo uye chengetedzo. Iri ndiro zuva rehupenyu husina magumo!”
  50,35,"Imomo vachawana zvido zvemoyo yavo uye tine zvizhinji (kwavari, sekuona Allah)"
  50,36,Uye madzinza mangani atakaparadza mushure mavo ange anemasimba kuvakunda. Uye (apo mutongo wedu wakauya) vakamhanya vachitsvaga rubatsiro kune dzimwe nzvimbo! Vakawana nzvimbo yekuhwanda here (kubva mukuparadzwa)
  50,37,"Zvirokwazvo, mune izvozvo mune yambiro kune uyo ane moyo kana anopa nzeve dzake achiteerera"
  50,38,"Uye zvirokwazvo takasika matenga nenyika uye zviri pakati pawo nemazuva matanhatu, uye hatina kuneta nazvo"
  50,39,"Nokudaro tsungirira (Muhammad (SAW)) mune zvose zvavanotaura, uye rumbidza kurumbidzwa kwaTenzi vako zuva risati rabuda uye risati ranyura (nekuita minamato yeFajr, Dhuhr ne Asr)"
  50,40,"Uye muchidimbu cheusiku varumbidze (nekuita minamato yeMaghrib neIsha), uyezve mushure meminamato (nekuita minamato isingamanikidzirwi maSunnah nekurumbidza uchiti Subhaanallaah, Alhamdulillaah, Allaahu Akbar)"
  50,41,Uye teererai iro zuva apo mudaidzi achadaidzira munzvimbo iri padyo
  50,42,Iro zuva ravachanzwa kusheedzera kwechokwadi. Iri ndiro richava zuva rekubuda (kubva kumakuva)
  50,43,"Zvirokwazvo, tisu tinopa upenyu uye tinokonzera rufu, uye kwatiri ndiko kwamuchadzokera"
  50,44,"Pazuva iro nyika ichatsemuka, vobuda vachimhanya. Uku ndiko kuchava kuunganidza kwatiri kuri nyore"
  50,45,"Tinoziva zvakanyanya izvo zvavanotaura. Uye (iwe Muhammad (SAW)) hausi\tiwe unovamanikidza (kutenda). Asi yambira neQur’aan uyo anotya tyisidziro yangu (yemurango)"
  51,1,(Ndinopika) nemhepo inopfumbura huruva
  51,2,Uye (nemakore) anotakura mvura inorema
  51,3,Uye neizvo zvinofamba pamusoro pemvura (ngarava) zviri nyore uye zvakadzikama
  51,4,"Uye neizvo (ngirozi) zvinopa (chikafu, mvura, nemamwe makomborero) nokuda kwaAllah"
  51,5,"Zvirokwazvo, izvo zvamunovimbiswa (kumutswa kubva kuvafi) ichokwadi"
  51,6,Uye zvirokwazvo kupa mubairo kuchaiitika
  51,7,Ndinopika nedenga iro rakazara nenzira
  51,8,"Zvirokwazvo, mune maonero akasiyana (maererano naMuhammad (SAW) neQur’aan"
  51,9,Akapfuratira kubva kwariri (Qur’aan) ndeuyo anopfuratidzwa (neurongwa waAllah)
  51,10,Kushorwa ngakuve kune vanonyepa
  51,11,Avo vasina hanya nezvezuva rokutongwa
  51,12,"Vanobvunza: “Zuva rekutongwa ririko rinhi?”"
  51,13,(Richava) zuva ravacharangwa nemoto
  51,14,“Ravirai murango wenyu (kutswa nemoto)! Izvi ndizvo zvamaikumbira kuti zvikurumidze kuitwa!”
  51,15,"Zvirokwazvo, vanotya (Allah) vachange vari mumapindu uye nezvitubu (muParadhiso)"
  51,16,"Vachinakirwa nezvinhu zvavanenge vapiwa naTenzi vavo. Zvirokwazvo, vakanga vari vaiti vemabasa akanaka mushure"
  51,17,Vairara nguva shoma usiku (vachinamata)
  51,18,Uye vaikumbira ruregerero mangwanani kusati kwachena
  51,19,Uye paupfumi hwavo pakanga paine kodzero dzeavo vanokumbira neavo vanotambura asi vasingakumbiri
  51,20,Uye panyika kune zviratidzo kune avo vanotenda uye vari pachokwadi
  51,21,Uye mukati menyu. Hamuoni here
  51,22,"Uye kumatenga ndiko kune raramo yenyu, uye izvo zvamakavimbiswa"
  51,23,"Naizvozvo ndinopika naTenzi vematenga nenyika, zvirokwazvo ichokwadi (zvamakavimbiswa) sokunge huchokwadi wekuti munotaura"
  51,24,Ko haina here kusvika kwamuri nyaya yevaenzi vaAbrahamu vanoremekedzeka (Gabriel nedzimwe ngirozi mbiri)
  51,25,"Apo vakapinda kwaari vakati: “Rugare!” Iye akati: “Rugare!” Akati: “Muri vanhu vandisingazivi.”"
  51,26,"Naizvozvo akaenda kumhuri yake, uye ndokubva auya nekamhuru kakakangiwa (hupfumi waAbrahamu wakawanda wange uri wemombe)"
  51,27,"Akabva akaisa pamberi pavo (achiti): “Hamungadyi here?”"
  51,28,"Naizvozvo akataridza kuvatya (apo pavasina kudya). Vakati: “Usatya.” Ndokubva vamupa mashoko akanaka emwanakomana ane ruzivo (rweIslaam)"
  51,29,"Zvino mukadzi wake akauya padyo neizwi riri pamusoro, akazvirova kumeso kwake ndokubva ati: “Mukadzi mukuru asingabereki!”"
  51,30,"Ivo ndokuti: “Ndizvo zvataurwa naTenzi vako. Zvirokwazvo, vane hungwaru hwese, vanoziva zvese.”"
  51,31,"(Abrahamu) akati: “Saka mavingei nhai vatumwa?”"
  51,32,"Vakati: “Zvirokwazvo, tiri vatumwa kune avo vanhu vanotadza.”"
  51,33,“Kuti titumire kwavari matombo evhu rakatsva.”
  51,34,“Akatarwa naTenzi vako kune avo vatadzi.”
  51,35,Naizvozvo takaburitsa vatendi mairi
  51,36,Nokudaro hatina kuwana imba yemutendi (Muslim) imomo kunze kweimwechete (Loti nevanasikana vake vaviri)
  51,37,Uye takasiya chiratidzo imomo (Dead Sea ku Palestine) kune avo vanotya murango unorwadza
  51,38,"Uye muna Musa zvakare (mune chiratidzo), apo takamutuma kuna Farawo nehumboo uri pachena"
  51,39,"Asi (Farawo) pamwe nevatsigiri vake vakafuratira, uye akati: “Munhu anoita masaramusi kana kuti anopenga.”"
  51,40,"Naizvozvo takamutora iye nemauto ake, uye tikavanyudza mugungwa, nokuda kwekuti ndiye akanga aine mhosva"
  51,41,"Uye kumaAad (kune chiratidzo), apo takatumira kwavari mhepo inoparadza"
  51,42,"Haina kusiya kana chii zvacho chayakasvikira, asi kuti yakasiya yaita marara"
  51,43,"Uye kuma Thamood (kune chiratidzo), apo zvakanzi kwavari: “Nakirwai kwekanguvana!”"
  51,44,"Asi havana kuteerera mirairo yaTenzi vavo vakazvikudza, ndokubva varohwa nemheni apo vakatarisa"
  51,45,"Zvino vakanga vasingachakwanisi kusimuka, kana kukwanisa kuzvibetsera"
  51,46,"Uye vanhu vaNowa mushure. Zvirokwazvo, vaive vanhu vasinganzwisisi (vasingateereri Allah)"
  51,47,Uye matenga takaagadzira nesimba. Uye zvirokwazvo tinokwanisa kuwawedzera
  51,48,"Uye nyika takaiparadzira, (uye) tiri nyanzvi dzakadii pakuparadzira zvakanaka"
  51,49,Uye pazvinhu zvose takasika zviviri zviviri kuitira kuti mugorangarira (makomborero aAllah)
  51,50,"Naizvozvo chimhanyirai kuna Allah (Islaam). Zvirokwazvo, ini (Muhammad (SAW)) ndiri muyambiri ari pachena kwamuri kubva kwavari"
  51,51,"Uye musatora chimwe chinamatwa pamwechete naAllah. Zvirokwazvo, ini (Muhammad (SAW)) ndiri muyambiri ari pachena kwamuri kubva kwavari"
  51,52,"Saizvozvo, hakuna mutumwa akauya kune avo mushure mavo kunze kwekuti vakati: “In’anga kana kuti anopenga!”"
  51,53,(Vanhu vekare) Vakavasiira here mashoko aya (maQuraish)? Kana kuti ivo vanhu vanotsaudzira mirairo
  51,54,"Zvino enda (Muhammad (SAW)) kure navo (vasingatendi), naizvozvo iwe hauna mhaka (nokuti wasvitsa shoko raAllah)"
  51,55,"Uye chiyeuchidza (Muhammad (SAW)), nokuti zvirokwazvo yeuchidzo inobetsera vanotenda"
  51,56,Uye handina (ini Allah) kusika maJinn nevanhu asi kuti vandinamate
  51,57,"Handidi raramo kubva kwavari, uye handidi kana kuti vandipe chikafu"
  51,58,"Zvirokwazvo, Allah ndivo muridzi wechengeto, muridzi wemasimba, vakasimba chaizvo"
  51,59,"Naizvozvo, zvirokwazvo kune avo vatadzi pane chidimbu chemurango wakafanana newevamwe vavo (mushure). Zvino ngavarege kundimhanyira mberi"
  51,60,"Naizvozvo, matambudziko kune avo vasingatendi (muhumwechete hwaAllah) kubva pazuva ravo ravakavimbiswa"
  52,1,(Ndinopika) negomo
  52,2,Uye neBhuku rakanyorwa
  52,3,Mugwaro risina kubhedhenurwa
  52,4,Uye neAl-Baitul Ma’moor (imba iri pamusoro pematenga iri pamusoro pe Ka’bah kuMakkah inogaro shanyirwa nengirozi)
  52,5,Uye nedenga rakasimudzwa mudenga
  52,6,Uye negungwa rakazadzwa (kana kuti richava moto wakatungidzwa pazuva rekutongwa)
  52,7,"Zvirokwazvo, kuranga kwaTenzi vako kuchaitika"
  52,8,Hakuna mumwe anokwanisa kukudzivirira (kuranga kwaAllah)
  52,9,Nezuva iro denga richadengeneka kudengeneka kunotyisa
  52,10,"Uye makomo achafamba, kufamba kunotyisa"
  52,11,Naizvozvo matambudziko kune avo vanoramba
  52,12,Avo vanotamba nekunyepa
  52,13,"Zuva ravachasundirwa kumoto zvokumanikidzwa, uye kumanikidzwa kunovhundutsa"
  52,14,Uyu ndiwo moto wamaimboramba
  52,15,Mapipi here ahwa kana kuti hamuoni
  52,16,"Pindai mauri (moravira kupisa kwawo), motsungirira kana kusatsungirira zvakangofanana kwamuri. Zvirokwazvo, murikungopiwa mubairo weizvo zvamaiita"
  52,17,"Zvirokwazvo, vanotya Allah vachange vari muParadhiso nezvinonakidza"
  52,18,"Vachinakidzwa nezvavapiwa naTenzi vavo, uye (nekuti) Tenzi vavo vakavabetsera kubva muhurango hwemoto unopisa"
  52,19,“Idyai nekunwa zvine mufaro nokuda kwezvamaiita.”
  52,20,"Vachagara pazvigaro zvakarongedzwa, uye tichavaroodza kune vakadzi vakanaka vane maziso ane rudo"
  52,21,"Uye avo vanotenda uye mhuri dzavo dzobva dzavatevera mukutenda, tichavabatanidza nemhuri dzavo kwavari, uye hatizodzikisi mugove wemabasa avo kana nechii zvacho. Munhu wese chipikirwa kune zvaakaita"
  52,22,Uye tichavapa michero nenyama yavanoda
  52,23,"Imomo vachapanana mukombe (wewaini), uye pachange pasina mitauro yakaipa kana chitadzo (nekuti vanenge vane mvumo yekunwa kubva kunaAllah)"
  52,24,Uye vakomana vavo (varanda) vachange vachitenderera pavari sokunge vari maPera akachengetedzwa
  52,25,Uye vamwe vachaswedera kune vamwe vachibvunzana
  52,26,"Vachiti: “Mushure taitya (murango waAllah) tiri mukati memhuri dzedu.”"
  52,27,"“Asi Allah vatiitira nyasha, uye vakatibetsera kubva mukurangwa nemoto.”"
  52,28,"“Zvirokwazvo, mushure taivasheedza (taivanamata). Zvirokwazvo (Allah) vane rudo, vane tsitsi.”"
  52,29,"Naizvozvo rangaridza (vanhu iwe Muhammad (SAW)). Nerudo rwaAllah, hausi mufemberi, kana kuti mupengo"
  52,30,"Kana kuti vanoti: “(Muhammad (SAW)) Mudetembi! Tiri kumirira kuti awirwe nedambudziko!”"
  52,31,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Mirai! Ndiri pamwechete nemi nevamiriri!”"
  52,32,Kana kuti njere dzavo dzinovatungamirira kune izvozvo (kunyepera Muhammad (SAW)) kana kuti vanhu vari kutyora mirairo (yaAllah)
  52,33,"Kana kuti vanoti: “(Muhammad (SAW)) Akawedzerera (Qur’aan)?” Asi ivo havatendi"
  52,34,Naizvozvo ngavaburitse mashoko akafanana naro (Qur’aan) kana vari pachokwadi
  52,35,Kana kuti vakasikwa pasina chiripo? Kana kuti ivo vakazvisika pachavo
  52,36,Kana kuti vakasika denga nenyika? Asi ivo havatendi
  52,37,Kana kuti vane hupfumi hwaTenzi vako? Kana kuti vadzvanyiriri vanoita zvavanoda nemutemo
  52,38,Kana kuti vane nzira yokudenga senzira yavo yekunzwa nayo (zvinenge zvichitaurwa nengirozi)? Zvino chisiya vateereri vavo vaburitse humboo uri pachena
  52,39,"Kana kuti ivo (Allah) vane vanasikana chete, uye imi mune vanakomana"
  52,40,"Kana kuti iwe (Muhammad (SAW)) uri kuvabvunza kuti vakupe mugove (wekusheedzera kuIslaam), nokudaro vakaremerwa nechikwereti"
  52,41,Kana kuti vane ruzivo rwezvisingaoneki zvavanonyora pasi
  52,42,Kana kuti vanoda kuronga (kupikisana newe Muhammad (SAW))? Asi avo vasingatendi (muhumwechete waAllah) ndivo vari kurongerwa
  52,43,Kana kuti vane chimwe chinamatwa chisiri Allah? Allah ngavarumbidzwe kubva mune izvo zvavanomusanganisa nazvo
  52,44,"Uye dai vakaona zvidimbu zvedenga zvichidonhera pasi, vaiiti: “Makore akaungana!”"
  52,45,Naizvozvo vasiye kusvikira vasangana nezuva ravo iro ravachatambura vokomoka (nekutyiswa)
  52,46,"Nezuva iro kuronga kwavo hakuvadziviriri, uye hakuzombovabetseri kana nechimwe"
  52,47,"Uye zvirokwazvo kune avo vanoita zvakaipa, vane murango umwewo (pasi rino nemumakuva), asi vazhinji vavo havazvizivi"
  52,48,"Saka mirira uchitsungirira (Muhammad (SAW)) matongero aTenzi vako, nokuti zvirokwazvo iwe uri pasi pemaziso edu; uye rumbidza Tenzi vako kana wamuka kubva kuhope"
  52,49,Uye nenguva dzemanheru varumbidze (Allah) uye nenguva dzekunyura kwenyeredzi
  53,1,Ndinopika nenyeredzi apo inoenda pasi
  53,2,Umwe wenyu (Muhammad (SAW)) haana kurasika kana kukanganisa
  53,3,Uye haangotauri zvaanoda pachake
  53,4,Anongori mashoko anodzikiswa kubva kudenga
  53,5,Akadzidziswa (Qur’aan) neuyo ane masimba makuru (Gabriel)
  53,6,"Uyo asina hurema pamuviri nepapfungwa dzake, uye akakwidza (Gabriel) akadzikama"
  53,7,Apo iye (Gabriel) paakanga ari pamusoro-soro pekupedzisira
  53,8,Ndokubva iye (Gabriel) aswedera ndokuuya padyo
  53,9,Uye akanga ari padyo seuta miviri kana kuti padyo
  53,10,Ndokubva (Allah) vadzikisa kumuranda wavo (Muhammad (SAW) kuburikidza naGabriel) zvavaida kudzikisa
  53,11,Moyo hauna kunyepa pane zvaakaona (Muhammad (SAW)
  53,12,"Munomupikisa here (Muhammad (SAW)) pane izvo zvaakaona (parwendo rwake rwekudenga, Mi’raaj)"
  53,13,Uye zvirokwazvo (Muhammad (SAW)) akamuona (Gabriel) kechipiri
  53,14,Padyo neSidratul Muntaha (muti weLoti uri pamuganhu redenga rekupedzisira uyo usina mupfuuri)
  53,15,Padyo nawo pane nzvimbo yekugara yeParadhiso
  53,16,Apo muti weLoti wakavharwa nezvakauvhara (Chiedza chaAllah uye nengirozi uye nemavara akasiyana siyana)
  53,17,Maziso ake (Muhammad (SAW)) haana kutarisa mativi kana kukanganisa
  53,18,"Zvirokwazvo, (Muhammad (SAW)) akaona zviratidzo zvaTenzi vake zvihombe"
  53,19,Murikuona here Laat naUzza (zvidhori zviviri zvemaArabhu zvavainamata)
  53,20,Uye naManaat (chimwe chidhori chemaArabhu chavainamata) wechitatu
  53,21,Ndizvo here kuti imi mune varume ivo (Allah) vane vakadzi
  53,22,"Zvirokwazvo, ikoko ndiko kugovanisa kwakaipa"
  53,23,"Anongori mazita chete amakatumidza imi nemadzibaba enyu, izvo Allah havana kudzikisa mvumo yazvo. Vanongotevedzera kufungidzira chete neizvo zvinoda moyo yavo, asi zvirokwazvo nungamiro yauya kwavari kubva kuna Tenzi vavo"
  53,24,Kana kuti munhu achawana zvaanoda
  53,25,Asi Allah ndivo muridzi wenyika yekupedzisira (hupenyu hwemangwana) uye wenyika yekutanga (pasi rino)
  53,26,"Uye ngirozi ngani dziri kumatenga idzo kureverera kwadzo hakuzombobetseri kana chimwechete, kunze kwekuti mushure mokunge Allah vabvumidza uyo wavanenge vada uye kufadzwa naye"
  53,27,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vasingatendi muzuva rekupedzisira vanotumidza ngirozi nemazita echikadzi"
  53,28,Asi havana ruzivo nazvo. Asi vanongotevera kufungidzira. Uye zvirokwazvo kufungidzira hakungatori nzvimbo yechokwadi
  53,29,Naizvozvo siyana (Muhammad (SAW)) neuyo anofuratira yeuchidzo yedu (Qur’aan) uye hapana chaanoda kunze hwehupenyu hwepanyika
  53,30,"Ndipo pavanosvika neruzivo rwavo. Zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vako ndivo vanoziva uyo anorasika kubva munzira yavo, uye vanoziva uyo ane kutungamirirwa"
  53,31,"Uye kuna Allah ndiko kune zviri kumatenga nepanyika, kuti vagopa mugove kune avo vanoita zvakashata neizvo zvavakaita, uye kupa mugove wakanaka kune avo vanoita zvakanaka"
  53,32,"Avo vanosiya zvitadzo zvihombe neFawaahish (zvitadzo nebonde risiri pamutemo) kusara kwezvidiki, zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vako vane kuregerera kukuru. Vanokuzivai chaizvo apo vakakusikai kubva muivhu, uye pamakanga muri mudumbu mavanaamai venyu. Naizvozvo musazvichenure. Vanoziva chaizvo uyo anotya (Allah)"
  53,33,Wakamuona here (Muhammad (SAW)) uyo anofuratira (Islaam)
  53,34,Uye akapa zvishoma ndokubva arega (kupa)
  53,35,Ane ruzivo here rwezvisingaonekwi kuti anoona
  53,36,Kana kuti haana kuziviswa nezviri mubhuku raMusa
  53,37,Uye neraAbrahamu uyo akazadzikisa zvose (zvaakatumwa)
  53,38,Kuti hakuna munhu ane musengwa wake (zvitadzo) achatakura musengwa wemumwe munhu
  53,39,Uyezve kuti munhu hapana chaachawana kunze kwezvaanoita
  53,40,Uye kuti mabasa ake achaonekwa
  53,41,Uyezve kuti achapiwa mubairo wakafanira wakakwana
  53,42,Uye kuti kuna Tenzi vako ndiko kune magumo
  53,43,Uye ndivo vanoita kuti (munhu) aseke uye kuchema
  53,44,Uye kuti ndivo vanokonzera rufu uye neupenyu
  53,45,"Uye kuti vanosika mapoka maviri, varume nevakadzi"
  53,46,Kubva muNutfah (mbeu yemukadzi nemurume) painobuditswa
  53,47,Uye kuti Allah ndivo vachamutsa zvakare (vafi)
  53,48,Uye kuti ndivo vanopa hupfumi hwakawanda uye nehushoma
  53,49,Uye kuti Allah ndivo muridzi weAsh-shi’raa (nyenyedzi yainamatwa nemaArabhu)
  53,50,Uye kuti ndivo (Allah) vakaparadza vanhu vekutanga vemhuri yaAad
  53,51,"Uye maThamood, havana kusiya kana umwechete wavo"
  53,52,"Uye nevanhu vaNowa mushure. Zvirokwazvo, vakanga vari vatadzi zvakanyanya vasinganzwi"
  53,53,Uye (Allah) vakaparadza maguta akarasirwa (eSodom uko kwakatumwa Loti)
  53,54,Naizvozvo vakavharwa neizvo zvakavavhara (chirango nematombo)
  53,55,Zvino ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu (imi vanhu) amusingagutsikani nawo
  53,56,Uyu (Muhammad (SAW)) muyambiri wevayambiri venguva yekutanga (kare)
  53,57,Zuva rekutongwa raswedera padyo
  53,58,Hakuna mumwe kunze kwaAllah anogona kuridzosa (shure kana mberi)
  53,59,Murikushamiswa here nemashoko aya (Qur’aan)
  53,60,Uye muchiwaseka musingachemi
  53,61,Apo muchitambisa nguva yenyu (nemafaro)
  53,62,Naizvozvo pfugamirai Allah uye munamatei (ari ega)
  54,1,"Nguva yaswedera, uye mwedzi wapatsanurwa (Vanhu vakakumbira chiratidzo kunaMuhammad (SAW), uye akavaratidza kupatsanurwa kwemwedzi"
  54,2,"Uye kana vakaona humboo vanofuratira, vachiti: “Aya ndivo mapipi asingaperi.”"
  54,3,"Uye vakaramba (Qur’aan) ndokutevera zvido zvavo. Uye zvinhu zvose zvichagadziriswa (zvichifambirana nemabasa, vaiti vemabasa akanaka vachaenda kuParadhiso, uye vaiti vemabasa akaipa vachaenda kuGehena)"
  54,4,Uye zvirokwazvo nhau dzakauya kwavari (muQur’aan) mune yambiro (inovarambidza zvakaipa)
  54,5,"Huchenjeri hwakakwana (iri Qur’aan), asi kuparidza kwevayambiri hakuvabatsiri"
  54,6,Naizvozvo iwe (Muhammad (SAW)) vasiye. Zuva iro mudaidzi achavadaidzira kune chinhu chinotyisa chaizvo
  54,7,Vachabuda mumakuva avo maziso aine kuzvininipisa sokunge vari hwiza idzo dzakapararira
  54,8,"Vachimhanyira kune mudaidzi. Vasingatendi vachati: “Iri izuva rakaoma.”"
  54,9,"Vanhu vaNowa mushure mavo vakaramba. Vakaramba muranda wedu, uye ndokuti: “Munhu anopenga!” Uye akatyityidzirwa"
  54,10,"Zvino akadaidza Tenzi vake (achiti): “Ndakurirwa, naizvozvo ndibetserei!”"
  54,11,Naizvozvo takavhura mikova yekudenga nemvura yainaya chaizvo
  54,12,Uye takaita kuti zvitubu zviyerere panyika. Naizvozvo mvura (yekudenga nepasi pano) yakasangana sekukomekedzwa kwakanga kwarongwa
  54,13,Uye takamutakura mungarava yakagadzirwa nemapuranga nezvipikiri
  54,14,Ichiyangarara iri pamusoro pemvura mumaziso edu (tichiona). Semubairo kune uyo akarambwa
  54,15,Uye zvirokwazvo takaisiya sechiratidzo. Saka pane here angarangarira
  54,16,Naizvozvo murango wangu nerangaridzo dzangu dzakanga dzakadii
  54,17,Uye zvirokwazvo takaita kuti Qur’aan rive nyore kunzwisisa uye kurangarira. Pane here angarangarira
  54,18,"(Vanhu va) Aad vakaramba (mutumwa wavo Hud), zvino mutongo wangu nerangaridzo yangu yakanga yakadii"
  54,19,"Zvirokwazvo, takatumira mhepo kwavari ine simba pazuva rakashata uye nematambudziko asingaperi"
  54,20,Ichiburitsa vanhu panze sokunge midzi yemadheti yakadzurwa
  54,21,Zvino mutongo wangu nerangaridzo yangu yakanga iri sei
  54,22,Uye zvirokwazvo Qur’aan takariita kuti rive nyore kunzwisisa uye kurangarira. Zvino pane here angarangarira
  54,23,MaThamood (zvakare) vakaramba yambiro
  54,24,"Vakati: “Tingatevera murume mumwechete pakati pedu? Chokwadi, tinenge tatorasika kana kukanganisika (kana kupenga)!”"
  54,25,“Ndizvo here kuti yeuchidzo yakatumirwa kwaari iye chete (Swaalih (AS)) mukati medu? Asi iye munyepi akaipa!”
  54,26,"Mangwana vachaziva kuti ndiani anonyepa, akaipa"
  54,27,"Zvirokwazvo, tirikutumira ngamera hadzi semuedzo kwavari. Saka vatarise (Swaalih (AS)), uye iva netariro"
  54,28,"Uye\tvazivise\tkuti\tmvura\tinogovaniswa\tpakati\tpavo,\tkodzero\tdzeumwe\tneumwe dzichizadzikiswa"
  54,29,Asi vakadaidza umwe wavo akatora banga (bakatwa) ndokubva aiuraya (ngamera)
  54,30,Saka mutongo wangu nerangaridzo yangu yakanga iri sei
  54,31,"Zvirokwazvo, takatumira kwavari Saihah imwe chete (murango weruzha rwakanyanya), uye vakabva vaita sokunge mashanga emafuro akaoma"
  54,32,"Uye zvirokwazvo takaita kuti Qur’aan rive nyore kunzwisisa uye kurangarira, zvino pane here angakwanisa kurangarira"
  54,33,Vanhu vaLoti vakaramba yambiro
  54,34,"Zvirokwazvo, takavatumira mhepo yematombo (yakavaparadza vese) kusara kwemhuri yaLoti. Takavabetsera munguva yokupedzisira yemanheru"
  54,35,Sechipo kubva kwatiri. Ndiwo mapiro atinoita mubairo kune uyo anopa kutenda
  54,36,"Uye zvirokwazvo iye (Loti) akavayambira maererano nemutongo wedu, asi vakataridza kusagutsikana neyambiro"
  54,37,"Uye zvirokwazvo vaida kunyadzisa vaenzi vake (nekuita hungochani navo). Naizvozvo takavhara maziso avo (tichiti): “Ravirai murango wangu neyambiro yangu.”"
  54,38,Uye zvirokwazvo murango wakafanira wakavasvikira rungwanani
  54,39,“Naizvozvo ravirai mutongo wangu neyambiro yangu.”
  54,40,Uye zvirokwazvo takaita kuti Qur’aan rive nyore kunzwisisa nekurangarira; zvino pane here umwe angarangarira
  54,41,Uye zvirokwazvo yambiro yakauya kune vanhu vaFarawo (kuburikidza naMusa naAroni)
  54,42,"Vakaramba humboo hwedu hwese, naizvozvo takavaparadza kuparadza kwemukuru anemasimba, uye anokwanisa kuita zvose"
  54,43,"Vari nani here avo venyu vasingatendi (imi maQuraish) pane avo (vari mushure mavo, vanhu vaNowa, Loti, Swaalih, naFarawo avo vakaparadzwa)? Kana kuti imi mune rusununguko rwakanyorwa (kuti hamuzowani chirango) mumabhuku"
  54,44,"Kana kuti vanoti: “Tiri vakundi vakawanda?”"
  54,45,Kuwanda kwavo kuchakurirwa uye vachafuratira vachitiza
  54,46,"Asi (Kumutswa) inguva yakatarwa kwavari, uye inguva ichange ichityisa zvikuru uye ichirwadza"
  54,47,"Zvirokwazvo, vatadzi vakarasika uye vachatsva (mumoto weGehena)"
  54,48,"Zuva iro vachadhonzerwa mumoto nezviso zvavo, (zvichanzi kwavari): “Ravirai imi kutsva nemoto!”"
  54,49,"Zvirokwazvo, takasika zvinhu zvose neQadar (nemarongero edu nekuda kwedu)"
  54,50,Uye kukomekedza kwedu kunongove kumwe chete sekubwaira kweziso
  54,51,"Uye zvirokwazvo, takaparadza vakafanana nemi, saka hapana here umwe angayeuka"
  54,52,Uye zvose zvavakaita zvakatonyorwa mumabhuku (emabasa)
  54,53,"Uye chinhu chose, chiduku kana chihombe chakanyorwa pasi (mu Al-Lauh Al-Mahfoodh chisati chaitika kana kuitwa)"
  54,54,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanotya (Allah), vachange vari mumapindu nenzizi (muParadhiso)"
  54,55,"Vachave muchigaro chechokwadi (Paradhiso), padyo naMambo (mukuru) ane simba rekuita zvose"
  55,1,Mupi ane tsitsi dzakanyanya (Allah)
  55,2,Vakava vanodzidzisa (vanhu) Qur’aan (netsitsi dzavo)
  55,3,Vakasika munhu
  55,4,Vakava vanomudzidzisa kutaura zvakanaka
  55,5,Zuva nemwedzi zvinomhanya munzira yadzo yakatarwa yakaerwa zvakanaka
  55,6,Uye zvirimwa (kana nyenyedzi) nemiti zvinopfugamira (Allah)
  55,7,"Uye matenga: Vakava vanomasimudza mudenga, uye vakava vanogadzirisa chikero"
  55,8,Kuti musazove munotsaudzira (kudzikisa) chikero
  55,9,"Uye muve munoera zvakafanira, uye musave munodzikisa chikero pakuera"
  55,10,"Uye nyika: Vakava vanoiita yezvisikwa"
  55,11,"Mukati\tmayo\tmune\tmichero,\tuye\tmiti\tyemadheti\tinobuditsa\tmapazi\tanenzvimbo dzinochengetedza michero"
  55,12,"Uye chibage chine mashizha acho nemashanga sechikafu chezvipfuyo, uye zvirimwa zvinonhuhwirira"
  55,13,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,14,Vakave vanosika munhu (Adam) kubva muivhu rakafanana neivhu rekuumbisa
  55,15,Uye maJinn vakaasika kubva muviriri remoto usina chiutsi
  55,16,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,17,Tenzi vekumabvazuva maviri (munguva yekupisa neyechando) nekumadokero maviri (munguva yekupisa neyechando)
  55,18,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,19,Vakave vanosiya nzizi mbiri (mvura ine munyu neisina) dzichisangana
  55,20,Pakati padzo pane chidziviro chekuti hapana inokwanisa kudarika imwe
  55,21,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,22,Madziri (nzizi) munobuda matombo akakosha (mapera nekora)
  55,23,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,24,"Uye ngarava ndedzavo dzinoenda nekuuya mumakungwa, semakomo"
  55,25,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,26,Zvose zviri pairi (nyika) zvichaparara
  55,27,"Uye kuchasara chiso chaTenzi vako chakazara nehukuru, neruremekedzo"
  55,28,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,29,"Ani naani ari kumatenga nepanyika vanovakumbira (Allah, rubetsero). Zuva nezuva vanenge vari mune zvimwe (sekupa hupenyu nerufu)"
  55,30,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,31,"Tichauya kwamuri, imi mapoka maviri (vanhu nemaJinn)"
  55,32,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,33,"Imi gungano remaJinn nevanhu! Kana muchikwanisa kupfuura hwaro hwematenga nenyika, pfuurai! Asi hamukwanisi kupfuura kunze kwekuti zvine mvumo (yaAllah)"
  55,34,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,35,"Kuchatumirwa kwamuri maviriri emoto usina chiutsi uye simbi yakanyunguduka, uye hamuzokwanisi kuzvidzivirira"
  55,36,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,37,"Zvino apo denga parichaparadzwa, uye robva raita dzvuku semafuta matsvuku"
  55,38,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,39,"Naizvozvo nezuva iroro hakuna mubvunzo uchabvunzwa munhu kana Jinn maererano nezvitadzo zvake (nekuti zvichange zvichizivikanwa nezviso zvavo, vamwe vachipenya (vekuParadhiso) uye vamwe vakasviba (vekuGehena)"
  55,40,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,41,"Vatadzi vachazivikananwa nezviratidzo zvavo, uye vachabatwa nebvudzi ravo repamberi uye netsoka dzavo"
  55,42,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,43,Iri ndiro Gehena iro vatadzi ravairamba
  55,44,Vachaenda pakati paro (Gehena) uye mvura inopisa
  55,45,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,46,Asi uyo anotya kumira pamberi paTenzi vake (oita mabasa akanaka) achawana mapindu maviri (muParadhiso)
  55,47,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,48,Anemapazi anopararira
  55,49,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,50,Mukati mawo muchange muine zvitubu zviviri zvinoerera
  55,51,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,52,Mukati mawo muchange muine marudzi ose emichero iri miviri miviri
  55,53,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,54,"Vachange vakarara pamibhedha yakarukirwa nesiriki, uye michero yemapindu maviri ichange iri padyo"
  55,55,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,56,"Mukati mawo muchange muine vakadzi vakatsiga, vasina varume kana maJinn akamborara navo"
  55,57,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,58,(Runako) Sokunge vari matombo akakosha (masandawana nemakora)
  55,59,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,60,Pane mubairo wezvakanaka here kunze kwezvakanaka
  55,61,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,62,"Uye asiri aya maviri, pane mamwe mapindu maviri (muParadhiso)"
  55,63,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,64,Ane ruvara rwakasvibira
  55,65,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,66,Mukati mawo (mapindu) muchange muine zvitubu zviviri zvinoerera
  55,67,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,68,Mukati mawo ose muchange muine michero uye madheti neRummaan (chibage chechirungu)
  55,69,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,70,Mukati mawo muchange muine vakadzi vakanaka
  55,71,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,72,Vakadzi vakanaka munzvimbo dzakachengetedzwa
  55,73,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,74,Hapana murume akambovabata mushure kana maJinn
  55,75,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,76,"Vanenge vakazorora pamakusheni akasvibira uye nemametiresi akakosha, akanaka"
  55,77,Naizvozvo ndeapi makomborero aTenzi venyu amucharamba (imi vanhu nemaJinn)
  55,78,"Rakakomborerwa zita raTenzi vako, mukuru, uye muridzi weremekedzo"
  56,1,Kana chiitiko chazoitika (zuva rekutongwa)
  56,2,Hapana marambiro nezvekuitika kwacho
  56,3,"Chichadzikisira (vamwe vachienda kuGehena), uye chichakwiridzira (vamwe vachienda kuParadhiso)"
  56,4,Apo nyika ichadengenyeka kudengenyeka kunotyisa
  56,5,Uye makomo achaparadzwa kuita huruva
  56,6,Kuti agove huruva inopepereka
  56,7,Uye mose muchange muri mapoka matatu
  56,8,"Naizvozvo avo vachange vari kuruoko rwerudyi (avo vachapiwa mabhuku ezviito zvavo mumaoko avo erudyi), zvichava zvakanaka sei kune avo vari kuruoko rwerudyi! (Seruremekedzo, nekuti vachapinda Paradhiso)"
  56,9,"Uye avo vachange vari kuruoko rweruboshwe (avo vachapiwa mabhuku ezviito zvavo mumaoko avo eruboshwe), vachange vakadii avo vari kuruoko rweruboshwe! (Sekunyadziswa, nekuti vachapinda kumoto)"
  56,10,Uye vekutanga (muIslaam nekuita mabasa akanaka pasi rino) vachange vari vekutanga (kuParadhiso)
  56,11,Vanhu vakadaro vachange vari padyo (naAllah)
  56,12,Mumapindu emufaro (Paradhiso)
  56,13,Huwandu hwavo (vekutanga) huchange huchibva kune vanhu vekutanga (kupinda muIslaam)
  56,14,Uye vashoma veavo (vekutanga) vachange vari kune vanhu vekupedzisira
  56,15,(Vachange vari) pazvigaro zvakashongedzwa nendarama nematombo akakosha
  56,16,"Vakagara ipapo, vakatarisana"
  56,17,Vakomana vasingafi vanovabatsira nekuvashandira vachange vachitenderera pavari
  56,18,"Nemakomichi, nemajagi, uye negirazi rewaini inoerera"
  56,19,Kubva kwairi havazombowani kurwadziwa nemusoro kana kudhakiwa
  56,20,Uye nemuchero wavanosarudza
  56,21,Nenyama yeshiri iyo yavanenge vachida
  56,22,Uye (kuchange kune) maHoor (vakadzi kwavo) vane maziso makuru ane rudo
  56,23,Sokunge matombo akakosha (mapera) akachengetedzwa
  56,24,Semubairo wezvavaiita
  56,25,Havambonzwi mashoko akaipa imomo kana kutaura kwehuipi imomo
  56,26,"Asi kutaura kuti: Rugare! Rugare! (kwaziso)"
  56,27,"Uye avo vokuruoko rwerudyi, vachange vari sei avo vekuruoko rwerudyi"
  56,28,Vachange vari pane miti yeLoti isina minzwa
  56,29,Uye mukati meTalh (miti yemabanana) ine michero yakaturikidzana imwe pamusoro peimwe
  56,30,Uye nemimvuri yakawedzerwa yakareba
  56,31,Uye nemvura ichierera
  56,32,Nemichero yakawanda
  56,33,"Isingashaiki kana kuita mishoma, kana isingaswikiriki"
  56,34,Uye mumibhedha yakasimudzwa mudenga
  56,35,"Zvirokwazvo, takavasika vakadzi vekuParadhiso vakakosha"
  56,36,Uye tikavaita mhandara
  56,37,"Vanoda (varume vavo chete), (uye) vezera rimwe"
  56,38,Veavo vekuruoko rwekurudyi
  56,39,Boka rakawanda (reavo veruoko rwerudyi) richabva kune vanhu vekutanga (vakatambira chitendero cheIslaam)
  56,40,Uye boka rakawanda (reavo vekuruoko rwerudyi) richabva muvanhu vekupedzisira
  56,41,"Uye avo vekuruoko rweruboshwe, vachange vakarasikirwa sei vekuruoko rweruboshwe"
  56,42,Mumhepo inopisa ine simba nemvura inokwata
  56,43,Nemumvuri wehutsi hutema
  56,44,"(Mvuri iwowo) hautonhoreri, kana kufadza"
  56,45,"Zvirokwazvo, mushure mezvo vainakidzwa"
  56,46,Uye vaishingirira kuita zvitadzo zvikuru (Kunamata Allah vachivasanganisa nezvimwe zvinhu nekuita mamwe mabasa akaipa)
  56,47,"Uye vaiti: “Kana tikafa tikave ivhu nemapfupa, zvirokwazvo tichazomutswa here?”"
  56,48,“Uye madzitateguru edu zvakare?”
  56,49,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “(Hongu!) Zvirokwazvo, avo vekare neavo vazvino.”"
  56,50,“Vose zvirokwazvo vachaunganidzwa pamwechete pamusangano wezuva rinozivikanwa.”
  56,51,“Uye zvakare zvirokwazvo imi vatadzi vanoramba (zuva rekutongwa)!”
  56,52,“Zvirokwazvo muchadya kubva pamiti yeZaqqoom (inovava zvikuru).”
  56,53,“Muchazadza matumbu enyu nazvo.”
  56,54,“Uye mobva manwa mvura inokwata pamusoro paizvozvo.”
  56,55,“Uye muchanwa (izvozvo) sekunge ngamera dzine nyota!”
  56,56,Ndiyo ichava varaidzo yavo pazuva rokutongwa
  56,57,"Isu takakusikai, saka sei musingatendi"
  56,58,Hamuoni here mvura yamunoburitsa (hurume)
  56,59,Ndimi here makaisika kana kuti isu tisu takaisika
  56,60,"Takatara rufu kwamuri mose, uye hatikurirwi"
  56,61,Kukushandurai uye tokusikai kukuitai izvo zvamusingazivi
  56,62,"Uye zvirokwazvo makatoziva kare mhando yechisikwa chokutanga (Adam), saka sei imi musingarangariri (kana kuchenjerera)"
  56,63,Zvino chindiudzai nezvembeu dzamunodyara pasi
  56,64,"Ndimi here munoita kuti dzikure, kana kuti tisu tinodzikudza"
  56,65,"Dai taida, tingadai takadziita marara akaoma, uye maizodemba (kana kusiiwa muchidzungaira)"
  56,66,"(Muchiti): “Zvirokwazvo taparadzwa!”"
  56,67,“Asi tanyengedzwa (tanyimwa)!”
  56,68,Munoiona here mvura yamunonwa
  56,69,Ndimi here munoita kuti inaye panyika kana kuti tisu tinokonzera kuti inaye pasi
  56,70,"Dai taida, tingadai takaiita munyu. Naizvozvo nemhaka yei musingatendi (Allah)"
  56,71,Munouona here moto uyo wamunotungidza
  56,72,"Ndimi here munoita kuti muti wacho ukure, kana kuti tisu tinoukudza"
  56,73,"Isu takauita yeuchidzo (yeGehena), uye chinhu chekushandisa kune vari parwendo (nevamwe vari munyika)"
  56,74,Zvino rumbidza zita raTenzi vako mukuru
  56,75,Saka ndinopika nekugara kwenyenyedzi
  56,76,Uye zvirokwazvo uku ndiko kupika kukuru dai maiziva
  56,77,Kuti zvirokwazvo (uku) kuverenga kunoremekedzwa (Qur’aan rinoremekedzwa)
  56,78,Kuri Mubhuku rakachengetedzwa (Al-Lauh Al-Mahfoodh)
  56,79,Iro (Bhuku rinaAllah) risingabatwi nemumwe munhu kunze kweavo vakachena (ngirozi)
  56,80,Rakadzikiswa (Qur’aan) kubva kuna Tenzi vezvisikwa zvose
  56,81,Ndiro here shoko iri (Qur’aan) ramunoramba (imi vasingatendi)
  56,82,"Uye pachinzvimbo (chokutenda Allah) pararamo yavakakupai, munovaramba (nekusatenda)"
  56,83,Naizvozvo sei musingabatsiri kana (mweya weuyo arikufa) wasvika pagurokuro
  56,84,Uye imi ipapo makatarisa
  56,85,"Asi isu (ngirozi dzedu dzinotora mweya) tiri padyo naye kupfuura imi, asi hamuzvioni"
  56,86,Sei musingati kana chokwadi musingazotongwi
  56,87,"Dzosai mweya (pamuviri wacho), kana imi muri pachokwadi"
  56,88,Zvino kana iye munhu ari kufa ari weavo wepedyo (naAllah)
  56,89,"(Kwaari kune) kuzorora neraramo, uye Paradhiso rinonakidza"
  56,90,Uye kana iye (mufi) ari wekurudyi
  56,91,Zvino pane kuchengetedzeka nerunyararo kune avo vekuruoko rwerudyi
  56,92,"Asi kana iye (mufi) ari umwe weavo vanoramba, vakarasika"
  56,93,Kwaari kuchave nemafaro emvura inokwata
  56,94,Uye kutsva mumoto weGehena
  56,95,"Zvirokwazvo, ichi ndicho chokwadi chaicho"
  56,96,Naizvozvo rumbidza zita raTenzi vako mukuru
  57,1,"Zvose zviri mumatenga nepanyika zvinorumbidza Allah, uye ndivo mukuru, ane hungwaru hwese"
  57,2,"Ndehwake humambo hwekumatenga nepanyika. Ndivo vanopa hupenyu uye rufu, uye ivo vanokwanisa kuita zvinhu zvose"
  57,3,"Ndivo vekutanga uye vekupedzisira, uye ndivo vepamusoro-soro uye vepadyo padyo. Uye ndivo vanoziva zvose"
  57,4,"Ndivo vakasika matenga nenyika mumazuva matanhatu, ndokubva vaenda pamusoro pechigaro (choumambo). Vanoziva zvinopinda munyika uye zvinobuda munyika, uye zvinodzika kubva kudenga uye izvo zvinosimuka kuenda ikoko. Uye vanemi kwese kwese kwamunenge muri. Uye Allah vanoona zvose zvamunoita"
  57,5,Ndehwake humambo hwekumatenga nepanyika. Uye hurongwa hwose hunodzokera kuna Allah
  57,6,"Vanoita kuti usiku hupinde muchaedza (kushomeka kweusiku kowedzerwa kunguva yemasikati), uye kuti chaedza (masikati) chipinde muhusiku (kudoka) (kushomeka kwemasikati kowedzerwa kuusika), uye vanoziva zvose zviri mumoyo"
  57,7,"Tendai muna Allah nemutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)), uye ipai kubva kune izvo zvavakakuitai vamiriri vazvo. Naizvozvo avo vanotenda pakati penyu uye vopa (munzira yaAllah), kwavari kune mubairo mukuru"
  57,8,Uye chii chinonetsa kwamuri kuti hamutendi kuna Allah! Uye mutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)) achikudaidzai kuti mutende kuna Tenzi venyu; uye ivo (Allah) zvirokwazvo vakatora chitsidzo chenyu kana muri vatendi chaivo
  57,9,"Ndivo vanodzikisa kune muranda wavo (Muhammad (SAW)) zviratidzo zviri pachena kuti vakuburitsei murima muchienda kuchaedza. Uye Allah vane chido nemi, uye tsitsi"
  57,10,"Uye chii chinonetsa kwamuri kuti hamupi (hupfumi hwenyu) munzira yaAllah? Uye kuna Allah ndiko kune nhaka yekumatenga uye nepanyika. Vasina kufanana pakati penyu ndeavo vakapa vasati vabudirira (kutora Makkah) uye vakarwa (neavo vakaita kudaro mushure). Vanhu vakadaro vane zvinzvimbo zvepamusoro kudarika avo vakashandisa (hupfumi) mushure uye vakarwa. Asi kune vose, Allah vakavimbisa zvakanaka. Uye Allah vanoziva zvose zvamunoita"
  57,11,"Ndiani uyo angapa Allah chikwereti chakanaka? Naizvozvo (Allah) vanobva vamuwedzera, uye anobva awana mubairo mukuru (Paradhiso)"
  57,12,"Zuva ramuchaona varume nevakadzi vanotenda, chaedza chavo chichimhanya mberi kwavo uye mumaoko avo ekurudyi. Mashoko akanaka kwamuri nhasi! Mapindu ane nzizi dzinoerera umo vachagara zvachose! Chokwadi, uku ndiko kubudirira kukuru"
  57,13,"Pazuva iro vanyengedzi, varume nevakadzi, vachati kune avo vanotenda: “Timirirei! Tibetserekane kubva muchaedza chenyu!” Zvichanzi: “Dzokerai kushure kwenyu! Motsvaga chiedza!” Saka mudhuri une gonhi uchaiswa pakati pavo. Mukati muchange muine tsitsi, uye panze pawo pachange paine murango"
  57,14,"(Vanyengedzi) vachavasheedza (vatendi): “Takanga tisiri nemi here?” (Vatendi) vachati: “Hongu! Asi makazvipinza pamiedzo pachenyu. Maitarisira kurangwa kwedu, uye hamuna kugutsikana (nekutenda), uye imi makanyengedzwa nezvido zvamanyepo kusvika kutonga kwaAllah kwasvika pakuitika. Uye mukuru wevanyengedzi (Satani) akakunyengedzai maererano naAllah.”"
  57,15,"Naizvozvo, zuva ranhasi hapana mubhadharo uchatorwa kwamuri (vanyengedzi), kunyangwe kubva kune avo vasingatendi (muIslaam). Nzvimbo yenyu imoto (weGehena). Ndiyo nzvimbo yenyu chaiyo. Uye zvirokwazvo ndiwo magumo akashata"
  57,16,"Haina kusvika here nguva kune avo vanotenda (muIslaam) kuti vabatikane moyo yavo nerangaridzo yaAllah (Qur’aan), uye nechokwadi chakadzikiswa, kuti vasazoita seavo vakapiwa Bhuku (Torah neVhangeri) mushure. Naizvozvo nguva ikarebeswa kwavari ndokubva moyo yavo yaomeswa? Asi vakawanda vavo vapanduki (havanzwisisi)"
  57,17,"Zivai kuti Allah vanopa hupenyu kune pasi mushure mekunge paparara. Zvirokwazvo, takaita kuti zviratidzo zvive pachena kwamuri, kana imi muchinzwisisa"
  57,18,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanopa maSwadaqaat (Zvipo neZakaah), vakadzi nevarume, uye vopa Allah chikwereti chakanaka chichawedzerwa kwavari, uye vachawana mubairo unoremekedzeka (Paradhiso)"
  57,19,"Uye avo vanotenda muna Allah nevatumwa vavo, vanhu vakadaro ndivo vari muchokwadi. Uye vakafa munzira yaAllah vana Tenzi vavo, vachawana mubairo wavo nechiedza chavo. Asi avo vasingatendi (muIslaam) uye vachiramba zviratidzo zvedu, vanhu vakadaro ndivo vachava vagari vemuGehena"
  57,20,"Zivai kuti zvirokwazvo hupenyu hwepanyika ndehwekungotamba chete, nokuvaraidzwa uye kunakidzwa nekungozvikudza chete pakati penyu, uye kuwanda kwehupfumi nevana. Zvakafanana nemvura inonaya, apo zvirimwa kukura kwazvo kunofadza vanorima; mushure mezvo munozviona zvichiita ruvara rwendarama, zvobva zvaoma zvoita mashanga. Asi muhupenyu hwemangwana kune mutongo wakaoma (kune vasingatendi - vanoita mabasa akaipa), nekuregererwa kubva kuna Allah uye mafaro (aAllah) (kune vatendi - vanoita mabasa akanaka). Uye hupenyu hwenyika ino hunongova kunakirwa kwekunyengedzwa"
  57,21,"Mhanyidzanai kururegerero rwaTenzi venyu, uye Paradhiso iyo yakakura sematenga nenyika, yakagadzirirwa avo vanotenda muna Allah nevatumwa vavo. Iwayo ndiwo makomborero aAllah avanopa uyo wavanoda. Uye Allah ndivo muridzi wemakomborero makuru"
  57,22,"Hakuna dambudziko rinouya panyika, kana kwamuri pachenyu, asi kuti rinenge rakatonyorwa mubhuku mushure tisati tariunza pakurarama. Zvirokwazvo, izvozvo zviri nyore kuna Allah"
  57,23,"Kuitira kuti musazoshungurudzika pane zvinhu zvamunokundikana kuwana, kana kufadzwa nezvinhu zvamunopiwa. Uye Allah havadi munhu anozvikudza achizvitutumadza"
  57,24,"Avo vakaomera uye vachikurudzira vanhu kuti vachiomera (Allah havadi zvipo zvavo). Uye uyo anofuratira (osiya kutenda), zvino zvirokwazvo Allah ndivo mupfumi (vasina chavanoda), vanofanirwa kurumbidzwa chete"
  57,25,"Zvirokwazvo, takatuma vatumwa vedu nezviratidzo zviri pachena, uye tikadzikisa Bhuku navo nechikero kuti vanhu vayere zvakafanira. Uye takadzikisa simbi, mairi mune simba uye pundutso kuvanhu, kuitira kuti Allah vagoziva kuti ndiani achavabetsera (muchitendero chavo) nevatumwa vavo pane zvisingaoneki. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vane simba, uye ndivo mukuru"
  57,26,"Uye zvirokwazvo takatumira Nowa naAbrahamu, uye takaisa mumhuri dzavo huporofita nemabhuku. Uye mukati mavo mune vamwe vakatungamirirwa; asi vakawanda vavo vapanduki (vasingateereri Allah)"
  57,27,"Uyezve takatevedza mushure mavo nevatumwa, uye tikatuma Jesu mwana waMariya, uye takamupa Injeel (Vhangeri). Tikaisa rudo netsitsi mumoyo yeavo vakamutevera. Asi kugara mukereke vachinamata vasingaroori kwavakawedzera, izvo hatina kuvanyorera, asi (vakazviita) vachitsvaga kufadza Allah chete, asi havana kuzviita maitirwo azvinofanira kuitwa. Naizvozvo takapa avo vakatenda mukati mavo mubairo wavo; asi vazhinji vavo vapanduki (vasingateereri Allah)"
  57,28,"Imi vanotenda (muna Musa naJesu)! Ityai Allah, uye motenda mune mutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)), vachakupai tsitsi dzavo dzakapetwa kaviri, uye vachakupai chiedza chamuchafamba nacho, uye vachakuregererai. Uye Allah ndivo vanoregerera, vane tsitsi zhinji"
  57,29,"Kuitira kuti vanhu veBhuku (Makristu nemaJudha) vagoziva kuti havana simba pamusoro pemakomborero aAllah, uye kuti makomborero ari muruoko rwaAllah, vanopa uyo wavanoda. Uye Allah ndivo muridzi wemakomborero makuru"
  58,1,"Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanzwa mashoko ake (Khaulah bint Tha’labah) uyo ari kuita gakava newe (Muhammad (SAW)) maererano nemurume wake (Aus Ibn As-Swaamit), uye achinyunyuta kuna Allah. Uye Allah vanonzwa kupikisana kwenyu. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanonzwa zvose, vanoona zvose"
  58,2,"Avo mukati menyu vanozvirambidza vakadzi vavo kuburikidza neDhihaar (Kuti kwavari: “Wakafanana naamai vangu”), havangaiti vana mai vavo. Hapana vanokwanisa kuita vana mai vavo kunze kweavo vakavabereka. Uye zvirokwazvo vanotaura mashoko akaipa nemanyepo. Uye zvirokwazvo Allah vanokanganwira, uye vanoregerera"
  58,3,Uye avo vanozvirambidza vakadzi vavo neDhihaar uye voda kuzvisunungura kubva kune zvavakataura vanofanirwa (panyaya yakadaro) kusunungura muranda vasati vabatana (kusangana pabonde). Ndiyo rairo kwamuri (kuti musave munozviita zwe). Uye Allah vanoziva zvamunoita zvose
  58,4,"Asi uyo asingakwanisi kuwana (Mari yekusunungura muranda) anofanirwa kutsanya mwedzi miviri yakatevedzana vasati vasangana (pabonde). Asi kana asingakwanisi (kutsanya), anofanirwa kupa chikafu kuvanhu makumi matanhatu vanotambura. Ndiko kuti muve nekutenda kwakakwana kuna Allah nemutumwa wavo. Uye iyi ndiyo mirairo yakatarwa naAllah. Uye vasingatendi, vachawana mutongo unorwadza"
  58,5,"Zvirokwazvo avo vanopikisa Allah nemutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)) vachanyadziswa, sokunyadziswa kwakaitwa avo mushure mavo. Uye takatumira zviratidzo zviri pachena. Uye vasingatendi vachawana mutongo unonyadzisa"
  58,6,Pazuva iro Allah vachavamutsa vese pamwechete nekuvaudza zvavakaita. Allah vakazvichengeta apo ivo vakazvikanganwa. Uye Allah mupupuri pamusoro pezvinhu zvose
  58,7,"Hauna kuona here kuti Allah vanoziva zvose zviri kumatenga nepanyika? Hapana zvinotaurwa muchivande nevatatu asi kuti ivo (Allah) ndevechina (neruzivo rwavo asi ivo vari pamusoro pematenga), kana kuti vashanu asi kuti ivo (Allah) ndevechitanhatu (neruzivo rwavo), kana kuti vashoma pane izvozvo kana vakawanda asi kuti (Allah) vanova pose pavanenge vari. Uyezve (Allah) vachavazivisa zvavaiita pazuva rekutongwa. Zvirokwazvo Allah ndivo vanoziva zvinhu zvose"
  58,8,"Hauna here kuona avo vakarambidzwa kuita misangano yavo muchivande ndokubva vadzokera kune izvo zvavakarambidzwa. Uye vanotaurirana zvitadzo nemabasa akashata uye nekusateerera mutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)). Uye kana ivo vakauya kwauri, vanokukwazisa nekwaziso isina kumboitwa naAllah kwauri, uye mumoyo vanoti: “Sei Allah vasingatirangi nokuda kwezvatinotaura?” Gehena richavakwanira, uye vachatsva imomo. Uye zvirokwazvo ndiwo magumo akashata"
  58,9,"Imi vanotenda! Kana muchiita musangano muchivande, itai kwete nechinangwa chekutadza kana mabasa akaipa uye kusateerera mutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)), asi taurai zvakanaka uye nekutya Allah; uye ityai Allah avo kwavari ndiko kwamuchaunganidzwa"
  58,10,"Zvirokwazvo, misangano yakavanzwa ndeyaSatani, kuitira kuti agokonzeresa kushushikana kune avo vanotenda. Asi haakwanisi kuvarwadzisa kana nechimwe chinhu asi nekuda kwaAllah. Uye vatendi vanofanirwa kuvimba naAllah"
  58,11,"Imi vanotenda! Kana zvikanzi kwamuri gadzirai nzvimbo pamisangano, gadzirai. Allah vachakugadzirirai nzvimbo (netsitsi dzavo). Uye kana zvikanzi simukai (kunonamata kana kunoita mamwe mabasa akanaka), simukai. Allah vachakwiridzira avo vanotenda pane chimwe chinzvimbo, pamwe neavo vakapiwa ruzivo. Uye Allah vanoziva zvamunoita"
  58,12,"Imi vanotenda! Kana muchida kuona mutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)) pachivande, ipai chipo musati masangana naye pachivande. Izvozvo zvakakunakirai uye zvakachena. Asi kana musingakwanisi kuwana (chipo), zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoregerera, vane tsitsi"
  58,13,"Mungatya kupa chipo musati masangana naye muchivande? Kana mukasazviita, uye Allah vakakuregererai, nokudaro chiitai Swalaah (Munamato) uye mopa chipo (Zakaah) uye moteera Allah nemutumwa wavo. Uye Allah vane ruzivo rweizvo zvamunoita"
  58,14,"Hauna kuona here (Muhammad (SAW)) avo (vanyengedzi) vanotora vanhu vakatsamwirwa naAllah seshamwari (maJudha)? Havasi vamwe venyu kana vamwe vavo (maJudha), uye vanopika nemanyepo apo vachiziva"
  58,15,"Allah vakavagadzirira mutongo wakaomarara. Zvirokwazvo, izvo zvavaiita zvakaipa"
  58,16,Vanoita mhiko dzavo chidzitiro (pamabasa avo akaipa). Nokudaro vanodzivisa (vanhu) munzira yaAllah. Naizvozvo vachawana mutongo unonyadzisa
  58,17,"Hupfumi hwavo nevana vavo hazvisi kana kuzovadzivirira kubva kuna Allah kana nechimwechete. Vanhu vakadaro ndivo vagari vekumoto, vachagara imomo zvachose"
  58,18,"Nezuva iro Allah vachavamutsa vose, zvino vachapika kwavari sekupika kwavanoita kwamuri (maMuslim). Uye vanofunga kuti vane zvavainazvo. Zvirokwazvo, ivo vanonyepa"
  58,19,"Satani akavakurira. Naizvozvo akavaita kuti vakanganwe kurangarira Allah. Vanhu vakadaro ndivo chikwata chaSatani. Chokwadi, chikwata chaSatani ndicho chakarasikirwa"
  58,20,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanopikisa Allah nemutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)), vachange vari mukati meavo vepasi pasi"
  58,21,"Allah vakatonyora: “Zvirokwazvo, ini nevatumwa vangu tisu tichakunda.” Zvirokwazvo, Allah ndivo vane simba rese, ndivo mukuru"
  58,22,"Iwe (Muhammad (SAW)) haufi wakawana vanhu avo vanotenda kuna Allah uye nezuva rekutongwa (rekupedzisira) vachiita ushamwari neavo vanopikisa Allah nemutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)), kunyangwe zvazvo vari vanababa vavo kana kuti vana vavo kana madzikoma avo kana hama dzavo dzepedyo. Kune vanhu vakadaro, (Allah) vakavanyorera kutenda mumoyo yavo, uye vakavasimbisa nemweya (uchapupu nechiedza) kubva kwavari. Uye vachavapinza muParadhiso rine nzizi dzinoerera mavachagara zvachose. Allah vachifara navo uye ivo vachifara naAllah. Vanhu vakadaro ndivo chikwata chaAllah. Chokwadi, chikwata chaAllah ndicho chichabudirira"
  59,1,"Zvose zviri kumatenga nepanyika zvinorumbidza Allah. Uye ndivo mukuru, vane huchenjeri hwese"
  59,2,"Ndivo vakaburitsa avo vasingatendi kubva kuvanhu veBhuku (maJudha emhuri ya Nadheer) kubva mudzimba dzavo pakuunganidzwa kwekutanga. Hamuna kumbofungidzira kuti ivo vachabuda. Uye ivo vaifunga kuti nzvimbo dzavo dzakachengetedzwa dzaizovadzivirira kubva kuna Allah! Asi Allah vakavasvikira (chirango chavo) kubva kune nzvimbo yavakanga vasingafungiri. Uye vakaisa kutya mumoyo yavo kusvika pakuti vakaparadza pokugara pavo pachavo nemaoko avo uye nemaoko evatendi. Zvino torai chidzidzo, imi vane maziso (ekuona)"
  59,3,"Uye dai kusiri kuti Allah vakanga vakanyora kudzingwa kwavari, vangadai zvirokwazvo vakavaranga panyika ino, uye kuhupenyu hwemangwana vachawana mutongo wemoto (Gehena)"
  59,4,"Nekuda kwekuti vakapikisa Allah nemutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)). Uye uyo anopikisa Allah, zvirokwazvo, Allah vakaoma pakuranga"
  59,5,"Iyo miti (yemadheti yemuvengi) yamakagura (maMuslim), kana kusiya yakamira nemidzi yayo, yakanga iri mvumo yaAllah, uye kuitira kuti vagonyadzisa vapanduki (vasingateereri)"
  59,6,"Uye zvakapiwa naAllah semhimbiri kune mutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)) kubva kwavari, musina kuzvirwira kana nehachi kana pangamera. Asi Allah vanopa simba kuvatumwa vavo pamusoro peuyo wavanoda. Uye Allah vanokwanisa kuita zvinhu zvose"
  59,7,"Izvo zvinopiwa naAllah semhimbiri kumutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)) kubva kune vanhu vemumaguta, ndezvaAllah, uye mutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)), uye hama dzake dzepedyo, uye nherera, uye vanoshaya, uye nevafambi (vari parwendo), kuitira kuti mukana usave wevapfumi chete mukati menyu. Uye chose chamunopiwa nemutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)), chibatisisei; uye izvo zvaanokurambidzai, siyai. Uye ityai Allah; zvirokwazvo, Allah vakaoma pakuranga"
  59,8,"(Pane mugove zvakare) kune vatami vanotambura, avo vakaburitswa mudzimba dzavo nehupfumi hwavo, vachitsvaga makomborero kubva kuna Allah uye mufaro wavo, uye kubetsera Allah (chitendero chavo) nemutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)). Vanhu vakadaro ndivo vari pachokwadi (mune zvavanotaura)"
  59,9,"Uye avo mushure mavo vakange vaine dzimba (kuMadinah) uye vakatenda, vanoda avo vakatama vachiuya kwavari, uye havana godo mumoyo yavo pane izvo zvavakapiwa (kubva muhupfumi wemhuri yaNadheer), uye vanovapa (vatami) sarudzo pamusoro pavo kunyangwe zvazvo ivo vaizvida. Uye uyo anobetserwa kubva mukuomera kwemoyo wake, vanhu vakadaro ndivo vachabudirira"
  59,10,"Uye avo vakauya mushure mavo vanoti: “Tenzi vedu! Tiregerereiwo uye madzikoma edu avo vakatitangira kutenda, uye musaise ruvengo mumoyo yedu kune avo vanotenda. Tenzi vedu! Zvirokwazvo, mune ngoni dzakazara, uye tsitsi zhinji"
  59,11,"Hauna (Muhammad (SAW)) kuona here vanyengedzi avo vanotaura kune madzikoma avo, avo vasingatendi kubva mune vanhu veBhuku (vachiti): “(Tinopika naAllah!) Kana imi mukadzingwa, zvirokwazvo tichaenda pamwe nemi, uye hatizomboteereri kana ani zvake pamusoro penyu; uye kana mukarwiswa, zvirokwazvo tichakubetserai.” Asi Allah vanopupura kuti zvirokwazvo vanyepi"
  59,12,"Chokwadi, kana vakaburitswa (maJudha), havambobudi (vanyengedzi) pamwe navo; uye kana vakarwisa havambovabetseri. Uye kana vakavabetsera, vachafuratira shure, uye havambozobudiriri"
  59,13,"Zvirokwazvo, imi (vatendi veIslaam) munotonyanya kutyisa mumoyo yavo kukunda Allah, nechikonzero chokuti vanhu vasinganzwisisi (masimba aAllah)"
  59,14,"Havambokurwisei imi vari pamwechete, asi kunze kwekuti vari mumaguta akachengetedzwa, kana kuseri kwemadziro. Ruvengo pakati pavo rwakasimba. Munofunga kuti vakabatana, asi moyo yavo yakapatsanurwa, nokuda kwekuti vanhu vasinganzwisisi"
  59,15,"Vakafanana neavo mushure mavo venguva yakapfuura yepedyo (maJudha vemhuri yaQainuqa), vakaravira magumo emabasa avo akaipa, uye vachawana (mune ramangwana) mutongo unorwadza"
  59,16,"(Shamwari dzavo dzinovanyengedza) Kufanana naSatani, paanoti kune munhu: “Usatenda muna Allah.” Asi paanorega kutenda, (Satani) anoti: “Ini ndakasununguka kubva kwauri. Zvirokwazvo, ini ndinotya Allah, Tenzi vezvisikwa zvose!”"
  59,17,"Naizvozvo, magumo avo vese ndeekuti vachange vari mumoto vose, umo vachagara. Iwowo ndiwo mubairo wevatadzi"
  59,18,"Imi vanotenda! Ityai Allah, uye munhu ngaatarise kuti chii chaarikuita kuitira mangwana, uye ityai Allah. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoziva zvose zvamunoita"
  59,19,"Uye musaite seavo vakakanganwa Allah, uye (Allah) vakavaita kuti vazvikanganwe pachavo. Vanhu vakadaro ndivo vatadzi (vasingateereri Allah)"
  59,20,Vagari vemumoto havana kufanana nevagari vemuParadhiso. Vagari vemuParadhiso ndivo vachave vakabudirira
  59,21,Dai takadzikisa Qur’aan iri kugomo mairiona richizvininipisa uye kuparara nekutya Allah. Iyi ndiyo mifananidzo yatinopa vanhu kuti pamwe vangacherechedze
  59,22,"Ndivo Allah, avo hakuna chimwe chinamatwa kunze kwavo, muzivi wezvisingaoneki nezvinooneka. Ndivo vane nyasha, vane tsitsi zhinji"
  59,23,"Ndivo Allah, avo hakuna chimwe chinamatwa kunze kwavo, Mambo, Mutsvene, Vakasununguka, Muchengetedzi, Mutarisi, Mukuru, Vane masimba, Mukuru Mukuru. Allah ngavarumbidzwe pamusoro pezvose zvavanomusanganisa nazvo"
  59,24,"Ndivo Allah, Musiki, Mutangi wezvinhu zvose, Muumbi wezvose. Vane mazita ese akanaka. Zvose zviri kumatenga nepanyika zvinovarumbidza. Uye ndivo Mukuru, vane huchenjeri hwese"
  60,1,"Imi vanotenda! Musatora mhandu dzangu nemhandu dzenyu seshamwari, muchidzitaridza rudo, asi vasina kutenda mune izvo zvauya kwamuri muchokwadi (Islaam), uye vachidzinga mutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)) pamwechete nemi (kubva munyika yenyu) nokuda kwekuti munotenda muna Allah, Tenzi venyu! Apo pamunobuda muchirwa munzira (yaAllah) yangu uye muchitsvaga mufaro wangu (musatora avo vasingatendi seshamwari). Munotaridza ushamwari kwavari muchivande, asi ini ndichiziva izvo zvamunovanza uye izvo zvamunoburitsa pachena. Uye uyo anozviita pakati penyu (maMuslim), zvirokwazvo anenge arasika chaizvo kubva munzira tsvene"
  60,2,"Kana vakakwanisa kuwana mukana pamusoro penyu, vanobva vaita mhandu dzenyu, uye vanobva vatambanudza maoko avo nerurimi rwavo mune zvakaipa, uye vanoshuvira kuti dai mukasatenda"
  60,3,Hama dzenyu nevana venyu havazokubetserai pazuva reQiyaamah (kumutswa kubva kuvafi). (Allah) vachatonga pakati penyu. Uye Allah vanoona zvose zvamunoita
  60,4,"Zvirokwazvo, pane muenzaniso wakanaka kwamuri pana Ibrahim (Abrahamu) neavo vakange vainaye, apo pavakati kune vanhu vavo: “Chokwadi, takasununguka kubva kwamuri uye neizvo zvamunonamata zvisiri Allah. Isu takurambai, uye pakati pedu nemi pave neruvengo uye kutsamwirana zvachose kusvikira imi matenda muna Allah mumwechete,” kusara kwemashoko aAbrahamu kuna baba vake: “Chokwadi, ndichakukumbirirai ruregerero (kuna Allah), asi handina simba rekukuitirai chimwe chinhu pamberi paAllah.” “Tenzi vedu! Tinovimba nemi, uye kwamuri ndiko kwatinoreurura, uye kwamuri ndiko kwatichadzokera.”"
  60,5,"“Tenzi vedu! Musatiite muedzo weavo vasingatendi, uye tiregerereiwo, Tenzi vedu! Zvirokwazvo imi, imi chete ndimi mukuru, ane huchenjeri hwose.”"
  60,6,"Chokwadi, paive nemuenzaniso wakanaka kwamuri kubva kwavari wekutevedzera, kune avo vanovimba kusanga naAllah uye zuva rekutongwa. Uye uyo anofuratira, zvirokwazvo, Allah ndivo mupfumi (vasina chavanoda), uye vanekodzero yekurumbidzwa chete"
  60,7,"Pamwe Allah vangagadzira hushamwari pakati penyu neavo vamakaita vavengi. Uye Allah vane simba (pamusoro pezvinhu zvese), uye Allah vanoregerera zvikuru, vane tsitsi zhinji"
  60,8,"Allah havakurambidzii kushanda (zvakafanira uye zvakanaka) neavo vasinga kurwisei maererano nechitendero kana kukudzingai mudzimba dzenyu. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoda avo vanoshanda zvakafanira uye zvakanaka"
  60,9,"Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanokurambidzai kune avo vakakurwisai muchitendero uye vakakudzingai mudzimba dzenyu, uye vakabetsera kukudzingai, Allah vanokurambidzai kuita ushamwari navo. Asi uyo anoita ushamwari navo, vanhu vakadaro ndivo vatadzi (vasingateereri Allah)"
  60,10,"Imi vanotenda! Kana vatendi vechikadzi vauya kwamuri sevatami, vaedzei, asi Allah vanoziva kutenda kwavo. Kana mukaona kutenda mavari, musavadzosera kune vasingatendi. Havabvumidzwi kwavari kana ivo kubvumidzwa kwavari (kuroorana). Uye vapei (vasingatendi) zvavakashandisa (Mahr – Mari inobviswa nemurume achipa mudzimai wake pazuva remuchato). Uye hapana mhaka kwamuri kana imi mukavaroora kana mukavapa mugove wavo (Mahr). Uye musarambe mune vakadzi vasingatendi sevakadzi venyu, uye mobvunza zvamakashandisa (kudzorerwa Mahr) uye ivo (vasingatendi) ngavabunzewo zvavakashandisa. Uku ndiko kutonga kwaAllah, vanotonga pakati penyu. Uye Allah vanoziva zvese, vane huchenjeri hwese"
  60,11,"Uye kana mumwe wevakadzi venyu akaenda kune avo vasingatendi achibva kwamuri (asiya chitendero, uye avo vasingatendi voramba kukudzorerai zvamakashandisa (Mahr), uye mukavarwisa movatorera hupfumi), chibhadharai (kubva muhupfumi iwowo) avo vane vakadzi vakaenda zvakangofanana nezvavakashandisa (Mahr). Uye ityai Allah avo vamunotenda mavari"
  60,12,"Iwe muporofita! Kana vakadzi vanotenda vauya kwauri vachikupa Bai’ah (Mhiko), kuti havasi kuzosanganisa chimwe chinhu naAllah, havasi kuzoba, uye kuti havasi kuzoita cheupombwe, uye kuti havasi kuzouraya vana vavo, uye kuti havasi kuzombotaura manyepo vachinyepa kuti vana vavainavo ndevevarume vavo, uye kuti havasi kuzorega kukuteerera pane izvo zvakana (Islaam), chitambira Mhiko (Bai’ah) dzavo kwauri, uye vokumbira Allah kuti vavaregerere. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoregerera zvikuru, vane tsitsi dzakanyanya"
  60,13,"Imi vanotenda! Musashamwaridzana nevanhu vakatsamwirwa naAllah (maJudha). Chokwadi, havana tarisiro yehupenyu hwemangwana (kuti vachawana zvakanaka), sekushaiwa tarisiro kweavo vasingatendi kune avo vari kumakuva (kuti vachamuka pazuva rekutongwa)"
  61,1,"Zvose zviri kumatenga nepanyika zvinorumbidza Allah. Uye ndivo mukuru, vane huchenjeri hwese"
  61,2,Imi vanotenda! Sei muchitaura izvo zvamusingaiti
  61,3,Zvakanyanya kuvengwa pamberi paAllah ndezvekutaura izvo zvamusingaiti
  61,4,"Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoda avo vanorwa munzira yavo vari pamitsara sokunge mudhuri wakasimba"
  61,5,"Uye rangarirai apo Musa akati kuvanhu vake: “Imi vanhu vangu! Nemhaka yei imi muchindirwadzisa asi imi muchiziva muchokwadi kuti ini ndiri mutumwa waAllah kwamuri?” Saka pavakafuratira, Allah vakaita kuti moyo yavo ifuratire (nzira yakanaka). Uye Allah havatungamiri vanhu vasingateereri"
  61,6,"Uye rangarirai apo Isa (Jesu) mwana wa Mariya akati: “Imi vana vaIzrairi! Ini ndiri mutumwa waAllah kwamuri, kuzodudzira izvo zvakauya pamberi pangu zviri muTorah, uye kupa mashoko akanaka emutumwa achauya mushure mangu, zita rake anonzi Ahmad (zita rimwe raMuhammad (SAW)).” Asi paakauya (Ahmad (SAW)) kwavari nehumboo huri pachena, vakati: “Aya masaramusi ari pachena.”"
  61,7,"Uye ndiani anotadza zvikuru kudarika uyo anonyepera Allah, asi iye achidaidzirwa kuIslaam? Uye Allah havatungamiriri vanhu vanotadza"
  61,8,"Vanoshuvira kudzima mwenje waAllah (Islaam) nemiromo yavo, asi Allah vachadzadzikisa mwenje wavo kunyangwe zvazvo vasingatendi vachizvivenga"
  61,9,Ndivo vakatuma mutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)) nenungamiro uye chitendero chechokwadi (Islaam) kuti chigokunda zvitendero zvose kunyangwe zvazvo maMushrikoon (Vasingatendi nevanonamata vana mwari vakawanda) vachizvivenga
  61,10,Imi vanotenda! Ndingakutungamirai here kune bhizimusi richakununurai kubva kumurango unorwadza
  61,11,"Kuti imi mutende kuna Allah uye mutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)), uye moshinga nekurwa munzira yaAllah nehupfumi hwenyu uye nehupenyu hwenyu. Izvozvo ndizvo zvakanaka kwamuri kana muchiziva"
  61,12,"(Allah) vachakuregererai zvitadzo zvenyu, uye vachakupinzai muParadhiso iro pasi paro panoerera nzizi, uyedzimba dzakanaka muEden, Paradhiso. Zvirokwazvo, ikoko ndiko kubudirira kukuru"
  61,13,"Nezvimwe zvamunoda kubva kuna Allah (vachakupai), rubatsiro kubva kuna Allah nekukunda kuri pedyo. Uye ipa mashoko akanaka (Muhammad (SAW)) kune vatendi"
  61,14,"Imi vanotenda! Ivai vabetseri vaAllah sokutaura kwakaita Isa (Jesu) mwana waMariya kuvadzidzi vake (achiti): “Ndivanaani vachandibetsera kuna Allah?” Vadzidzi vakataura kuti: “Isu tiri vabetseri vaAllah!” Naizvozvo chikwata chevana veIzrairi chakatenda uye chikwata chimwe hachina kutenda. Naizvozvo takapa simba kune avo vakatenda pamusoro pemhandu dzavo, uye vakabva vakunda"
  62,1,"Zvose zviri kumatenga nepanyika zvinorumbidza Allah, Mambo, Mutsvene, Mukuru, Muchenjeri"
  62,2,"Ndivo avo vakatuma kubva mune vasina kudzidza mutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)) mukati mavo, achiverenga ndima dzavo kwavari, uye achivachenura (kubva mukusatenda), uye achivadzidzisa Bhuku (Qur’aan) neruzivo Al-Hikmah (Sunnah: Manamatiro nemagariro aMuhammad (SAW)), kunyange zvazvo vakange vari mukurasika kuri pachena"
  62,3,"Uye (vakamutuma Muhammad (SAW)) kune vamwe mukati mavo (maMuslim) avo vasati vave navo (asi vachauya). Uye (Allah) ndivo mukuru, vane huchenjeri wese"
  62,4,Ndiwo makomborero aAllah avanopa kune wavanoda. Uye Allah ndivo muridzi wemakomborero makuru
  62,5,Muenzaniso weavo vakapiwa Torah vobva varega kurichengetedza wakafanana nedhongi rinotakura mabhuku (asi ariwanzwisisi). Wakaipa sei muenzaniso weavo vanoramba zviratidzo zvaAllah. Uye Allah havatungamiri vanhu vanotadza
  62,6,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Imi maJudha! Kana imi muchiita sokunge shamwari dzaAllah, kusara kwevanhu vose, chishuvirai rufu kana muri pachokwadi.”"
  62,7,Asi havamborushuviri (rufu) nokuda kwezvakaitwa nemaoko avo! Uye Allah vanoziva zvikuru vatadzi
  62,8,"Iti (kwavari): “Zvirokwazvo, rufu rwamunotiza, zvirokwazvo rwuchakubatai, muchazodzorerwa zvakare kuna (Allah), muzivi wezvisipo nezvinoonekwa, uye vachakuzivisai (Allah) izvo zvamaiita.”"
  62,9,"Imi vanotenda! Kana Swalaah ikadaidzirwa nemusi weChishanu (munamato weJumu’ah), mhanyirai kundangariro yaAllah (Mharidzo nemunamato weJumu’ah), uye mosiya mabhizimusi (nemamwe mabasa). Ndizvo zvakanaka kwamuri kana muchiziva"
  62,10,"Zvino kana munamato weJumu’ah wapera, chipararirai nenyika, uye motsvaga makomborero aAllah (nekushanda), uye morangarira Allah zvakanyanya kuti mugobudirira"
  62,11,"Uye apo pavakaona bhizimusi kana mutambo (ngoma dzichiridzwa) vakamhanyira kwazviri, uye vakakusiya (Muhammad (SAW)) wakamira (uchiparidza). Iti: “Izvo zvina Allah zvakanaka kupfuura mutambo nemabhizimusi! Uye Allah ndivo mupi akanaka.”"
  63,1,"Kana vanyengedzi vakauya kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)) vanoti: “Tinopa uchapupu kuti zvirokwazvo uri mutumwa waAllah.” Uye Allah vanoziva kuti iwe uri mutumwa wavo, uye Allah vanopupura kuti zvirokwazvo vanyengedzi vanyepi"
  63,2,"Kupika kwavo vakakuita dziti. Naizvozvo ivo vanodzivisa (vanhu) munzira yaAllah. Zvirokwazvo, zvavaiita ndizvo zvakashata"
  63,3,"Nokuda kwekuti vakatenda ndokubva varega kutenda; naizvozvo moyo yavo yakavharwa, saka havanzwisisi"
  63,4,"Uye kana wakavatarisa, miviri yavo inokufadza; uye kana vakataura, unoteerera mashoko avo. Vakaita sokunge matanda akarongedzwa. Vanofunga kuti kuchema kwese kwakanangana naivo. Ndivo vavengi, saka vachenjerere. Dai Allah vakavashora! Sei vachiramba (vachisiya) nzira yakanaka"
  63,5,"Uye kana zvikanzi kwavari: “Huyai, kuitira kuti mutumwa waAllah agokukumbirirai ruregerero kuna Allah,” vanotendeudza misoro yavo, uyezve uchavaona vachitendeudza zviso zvavo apo ivo vachizvitutumadza"
  63,6,"Zvakangofanana kwavari kunyangwe (iwe Muhammad (SAW)) ukavakumbirira ruregerero kana kusavakumbirira ruregerero, Allah havambovaregereri. Zvirokwazvo, Allah havatungamiriri vanhu vasingateereri (vanotadza)"
  63,7,"Ndivo avo vanoti: “Musabetsere (nekuvapa zvipo) avo vane mutumwa waAllah (SAW) kusvikira vamusiya.” Uye kuna Allah ndiko kune hupfumi hwematenga nepanyika, asi vanyengedzi havanzwisisi"
  63,8,"Vanoti (vanyengedzi): “Kana tikadzokera kuMadinah, zvirokwazvo anoremekedzeka (Abdullah Ibn Ubayy Ibn Salool, mutungamiri wevanyengedzi kuMadinah) achadzinga munhu wepasi (Muhammad (SAW)).” Asi ruremekedzo nderwaAllah nemutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)), uye nekuvatendi, asi vanyengedzi havazvizivi"
  63,9,"Imi vanotenda! Musasiye hupfumi hwenyu nevana venyu zvichikutendeudzai kubva munzira yekurangarira Allah. Uye uyo anoita izvozvo, zvino ndivo vakarasikirwa"
  63,10,"Uye shandisai (kupa zvipo) kubva mune izvo zvatakakupai rufu rwusati rwasvikira umwe wenyu, kuti azoti: “Tenzi wangu! Dai mandipa mukana, kwekanguva kadiki, kuti ndipe Swadaqah (chipo) uye ndive uyo weavo vanoita zvakanaka (Hajj nemamwe mabasa akanaka)"
  63,11,Uye Allah havambopi mukana wekanguva kune munhu kana nguva yake (yekufa) yakwana. Uye Allah vanoziva zvose zvamunoita
  64,1,"Zvose zviri kumatenga nepanyika zvinorumbidza Allah. Humambo ndehwavo, uye rumbidzo nekutenda kwese ndekwavo, uye (Allah) vane simba pamusoro pezvinhu zvose"
  64,2,"Ndivo (Allah) vakakusikai, naizvozvo vamwe venyu havatendi uye vamwe venyu vanotenda. Uye Allah vanoona zvose zvamunoita"
  64,3,"Vakasika matenga nenyika muchokwadi, uye vakakuumbai ndokubva vaita maumbirwo enyu kuti ave akanaka. Uye kwavari ndiko kune magumo ekupedzisira"
  64,4,"(Allah) vanoziva zvose zviri kumatenga uye zvose zviri panyika, uye vanoziva zvamunovanza uye izvo zvamunoburitsa pachena. Uye Allah vanoziva zvose zviri muhana"
  64,5,"Hadzina kusvika kwamuri here nhau dzeavo vasina kutenda mumashure? Naizvozvo vakaravira magumo emabasa avo akaipa (kusatenda kwavo), uye vachawana mutongo unorwadza"
  64,6,"Nokuda kwekuti vatumwa vavo vakauya kwavari nezviratidzo zviri pachena, asi vakati: “Varume zvavo vangatitungamira?” Naizvozvo havana kutenda ndokubva vafuratira (chokwadi). Uye Allah vakanga vasingadi rubetsero rwavo. Uye Allah ndivo mupfumi (hapana chavanoda), muridzi werumbidzo dzese"
  64,7,"Avo vasingatendi vanofungidzira kuti havasi kuzomutswa. Iti (Muhammad(SAW)): Hongu! Ndinopika naTenzi vangu, kuti zvirokwazvo muchamutswa, uye muchazoudzwa izvo zvamaiita, uye izvozvo zviri nyore kuna Allah"
  64,8,"Naizvozvo tendai muna Allah nemutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)), uye nechiedza chatakatumira (Qur’aan iri). Uye Allah vanoziva zvose zvamunoita"
  64,9,"(Rangarirai) Zuva iro (Allah) vachakuunganidzai mose pazuva rekuungana. Ndiro richava zuva rokuwana nekurasikirwa (vatendi vachipinda Paradhiso uye vasingatendi vachipinda Gehena). Uye uyo anotenda muna Allah uye achiita mabasa akanaka, (Allah) vachamukanganwira zvitadzo zvake, uye vachamupinza mumapindu ayo anoerera nzizi pasi pawo, umo vachagara zvachose. Uku ndiko kubudirira kuhombe"
  64,10,"Uye avo vasingatendi (muhumwechete waAllah) uye vakaramba zviratidzo zvedu, vanhu vakadaro ndivo vagari vekumoto, umo vachagara zvachose. Uye magumo akadaro ndiwo akashata"
  64,11,"Hakuna matambudziko anouya asi nokuda kwemvumo yaAllah. Uye wese anotenda kuna Allah, vachatungamira moyo wake (kuchokwadi). Uye Allah vanoziva zvinhu zvose"
  64,12,"Uye teererai Allah uye moteerera mutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)); asi kana mukafuratira, zvino zvirokwazvo basa remutumwa wedu kuparidza shoko pachena"
  64,13,Allah! Laa ilaaha illaa Huwa (Hakuna chimwe chinamatwa kunze kwavo). Uye regai vatendi vavimbe naAllah (vega)
  64,14,"Imi vanotenda! Zvirokwazvo mukati mevakadzi venyu nevana venyu pane mhandu dzenyu (vanokudzivirirai kuteerera Allah), naizvozvo vachenjererei! Asi kana mukavasiya uye kuvakanganwira nekuvaregerera, zvirokwazvo Allah vanoregerera zvikuru, vane tsitsi zhinji"
  64,15,"Zvirokwazvo hupfumi hwenyu nevana venyu miedzo chete, apo Allah vane mubairo mukuru (Paradhiso)"
  64,16,"Naizvozvo ityai Allah sekukwanisa kwamunoita; inzwai uye teererai, uye shandisai (hupfumi hwenyu), zvakanaka kwamuri. Uye uyo anonunurwa kubva mukuomera kwemoyo wake, vanhu vakadaro ndivo vachabudirira"
  64,17,"Kana mukapa Allah chikwereti chakanaka (mochishandisa munzira yaAllah), vachachipeta kaviri kwamuri, uye vachakuregererai. Uye Allah vanotenda zvikuru, uye vane moyo munyoro"
  64,18,"Ndivo muzivi wezvose zvisingaoneki nezvinooneka, mukuru, vane hungwaru wese"
  65,1,"Iwe Muporofita (Muhammad (SAW))! Kana uchiramba vakadzi, varambe nenguva yavo yakatarwa (Iddah), uye verenga nguva (Iddah) yavo zvakanaka. Uye ityai Allah, Tenzi wenyu. Uye imi musavaburitsa mudzimba dzavo kana ivo kubuda pachavo, kusara kwekuti vaita chitadzo chiri pachena (hupombwe). Uye iyi ndiyo mirairo yaAllah. Uye uyo anotsaudzira mirairo yaAllah, zvirokwazvo anenge azvitadzira pachake. Hauzivi (iwe murambi wemukadzi wake) kuti pamwe Allah vanogona kuunza chiitiko chitsva mushure mezvo (kukudzorera mukadzi kana kwange kuri kurambana kwekutanga kana kwechipiri)"
  65,2,"Saka kana vapedza nguva yavo yakatarwa, vatorei mune zvakanaka, kana kuti mosiyana mune zvakanaka. Uye torai vapupuri vaviri vakanaka mukati menyu (maMuslim). Uye ivai munopika naAllah. Iyi ndiyo rairo kune uyo anotenda naAllah uye muzuva rekupedzisira. Uye uyo anotya Allah, vachamugadzirira nzira yekubuda nayo (mumatambudziko)"
  65,3,"Uye vachamupa raramo kubva kune zvaakanga asingafungiri. Uye uyo anovimba naAllah, zvino vanomuitira zvaanoda. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vachadzadzikisa chinangwa chavo. Zvirokwazvo Allah vakatara raramo pazvinhu zvose"
  65,4,"Uye avo vevakadzi venyu vasingachatsiki mwedzi, Iddah (Nguva yakatarwa) yavo kana musingagutsikani, imwedzi mitatu; uye avo vasingaendi kumwedzi (kutsika, nekuti vadiki, nguva yavo imwedzi mitatu, kunze keavo vakafirwa – Qur’aan 2: 234). Uye avo vakazvitakura (varambwa kana kuti vafirwa nevarume), nguva yavo kusvikira vabetserwa; uye uyo anotya Allah achiita mabasa avo, vachaita kuti hupenyu hwake huve nyore"
  65,5,"Iyi ndiyo mitemo yaAllah yavanodzikisa kwamuri; uye uyo anotya Allah achiita mabasa avo, vachamukanganwira zvitadzo zvake, uye vowedzera mubairo wake"
  65,6,"Vagarisei (vakadzi varambwa) pamunogarawo imi, sezvamunokwanisawo kuwana, uye musavarwadzise muchivashungurudza (kuti vagosiya misha yenyu). Asi kana vakazvitakura vachengetei kusvikira vasununguka pamuviri pavo. Uye kana vakayamwisa vana venyu, vapei mugove wavo, uye umwe wenyu ngaatambire yambiro yeumwe mune zvakanaka. Asi kana mukaomeserana, umwe mukadzi anokwanisa kuvayamwisira (baba vemwana)"
  65,7,Mupfumi ngaachengete zvichienderana nekuwana kwake; uye uyo anowana zvishoma ngaachengete zvichiendarana nezvaakapiwa naAllah. Allah havaisi musengwa pamunhu kudarika izvo zvavakamupa. Allah vachaunza rugare mushure mematambudziko
  65,8,"Uye maguta akawanda akatsaudzira mirairo yaTenzi wavo uye vatumwa vavo. Naizvozvo takawapa mutongo wakaoma (pasi rino), uye tichavaranga nemurango unorwadza chaizvo (muhupenyu unotevera)"
  65,9,"Naizvozvo vakaravira magumo emabasa avo akashata, uye magumo emabasa avo kurasikirwa (pasi rino nekudenga)"
  65,10,"Allah vakavagadzirira mutongo (unorwadza) wakaoma. Saka ityai Allah, imi vanonzwisisa, avo vanotenda! Zvirokwazvo Allah vadzikisa rangaridzo kwamuri (Qur’aan iri)"
  65,11,"(Vakatuma zvakare) mutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)) anokuverengerai zviratidzo zvaAllah (Qur’aan) zviri pachena, kuitira kuti vagoburitsa avo vanotenda neavo vanoita mabasa akanaka kubva murima (kusatenda) kuenda kune chiedza (Islaam). Uye uyo anotenda muna Allah uye achiita zvakanaka, (Allah) vachamupinza mubindu (Paradhiso) iro rine nzizi dzinoerera pasi paro kuti agogara imomo zvachose. Zvirokwazvo Allah vachamupa raramo yakanaka"
  65,12,"NdiAllah vakasika matenga manomwe uye nenyika yakafanana nawo (nomwe). Mutemo wavo unodzika pakati pavo (matenga nenyika), kuitira kuti muzive kuti Allah vane simba pamusoro pezvinhu zvose, uye zvirokwazvo kuti Allah vakakomberedza zvinhu zvose neruzivo rwavo"
  66,1,"Iwe muporofita! Nemhaka yei uchirambidza izvo zvakabvumidzwa kwauri naAllah, uchida kufadza vakadzi vako? Uye Allah vanoregerera, vane tsitsi"
  66,2,"Zvirokwazvo Allah vakatokukomekedzai (imi vanhu) kuti musunungure mhiko dzenyu. Uye Allah ndivo muchengeti wenyu, uye ndivo vane ruzivo, uye huchenjeri"
  66,3,"Uye (rangarirai) apo muporofita (Muhammad (SAW)) akavandudza mashoko kune umwe wevakadzi vake (Hafsah), ndokubva iye (mukadzi) azvitaura (kuna Aishah). Uye Allah vakaita kuti azvizive. Akamuudza chidimbu akasiya chidimbu. Zvino iye (muporofita) paakamuudza nezvazvo akati: “Ndiani akuudza izvozvo?” Iye akati: “Muzivi wazvose, ane ruzivo chairwo (Allah) ndiye andiudza.”"
  66,4,"Kana imi muri vaviri (Aishah naHafsah) mukasakumbira ruregerero kuna Allah, zvirokwazvo moyo yenyu inenge yabatana (kupikisa muporofita). Uye kana imi mukabetserana maringe naye (Kupikisana naye), zvirokwazvo Allah ndivo muchengeti wake, naGabriel, uye nevatendi vanoita zvakanaka; uye pamusoro pezvo, nengirozi dzinomubetsera"
  66,5,"Pamwe Tenzi vake, kana iye akakurambai, vanogona kumupa vamwe vakadzi vasiri imi, vari nani kudarika imi, maMuslim (vanozvipira kuna Allah), vatendi, vanoteerera (Allah), vanokumbira Allah ruregerero, vanonamata Allah nemoyo wese, vanotsanya (kana vakatama munzira yaAllah), vakamboroorwa uye mhandara"
  66,6,"Imi vanotenda! Zvinunurei imi nemhuri dzenyu kubva kumoto uyo huni dzacho vanhu nematombo, pamusoro pawo pane ngirozi dzakasimba dzakakasharara, dzisingaiti zvokusateerera Allah pane izvo zvaanodzikomekedza, uye dzinoita izvo zvinenge zvakomekedzerwa"
  66,7,Imi vasingatendi (mu Islaam)! Musape kana zvikonzero zuva ranhasi. Zvirokwazo murikupiwa mubairo wezvamakaita
  66,8,"Imi vanotenda! Kumbirai ruregerero kuna Allah zvakakwana! Pamwe Tenzi venyu vachakukanganwirai zvitadzo zvenyu, uye vachakupinzai mumapindu ayo pasi pawo pane nzizi dzinoyerera. Zuva iro Allah havazi kuzonyadzisa muporofita (Muhammad (SAW)) neavo vanotenda pamwe naye. Chiedza chavo chichimhanya mberi kwavo uye nekurudyi rwavo. Vachange vachiti: “Tenzi vedu! Zadzikisai chiedza chedu (kusvikira tayambuka As-Siraat (bhiriji riri pamusoro peGehena)) uye tiregerereiwo. Zvirokwazvo imi munokwanisa kuita zvose.”"
  66,9,"Iwe muporofita(Muhammad (SAW))! Shinga pamberi pevasingatendi nevanyengedzi, uye wokasharara kwavari; uye kuGehena ndiko kwavachagara, uye zvirokwazvo ndiwo magumo akashata"
  66,10,"Allah vanopa muenzaniso kune avo vasingatendi: Mukadzi waNowa nemukadzi waLoti. Vakanga vari pasi pevaranda vedu vaviri vatsvene asi vakavabhanya (varume vavo nekuramba chitendero chavo). Uye (Nowa naLoti) havana kukwanisa kuvadzivirira kubva kuna Allah, uye zvakanzi: “Pindai mumoto pamwe nevarikupinda mumoto!”"
  66,11,"Uye Allah vakapa mufananidzo kune avo vanotenda: Mukadzi waFarawo apo akati: “Tenzi vangu! Ndivakirei imba kwamuri muParadhiso, uye ndinunurei kubva kuna Farawo nemabasa ake, uyezve ndinunureiwo kubva kune vanhu vanotadza.”"
  66,12,"Uye naMaria mwanasikana waImraan uyo akachengetedza hunhu hwake. Uye takafemera maari (mumbasha dzaakange akapfeka) kubva mumweya wedu (Gabriel), uye akabvuma mashoko aTenzi vake (akatenda mushoko raAllah rekuti: “Ivapo!” – uye akavapo Jesu mwanakomana waMaria mutumwa waAllah), uye (akabvuma) mabhuku avo, uye akanga ari weavo vanoteerera (Allah)"
  67,1,Vakakomborerwa ndeavo mumaoko avo mune humambo wese. Uye vanokwanisa kuita zvinhu zvose (Vane masimba pamusoro pezvinhu zvose)
  67,2,"Avo vakasika rufu neupenyu kuti vave vanokuedzai kuti ndiani pakati penyu anemabasa akanaka. Uyezve ndivo samasimba ose, vane ruregerero rwese"
  67,3,Avo vakasika matenga manomwe rimwe pamusoro perimwe. Uye haukwanisi kuona chakakanganiswa pazvisikwa zvaane tsitsi dzose. Dzokororazve kutarisa! “Uri kuona here kutsemuka?”
  67,4,Nokudaro dzokorora zvakare kutarisa! Asi maziso ako anodzoka kwauri anenyadzi uyezve aneta
  67,5,"Uye zvirokwazvo, takashongedza denga repadyo nenyika nemarambi, uye takaaita marambi iwayo sezvombo kumaDhiyabhorosi, uye takavagadzirira marwadzo emoto unobvira"
  67,6,"Uye kune avo vasingatendi muna Tenzi vavo kune marwadzo eGehena, uye inzvimbo yokugara yakaipisisa"
  67,7,Apo pavachakandwa imomo mariri vachanzwa kukweva mariri (kwakasimba) apo parinenge richifema apo richibvira
  67,8,"Richasvika pakuda kuputsika nehasha. Nguva dzose chikwata pachinokandwa mariri, vachengetedzi varo vachabvunza: “Muyambiri haana kuuya kwamuri here?”"
  67,9,"Vachati: “Hongu, zvirokwazvo muyambiri akauya kwatiri, asi takamuramba tikati: ‘Allah havana kutumira pano pasi chimwe chinhu (mashoko), asi makarasika zvakanyanya.’”"
  67,10,"Uye vachati: “Dai takateerera kana kushandisa huchenjeri hwedu, taisazowanikwa muvanhu vekumoto!”"
  67,11,"Vachapupura zvitadzo zvavo. Nokudaro, ngavave kure vanhu vekumoto unobvira"
  67,12,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanotya Tenzi vavo vakavanzika, vachawana ruregerero uye mubairo mukuru"
  67,13,"Uye taurai mashoko enyu muchizevezeve kana kuwaburitsa pachena, zvirokwazvo (Allah) vanoziva zvakanyanya izvo zviri muzvipfuva (zvevanhu)"
  67,14,"Havangazivi here ivo vari ivo vakasika? Uye ndivo vane tsitsi dzose, muzivi wezvose"
  67,15,"Ndivo vakaita kuti nyika ive inozvipira kwamuri (muchifamba nokugara pamusoro payo uye nekuirima), nokudaro fambai munzira dzayo uye idyai zvokudya zvayo. Uye kwavari ndiko kune kumutswa kwenyu"
  67,16,"Munogadzikana here kuti avo vari pamusoro pematenga (Allah) havaiiti nyika kuti inyure nemi, apo paino dengenyeka"
  67,17,Kana kuti munogadzikana here kuti avo vari pamusoro pematenga havakwanisi kukutumirai kwamuri mhepo yakasimba? Nokudaro muchaziva kuti yambiro yangu yakaita sei
  67,18,"Uye zvirokwazvo avo vaiva kumashure kwenyu vakaramba, nokudaro kwakaipa sei kuvaramba kwangu (chirango changu)"
  67,19,"Havaoni here shiri pamusoro pavo dzichitambanudza mapapiro adzo, nekumadzosa mukati? Hapana anodzitakura kunze kwamuzvina tsitsi dzose. Zvirokwazvo, ndivo muoni wezvose"
  67,20,Ndiani kunze kune vane tsitsi dzose (Allah) vanokwanisa kuva masoja kwamuri kuti akubetserei? Vasingatendi hapana mavari kunze kwemumanyepo (munyengedzo)
  67,21,"Ndiani angakupai imi (zvokushandisa, kudya) kana vakabata zvokudya (vakasakupai) zvavo? Asi vanoenderera mberi nekuzvitutumadza, uye nekutiza (kubva pachokwadi)"
  67,22,"Ndizvo here kuti uyo anofamba nechiso chake asingaoni, akatungamirirwa zvakanyanya kudarika uyo anofamba akatwasuka munzira yakatwasuka (Islaam)"
  67,23,"Iti: “Ndivo vakakusikai, uye vakakupai nzeve uye maziso uye nemoyo. Asi munotenda zvishoma.”"
  67,24,"Iti: “Ndivo vakakusikai munyika, uye kwavari muchaunganidzwa (muhupenyu hwamangwana).”"
  67,25,"Vanoti: “Ndiriniko pachauya vimbiso iyi (zuva rekutongwa) kana muchitaura chokwadi?”"
  67,26,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Zvirokwazvo, ruzivo rwuna Allah voga, uye zvirokwazvo ndiri muyambiri ari pachena.”"
  67,27,"Asi pavachaona (marwadzo eZuva Rokutongwa) achiuya, zviso zveavo vasingatendi zvichachinja zvoita zvitema uye zvichanzi: “Iyi ndiyo (vimbiso) yamaidana!”"
  67,28,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Ndiudzei! Kana Allah vakandiparadza neavo vandinavo, kana kuti votiitira tsitsi, ndiani achabatsira vasingatendi kubva kumarwadzo akaoma?”"
  67,29,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Ndivo vane tsitsi dzose (Allah), kwavari tinotenda, uye tinovimba navo. Nokudaro muchaziva kuti ndiani akarasika zviri pachena.”"
  67,30,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Ndiudzei! Kana mvura yenyu yose ikanyura, ndiani achakupai mvura inoyerera?”"
  68,1,"Noon. (Mashoko aya ndemamwe ezvishamiso zveQur’aan, uye hapana anoziva zvaanoreva kunze kwaAllah). (Ndinopika) nechinyoreso uye (ndinopika) neizvo zvazvinonyora (ngirozi) (mumabhuku emabasa evanhu)"
  68,2,Iwe (Muhammad (SAW)) nenyasha dzaTenzi vako haupengi
  68,3,"Uye zvirokwazvo, uchawana (Muhammad (SAW)) mubairo usingagumi"
  68,4,"Uye zvirokwazvo, (iwe Muhammad (SAW) ndiwe une tsika dzepamusoro-soro"
  68,5,Uchawona uyezve vachawona
  68,6,Ndeupi pakati penyu asina kukwana (anopenga)
  68,7,"Zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vako ndivo muzivi mukuru weavo vakarasika kubva munzira, uye ndivo muzivi mukuru wevari pagwara"
  68,8,Nokudaro (iwe Muhammad (SAW)) usava unoteerera avo vanoramba (kutenda)
  68,9,Vanoshuvira kuti uve unonzwisisana navo (Panyaya dzechitendero). Nokudaro ivo vonzwisisana newe
  68,10,Uye (iwe Muhammad (SAW)) usava unoteerera wega wega ari Hallaaf Maheen (uyo anopika zvakanyanya achinyepa kana asina maturo)
  68,11,Uye mupomeri manyepo (munyeyi) anofamba nemakuhwa
  68,12,"Uye mudziviriri wezvakanaka, mutyori wemutemo, mutadzi mukuru"
  68,13,Uye ane utsinye pamusoro pazvo akazvarwa zvisiri pamutemo
  68,14,Anga akadaro nokuti anga aine hupfumi nevana
  68,15,"Kana ndima dzedu dzichiverengwa (Qur’aan) kwaari anoti: “Ingano dzevanhu vakare!”"
  68,16,Tichamuisa muchiso pamhuno
  68,17,"Zvirokwazvo, tinovaedza semaedzero atakaita vanhu vebindu, pavakapika kukohwa michero mangwanani"
  68,18,"Vasina kuti: “Kana Allah vakatitendera (Inshaa Allaah).”"
  68,19,Nokudaro wakapfuura napo muenzi (moto) kubva kuna Tenzi vako ivo vakarara
  68,20,Nokudaro (bindu) rakava dema sehusiku hutema
  68,21,Vakashevedzana mangwanani ngwanani
  68,22,"Vachiti: “Endai kubindu renyu, kana muchida kukohwa michero.”"
  68,23,Nokudaro vakasimuka vachitaura chinyararire nezwi riri pasi pasi
  68,24,Hakuna murombo achakupindirai mariri zuva ranhasi
  68,25,Uye vakaenda mangwanani nechinangwa chakasimba vachifunga kuti vane samba (rokunyima varombo michero)
  68,26,"Asi pavakariwona (bindu) vakati: “Zvirokwazvo, tarasika.”"
  68,27,"Vakati: “Pamwe zvirokwazvo tiri kudzvinyirirwa (pamuchero)!”"
  68,28,"Akanaka pakati pavo akati: “Handina kukuudzai here kuti sei musingati kana Allah vachida (Inshaa Allaah)?”"
  68,29,"Vakati: “Rumbidzo ngadzive kuna Tenzi vedu. Zvirokwazvo, tanga tiri vatadzi.”"
  68,30,Vakatendeukirana umwe neumwe pakati pavo vachipomerana
  68,31,"Vakati: “Marwadzo kwatiri. Zvirokwazvo, tanga tiri vatadzi.”"
  68,32,"“Tinovimba kuti Tenzi vedu vachatipa rinani (bindu) kupfuura iri. Zvechokwadi, tinotendeukira kuna Tenzi vedu (tichishuvira zvakanaka neruregerero nemubairo muhupenyu unotevera).”"
  68,33,"Aya ndiwo marwadzo, asi zvirokwazvo marwadzo ehupenyu hwamangwana makuru dai henyu maiziva"
  68,34,"Zvirokwazvo, kuvatsvene kune mapindu akanaka kuna Tenzi vavo"
  68,35,Tobata here maMuslim (vatendi) sevatadzi
  68,36,Mhaka yenyu ndeyeyi? Munotonga sei
  68,37,Kana kuti mune bhuku ramunodzidza mariri
  68,38,Kuti zvirokwazvo kwamuri mariri mune zvose zvamunosarudza
  68,39,"Kana kuti mune mhiko kubva kwatiri, kusvika pazuva rokutongwa, kuti kwamuri kuchava zvamunotonga"
  68,40,"Vabvunzei: “Ndiani pakati pavo achamira pazviri?”"
  68,41,“Kana kuti vane shamwari?” Nokudaro vasiyei vauye neshamwari dzavo kana vari pachokwadi
  68,42,"(Rangarirai) zuva iro gumbo (raAllah) richaburitswa pachena, uye vachadanwa kuti vapfugame (pamberi paAllah), asi vachakundikana (avo vasinganamati kana kuti avo vasinganamati nemoyo wese)"
  68,43,"Maziso avo akadzikiswa uye nyadzi dzakavavhara, nokuti zvirokwazvo vaidanwa kuti vapfugame vari vatano (asi vaitadza kudaro)"
  68,44,Saka ndisiyei neavo vanoramba Qur’aan iri. Tichavaranga zvishoma nezvishoma kubva kumativi avasingazivi
  68,45,"Uye ndichavapa nguva. Zvirokwazvo, hurongwa hwangu hwakakura"
  68,46,"Kana kuti (iwe Muhammad (SAW)) uri kuvabvunza mubhadharo, nokudaro vakaomerwa nezvikwereti"
  68,47,Kana kuti zvisingaonekwi zviri mumaoko avo kuti vazvinyore pasi
  68,48,"Saka mirira nekutsungirira hurongwa hwaTenzi vako, uye usava unoita semuvakidzani wehove, paakachema (kwatiri) aine kushushikana kwakanyanya"
  68,49,"Dai dzisiri nyasha dzaTenzi vake dzakamusvikira, aisiiwa (mudumbu mehove), asi akanorutsirwa (akakandwa) kumahombe kombe achipomerwa mhosva"
  68,50,Nokudaro Tenzi vake vakamusarudza uye vakamuita umwe wevatsvene
  68,51,"Uye zvirokwazvo, avo vasingatendi vanoposa zvishoma kukuita kuti utsvedze nekuda kwemaziso avo (aneruvengo) apo pavanonzwa yeuchidzo (Qur’aan), uye vanoti: “Zvirokwazvo, (Muhammad (SAW)) munhu anopenga!”"
  68,52,Asi hapana chiripo kunze kweyeuchidzo kuzvisikwa zvose (vanhu nemaJinn)
  69,1,Rechokwadi (Zuva rekutongwa)
  69,2,Chii chacho chechokwadi
  69,3,Uyezve chii chingakuite kuti uzive chechokwadi chacho kuti chii
  69,4,MaThamood nemaAad vakaramba Al-Qaari’ah (kusvika kwezuva rekutongwa)
  69,5,"Vari semaThamood, vakaparadzwa neruzha rwakasimba"
  69,6,"Uye vari semaAad, vakaparadzwa nemhepo yakasimba"
  69,7,"Iyo yavakatarirwa (naAllah) kwehusiku hunomwe nemazuva masere achitevedzana, zvokuti waiona varume vakarara sekunge ingwanda dzemiti yemadheti"
  69,8,Uri kuona here zvakasara zvavo
  69,9,"Uye Farawo, neavo vaiva mushure make, uye nemaguta (evanhu vaLoti) akatsindikirwa vaiita zvitadzo"
  69,10,"Uye havana kuteerera mutumwa waTenzi vavo, nokudaro vakavapa marwadzo akaomarara"
  69,11,"Zvirokwazo, apo mvura payakapfachukira (mvura yaNowa), takakutakurai (imi vanhu) muri pamusoro payo (mungarava yakagadzirwa naNowa)"
  69,12,"Kuti tiyiite (ngarava yaNowa) kuti ive chiyeuchidzo kwamuri, uye kuti nzeve inonzwisisa ive inonzwa"
  69,13,Nokudaro apo pacharidzwa hwamanda zvine simba kamwechete (Kuridza kwekutanga)
  69,14,"Uye nyika nemakomo zvichabviswa panzvimbo dzawo, uye zvoputswa kamwechete"
  69,15,Zuva iro chiitiko chikuru chichaiitika
  69,16,Uye denga richatsemuka. Pazuva iri richava nyore (kutsemuka) nekudambuka
  69,17,"Uye ngirozi dzichava mumativi arwo, uye ngirozi sere dzichange dzakatakura chigaro chehumambo hwaTenzi vako pamusoro padzo zuva iri"
  69,18,"Zuva iri muchaunzwa kuhutongi, (uye) hapana chakavanzika chenyu chichavigwa"
  69,19,"Nokudaro kune uyo achapihwa zvinyorwa zvake (bhuku) kuruoko rwerudyi achati: “Kuno! Verengai zvinyorwa zvangu!”"
  69,20,“Zvirokwazvo ini ndaitenda kuti ndichasangana nekutongwa kwangu!”
  69,21,Nokudaro achava muupenyu wemufaro
  69,22,Mubindu rakakwiridzirwa (Paradhiso)
  69,23,Michero iri bumbu iri pazasi uye pedyo
  69,24,Idyai nekunwa makadekara izvo zvamakatungamidza mazuva apfuura
  69,25,"Asi kune uyo achapihwa zvinyorwa zvake (bhuku) kuruoko rweruboshwe achati: “Dai hangu ndisina kupihwa chinyorwa changu!”"
  69,26,“Uyezve ndisingazive kuti mutongo wangu wakamira sei!”
  69,27,“Dai (rufu) rwakaita magumo angu!”
  69,28,“Hupfumi hwangu hauna kundidzivirira!”
  69,29,“Simba rangu (hutongi) hwabva pandiri!”
  69,30,"(Zvichanzi): “Mubatei momusunga!”"
  69,31,“Mobva mamukanda murimi remoto!”
  69,32,“Mobva mamusunga nengetani kureba kwadzo makumi manomwe ehonokono!”
  69,33,"Zvirokwazvo, anga asingatendi muna Allah mukuru wezvose"
  69,34,Uye aive asingakurudziri kuti varombo vapihwe chekudya
  69,35,Nokudaro haana shamwari yaanayo pano zuva ranhasi
  69,36,Kana chokudya kunze kwemvura dzezvironda (nemakwati)
  69,37,Hakuna anoadya kunze kwevatadzi (nevasingatendi)
  69,38,Uye ndinopika neizvo zvose zvamunoona
  69,39,Uyezve neizvo zvose zvamusingaoni
  69,40,"Kuti zvirokwazvo, ishoko remutumwa anoremekedzwa (Gabriel kana kuti Muhammad(SAW) raaunza kubva kuna Allah"
  69,41,Haasi mashoko anyanduri. Zvishoma ndizvo zvamunotenda
  69,42,Kana kuti mashoko emufemberi. Zvishoma ndizvo zvamunorangarira
  69,43,(Aya mashoko) akadzikiswa kubva kuna Tenzi vezvinhu zvese
  69,44,Dai (Muhammad (SAW)) aitaura mashoko enhema maererano nesu (Allah)
  69,45,Zvirokwazvo taimubata neruoko rwake rwerudyi
  69,46,Uye tomudambura tsinga dzake dzeupenyu
  69,47,Uye hapana mumwechete wenyu aikwanisa kutitadzisa kumuranga
  69,48,"Uye zvirokwazvo, iri (Qur’aan) murangaridzo wevatsvene (Qur’aan)"
  69,49,"Uye zvirokwazvo, tinoziva kuti pakati penyu pane vamwe vanoriramba"
  69,50,"Uye zvirokwazvo, iri (Qur’aan) richava chirwadzo kune avo vasingatendi (Pazuva rekutongwa)"
  69,51,"Uye zvirokwazvo, iri (Qur’aan) ichokwadi chiri pachena"
  69,52,"Nokudaro rumbidza zita raTenzi vako, mukuru mukuru wezvose"
  70,1,Mubvunzi akabvunza maererano nemutongo uchaitika
  70,2,"Kune vasingatendi, uyo usina anokwanisa kuudzivirira"
  70,3,"Kubva kuna Allah, Tenzi venzira dzekukwira"
  70,4,Ngirozi neRooh (Gabriel) dzinokwira kwavari pazuva rakaenzana nemakore zvuru makumi mashanu
  70,5,Naizvozvo tsungirira (Iwe Muhammad (SAW)) kutsungirira kwakanaka
  70,6,"Zvirokwazvo, vanouona (mutongo) seuri kure"
  70,7,Asi tinouona uri padyo
  70,8,Zuva iro denga richaita kunge marara emafuta akavira
  70,9,Uye makomo achaita kunge marara eshinda
  70,10,Uye hapana shamwari ichabvunza shamwari
  70,11,"Kunyangwe vachange vachionana (pazuva rokutongwa, asi hapana achataudza mumwe kana kubvunza). Mutadzi achashuvira kuzvibhadharira kubva kune marwadzo ezuva iroro nevana vake"
  70,12,Uye mukadzi wake nemukoma wake
  70,13,Uye nehama dzake dzaimuchengeta
  70,14,Uye nevese vari panyika kuti vamubatsire (vamununure)
  70,15,"Hazvigoneke! Zvirokwazvo, uchange uri moto wekuGehena"
  70,16,Uchitora (uchipisa) nyama yemusoro
  70,17,Uchisheedza uyo akafuratira nemusana wake nechiso chake (achisiya kutenda)
  70,18,Achiunganidza (hupfumi) uye achiuvanza (kubva mukupa munzira yaAllah)
  70,19,"Zvirokwazvo, munhu akasikwa ane kusatsungirira"
  70,20,Kana zvakaipa zvamubata anonyunyuta
  70,21,Uye kana zvakanaka zvamubata anonyima
  70,22,Kusara kweavo vanonamata (vanoita Swalaah)
  70,23,Avo vanobatisisa minamato yavo
  70,24,Uye avo muhupfumi hwavo munekodzero dzinozivikana
  70,25,Kune anokumbira uye anoshaya (anorasikirwa nehupfumi wake uye upenyu womuomera)
  70,26,Uye avo vanotenda muzuva rekutongwa
  70,27,Uye avo vanotya mutongo waTenzi vavo
  70,28,"Zvirokwazvo, mutongo waTenzi vavo ndeuyo usina ani nani angazvidzivirire"
  70,29,Uye avo vanochengetedza nhengo dzavo dzakavanzika (kubva muhupombwe nedzimwe nzira dzisiri pamutemo dzekuzvifadza nadzo)
  70,30,Kunze kwekuvakadzi vavo kana (varandakadzi) vari mumaoko avo ekurudyi. Kwavari hakuna kupomerwa mhosva
  70,31,"Asi uyo achatsvaka zvinopfurikidza ipapo, ndivo avo vatadzi (vanopfurikidza mwero)"
  70,32,Uye avo vanochengeta vimbiso dzavo nemhiko
  70,33,Uye avo vanomira zvakadzama pauchapupu hwavo
  70,34,Uye avo vanochengetedza zvakanaka minamato yavo (Swalaah)
  70,35,Vakadaro ndivo vachagara muParadhiso vachiremekedzwa
  70,36,"Naizvozvo sei avo vasingatendi vachimhanyira kukuteerera (Iwe Muhammad (SAW), kuti vave vanokuramba kana kukuseka"
  70,37,(Vakagara) Muzvikwata zvikwata kurudyi nekuruboshwe (kwako iwe Muhammad (SAW)
  70,38,Munhu wese pakati pavo anoshuvira here kupinda Paradhiso remafaro
  70,39,"Kwete! Zvirokwazvo, takavasika kubva kune izvo zvavanoziva"
  70,40,Naizvozvo ndinopika naTenzi vemabvazuva nemadokero kuti zvokwadi tinokwanisa
  70,41,Kuunza vamwe vari nani pachinzvimbo chavo; uye hapana vanotikunda
  70,42,Naizvozvo vasiyei vachitaura mukuzvikudza nekutamba kudzamara vasangana nezuva ravo iro ravakavimbiswa
  70,43,Zuva iro ravachabuda mumakuva nekuchimbidza sevari kumhanyira kune chinangwa
  70,44,"Maziso avo akatarisa pasi nekutya uye nekuzvininipisa, vakazara nekuzvidzikisira! Iro ndiro zuva ravakavimbiswa"
  71,1,"Zvirokwazvo, takatumira Nuh (Nowa) kuvanhu vake (tichiti): “Yambira vanhu vako mutongo unorwadza usati wauya kwavari.”"
  71,2,"(Nuh) akati: “Imi vanhu vangu! Zvirokwazvo, ndiri muyambiri ari pachena kwamuri.”"
  71,3,"“Munofanira kunamata Allah (vega), uye nekuvatya, uyezve mova munonditeerera.”"
  71,4,"“(Allah) vachakuregererai zvitadzo zvenyu uye vokusiyai kusvika panguva yakatarwa. Zvirokwazvo, kana nguva yaAllah yasvika, haigoni kunonotswa dai maiziva.”"
  71,5,"Nuh akati: “Tenzi vangu! Zvirokwazvo, inini ndasheedza vanhu vangu usiku nesikati.”"
  71,6,“Asi kusheedza kwangu hakuna kuvawedzera (kuvabatsira) kunze kwekutiza (chokwadi).”
  71,7,"“Uye zvirokwazvo, pese pandinovasheedza kuti muve munovaregerera, vanoisa minwe yavo munzeve dzavo, vozvifukidza nenguwo dzavo, uye vosimbirira (nekuramba kwavo), uye vozvitutumadza zvakanyanya.”"
  71,8,"“Uye zvirokwazvo, inini ndaivasheedza pachena (nezwi riri pamusoro).”"
  71,9,"“Uye zvirokwazvo, ndaivaparidzira pachena, uye ndaivakumbira pakahwanda.”"
  71,10,"“Naizvozvo ndikati (kwavari): ‘Kumbirai ruregerero kuna Tenzi venyu. Zvirokwazvo, vazere neruregerero.’"
  71,11,‘Vachatumira mvura zhinji kwamuri.’
  71,12,"‘Uye vanokuwedzerai hupfumi uye nevana, uye vanokupai minda uye vanokupai nzizi.’”"
  71,13,Dambudziko renyu nderei? Hamushuviri mubairo kubva kuna Allah
  71,14,"Uye zvirokwazvo, vakakusikai nezvidanho (Nutfah, Alaqah, uye Mudghah – Qur’aan)"
  71,15,Hamuoni here kuti Allah vakasika sei matenga manomwe rimwe pamusoro perimwe
  71,16,"Uye vakasika mwedzi sechiedza pakati pawo (matenga), uye vakasika zuva serambi"
  71,17,Uyezve Allah vakakusikai kubva kuivhu
  71,18,"Naizvozvo vachakudzorerai ikoko (kuivhu), uye vozokumutsai zvakare (pazuva rekutongwa)"
  71,19,Uye Allah vakakusikirai nyika yakafara
  71,20,Kuti mufambe mairi munzira dzakafara
  71,21,"Nuh (Nowa) akati: “Tenzi vangu! (Vanhu ava) vakaramba kunditeerera, uye vakatevera uyo hupfumi nevana vake hazvina zvazvinomuwedzera kunze kwekurasikirwa.”"
  71,22,“Uyezve vakaronga kuronga kukuru.”
  71,23,"“Uyezve vakati (kune vamwe vavo): ‘Hamufanirwi kusiya vanamwari venyu, kana kuti musiye Wadd, kana kuti Suwaa, kana kuti Yaghooth, kana kuti Yauooq, kana kuti Nasr (Aya mazita ezviumbwa zvavainamata).’”"
  71,24,"“Uye zvirokwazvo vakatsaudza vakawanda, uye (Allah): ‘Musawedzere avo vanoita zvakaipa kunze kwekurasika.’”"
  71,25,"Nekuda kwezvitadzo zvavo vakanyudzwa (mumvura), vakaitwa kuti vapinde mumoto. Uyezve havana kuwana mubatsiri kunze kwaAllah"
  71,26,"Uye Nuh (Nowa) akati: “Tenzi vangu! Musava munosiya kana mumwechete wevasingatendi panyika (Paradzai vese)!”"
  71,27,"“Kana mukavasiya, vachatsaudza varanda venyu, uye havazombobereki (vana) asi vasingatendi.”"
  71,28,"“Tenzi vangu! Ndiregererei inini, uye nevabereki vangu, uye neuyo anopinda mumba mangu ari mutendi, uye nevatendi vose varume nevakadzi. Uye kune avo vasingatendi (vaiiti vezvakaipa), musava munovawedzera asi mukuparadzwa.”"
  72,1,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Zvadzikiswa kwandiri kuti chikwata chemaJinn (Zvisikwa zvakasikwa nemoto) chaiteerera (Qur’aan iri). Vakati: ‘Zvirokwazvo, tanzwa maverengero akanaka anoshamisa (Qur’aan)!’"
  72,2,"‘Rinotungamirira mugwara rakanaka, uye tinotenda mariri, uye hatimbosanganise (pakunamata) chipi zvacho naTenzi vedu (Allah).’"
  72,3,"‘Uye uMambo waTenzi vedu ndewe pamusoro, havana kutora mukadzi kana mwanakomana.’"
  72,4,‘Uye vasina kukwana pakati pedu vaitaura pamusoro paAllah manyepo makuru.’
  72,5,‘Uye zvirokwazvo taifunga kuti vanhu nemaJinn (Zvisikwa zvakasikwa nemoto) havatauri manyepo pamusoro paAllah.’
  72,6,"‘Uye zvirokwazvo, mukati mevanhu maive nevarume vaitsvaga rudziviriro kubva kuvarume pakati pemaJinn, asi vakavawedzera mukutadza nekupfurikidza mwero.’"
  72,7,‘Uye vaifunga semafungiro enyu kuti Allah havazombotumire mutumwa (kuvanhu nemaJinn).’
  72,8,‘Uye takati tisvike kudenga asi tikawana kwakazara nevachengetedzi vakasimba uye nemoto unobvira.’
  72,9,"‘Uye zvirokwazvo, taiwanzogara ikoko muzvikwata, kuti tinzwe, asi upi zvake anoteerera izvezvi anowana moto uchibvira wakamugaririra.’"
  72,10,"‘Uye hatizivi kana chakaipa chashuvirwa kune avo vari panyika, kana kuti Tenzi wavo vanovashuvira nzira yakanaka.’"
  72,11,"‘Pakati pedu pane vamwe vanoita zvakanaka, uye vamwe vanopikisa. Tiri mapoka ane nzira dzakasiyana.’"
  72,12,"‘Uye tinofunga kuti hatipukunyiki (mumarwadzo) kubva kuna Allah panyika, kana kupukunyuka kwavari nekutiza.’"
  72,13,"‘Uye zvirokwazvo, patakanzwa nhungamiro (Qur’aan) takatenda mairi, uye ani nani anotenda kuna Tenzi vake haazombotyi, kana kudzikisirwa mugove wemabasa ake akanaka, kana kuwedzerwa mutongo wezvitadzo zvake.’"
  72,14,"Uye pakati pedu vamwe maMuslim (mushure mekunzwa Qur’aan), uye pakati pedu vamwe havasi vatendi. Uye ani nani anopinda muchitendero cheIslaam, vakadaro ndivo vatsvaga nzira yakanaka.”"
  72,15,"Uye kune avo vasingatendi, vachange vari huni dzemoto wekuGehena"
  72,16,"Dai (vasingatendi) vakatenda muna Allah, uye vakafamba munzira yakanaka (Islaam), chokwadi tingadai takavadzikisira mvura muhuwandu"
  72,17,"Kuti tive tinovaedza naizvozvo. Uye ani nani anobva muyeuchidzo yaTenzi vake (Qur’aan iri), vachamupinza mumarwadzo makuru (Gehena)"
  72,18,"Uye nzvimbo dzekunamatira (maMasjid) ndedzaAllah, saka musava munonamata ani nani naAllah"
  72,19,"Uye muranda waAllah (Muhammad (SAW)) paakamira achivanamata (Allah) mumunamato, (MaJinn) vakamuunganira sekunge vanga vakanamatirana (kuti vanzwe)"
  72,20,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Ndinonamata Tenzi vangu chete, uye handisanganisi vamwe vanhu naivo.”"
  72,21,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Harisi simba rangu kukonzera marwadzo kwamuri, kana kukuunzai kunzira yakanaka.”"
  72,22,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Hakuna anondidzivirira kubva mumarwadzo aAllah (kana ndikasavateerera), kana kuwana pekuhwanda kunze kwavari.”"
  72,23,"“(Changu chete) asi kuparidza chokwadi kubva kunaAllah nemashoko avo. Uye ani nani asingatendi muna Allah uye nemutumwa wavo, zvirokwazvo, kwaari kune moto wekuGehena achagara imomo zvachose.”"
  72,24,"Kusvikira, vaona izvo zvavakavimbiswa, vachaziva kuti ndeupi akarenda mumubatsiri uye muhushoma muuhwandu"
  72,25,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Handizivi kuti chamakavimbiswa chiri pedyo kana kuti Tenzi vangu achachiita kure.”"
  72,26,"“(Ivo pachavo) vazivi veizvo zvisingaonekwi, uye havazaruriri (havatumiri) ani zvake zvisingaonekwi.”"
  72,27,"“Kunze kune uyo vakamusarudza kuva mutumwa, uye zvirokwazvo, vanogadzira chikwata chevatarisi (ngirozi) kuti dzifore mushure uye nemberi kwake.”"
  72,28,"“Kusvikira vaona kuti vaparidzira mashoko aTenzi wavo (Allah). Uye ivo (Allah) vanoziva zvose zvavanazvo, uye ivo (Allah) vanoziva huwandu wezvinhu zvese.”"
  73,1,Iwe wakaputirwa mumachira (Mutumwa Muhammad (SAW)
  73,2,Muka (mira) unamate usiku hwose kusiya kwekachidimbu (kehusiku) Tahajjud
  73,3,Chidimbu chepakati nepakati kana chishoma pane izvozvo
  73,4,"Kana kuti owedzera zvishoma (kubva pakati nepakati). Uyezve verenga Qur’aan (uchisheedzesa) zvinyoro-nyoro, (nezwi rinoyevedza) uchinyatsokukwenenzvera"
  73,5,"Muzvirokwazvo, tichaburutsa kwauri mashoko ane hudzamu (huremu) (mitemo, zvinhu zvakakomekedzwa)"
  73,6,"Zvirokwazvo, kumuka pakati pehusiku (uchinamata/uchimukira munamato weTahajjud) chinhu chakaoma chinonetsa, uye chinobatsira zvikuru (chiguro), uye chakanaka pakuzvichengetedza, uye ndicho chinonyatsoita kuti munhu anyatsonzwisisa shoko (raAllah)"
  73,7,"Zvirokwazvo, muswero wezuva unenge uine mabasa (akasiyana siyana akawanda) emazuva ose"
  73,8,Uyezve rangarira zita raTenzi vako (Allah) wova unozvipira kwavari nemoyo wese (wakaperera)
  73,9,"(Ndivo woga) Tenzi vemabvazuva nemadokero (nemavirira); Laa ilaaha illaa Huwa (Hakuna mumwe anofanirwa kunamatwa kunze kwavo – Allah). Naizvozvo, tora ivo voga semuriritiri (vanokwanisa kumiririra mumabasa ako Muhammad (SAW)"
  73,10,"Uye, iwe chitsungirira (Muhammad (SAW)) mune zvose zvavanotaura (maKuffaar), uye wogara kure navo mune zvakanaka (usinganetsane navo)"
  73,11,"Uyezve chindisiya (ini Allah) ndega ndipedzerane neavo maKuffaar (avo vanoramba zviratidzo zvangu), avo vane zvakanyatsonaka zveupenyu (hupfumi). Zvekare (iwe Muhammad (SAW)) chimbovasiya kwechinguvana"
  73,12,"Muzvirokwazvo, tine ngetani (dzekuvasungisa), uyezve nemoto (unopisa samare)"
  73,13,"Uyezve (tine) chikafu chinokachidza, zvekare nemutongo unorwadza"
  73,14,"Pazuva iro pachandengendeka nyika nemakomo (zvine ukasha mukati), zvekare makomo achave dutu rejecha rakamwararidzwa"
  73,15,"Zvirokwazvo, tave tinokutumirai Mutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)) semupupuri kwamuri, sekutumira mutumwa (Musa kwatakaita) kuna Farawo"
  73,16,Naizvozvo Farawo haana kuteerera Mutumwa (Musa (AS)); naizvozvo takamuranga (takamutora) nemurango (mukuru) wakaoma
  73,17,"Ko mungadzivirira sei murango kana imi musingatende, pazuva iro (zuva rokutongwa) richaita kuti vana vadiki vamere imvi (kuva nebvudzi rebvumu)"
  73,18,(Zuva iro) denga parichatsemuka. Muzvokwadi chivimbiso chavo (Allah) chichazadzikiswa
  73,19,"Muzvirokwazvo, iyi iyeuchidzo; naizvozvo uyo anenge ada musiyei atore nzira yekuna Tenzi vake"
  73,20,"Zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vako (Allah) vanozviziva kuti unomira (uchinamata usiku) neboka revatevedzeri vako zvishomanana pane zvidimbu zviviri kubva muzvitatu (2/3) dzeusiku, kana kuti chidimbu kubva muzviviri (1/2) dzeusiku, kana kuti chidimbu chimwe kubva muzvitatu (1/3) dzeusiku. Uyezve Allah vanoyera (vanopima) husiku nemasikati. (Allah) vanozviziva kuti haukwanise kunamata husiku hwose, naizvozvo vave vanokuregerera (netsitsi). Naizvozvo chiverenga Qur’aan (zvaunoona) zviri nyore kwauri. (Allah) vanozviziva kuti pakati penyu pane varwere, uyezve vamwe ndivo vanofamba munyika vachitsvaga (makomborero) aAllah, vamwewo ndivo vanorwa munzira yaAllah. Saka naizvozvo verengai kubva mariri (Qur’aan) zvamunokwanisa, zvekare ivai munoita Swalaah (Munamato), mopa Zakaah (Zvipo), mokweretesa Allah kwereteso yakanaka (Moita mabasa akanaka vachakupai mibairo). Uyezve, chingave chii zvacho chamunoita chanaka (Nawaafil Swalaah, Saum, Zakaat, Hajj, Umrah nezvakadarowo), muzvirokwazvo muchazviwana zvina Allah zvitori nani kana kutodarika ipapo pamubairo. Zvekare ivai munokumbira ruregerero kubva kuna Allah. Zvirokwazvo, Allah ndivo muregereri, vane ngoni zhinji"
  74,1,Iwe (Muhammad (SAW)) akaputirirwa mumachira
  74,2,Muka uyambire
  74,3,Uyezve kudza Tenzi vako (Allah)
  74,4,Zvekare iva unochenesa nhumbi dzako
  74,5,Uyezve iva unoswedera kure ne Ar-Rujz (zvidhori/zviumbwa)
  74,6,Zvekare usave unopa chinhu kuti uwane zvakawanda (kana kuti usave unoona kuita mabasa kwaunoita semutsa kuna Allah)
  74,7,Uyezve iva unotsungira kuti ufadze Tenzi vako (Allah)
  74,8,Pedzezvo kana hwamanda ichinge yaridzwa (kuridzwa kwehwamanda kwechipiri)
  74,9,Muzvokwadi zuva iroro rinenge riri zuva rakaoma
  74,10,Risiri nyore (zvamuchose) kumaKuffaar (vasingatendi)
  74,11,Chindisiya (ini Allah) (ndipedzerane neuyo) wandakasika ari oga (asina hupfumi kana vana nezvimwewo zvakadaro uyo anonzi Al-Waleed bin Al-Mugheerah Al-Makhzoomi)
  74,12,Uyezve pedzezvo (ini Allah) ndakamupa hupfumi uzhinji
  74,13,Uyezve nevana kuti vave padivi pake
  74,14,Zvekare (ini Allah) ndakaita kuti hupenyu huve hunoendeka zvakanaka (nekufara) kwaari
  74,15,Pedzezvo anoshuwira kuti ndiwedzere
  74,16,"Kwete! Muzvirokwazvo akanga achipikisa maAayaat edu (zvidzidzo, ndima, nezviratidzo)"
  74,17,Ndicharovekedza kwaari (kuti akwire gomo rinotsvedza muJahannam rinonzi Sa’uood kana) kuti awane mutongo wakaoma
  74,18,"Muzvirokwazvo, akadzamisa pfungwa mukufunga pamwe nekuronga"
  74,19,"Naizvozvo siyai arengerwe (apihwe rushambwa), hazvina basa marongero (mazengezero) anoita"
  74,20,"Pedzezvo ngaarengerwe zvekare (ngaapihwe rushambwa zvekare), hazvina basa marongero (mazengezero) anoita"
  74,21,Pedzezvo akafunga
  74,22,"Pedzezvo akafinyama, uye ndokutaridza kukanganisirwa"
  74,23,"Pedzezvo ndokucheuka shure (kufuratira), uye achizvikudza"
  74,24,"Ndokuti: “Izvi hazvisi chimwe chinhu kunze kwehuroyi uyo wekare.”"
  74,25,“Izvi hazvisi chimwe chinhu kunze kweshoko (izwi) remunhu!”
  74,26,(Ini Allah) ndichave ndinomukanda (mugomba remoto) muGehena
  74,27,Uye chiiko chichakuzivisa nezveGehena
  74,28,Haritombosiyi (mutadzi wese) kana kuregera (kana nechinhu chipi zvacho chisina kutsva)
  74,29,Richingopisa nekusvibisa makanda (evanhu)
  74,30,Pamusoro paro pane ngirozi (19) gumi nepfumbamwe (Ngirozi dzinochengetedza Jahannam)
  74,31,"Uye hatina kuisa vamwe sevachengetedzi veJahannam kunze kwengirozi. Uye takave tinotara huwandu hwadzo (19) semuyedzo kune (avo) vasingatendi, nechinangwa chokuti avo vakapuhwa Bhuku (Gwaro) (maJudha nemaKristu) vave nechokwadi nazvo (kuti Qur’aan irori ndere chokwadi uyezve rine chokwadi chose nekuwirirana neMabhuku (Taurah, Injeel) panyaya dzouwandu wengirozi dziri pamusoro peJahannam (19)), uye kuti vatendi vave vanowedzera kutenda (Iymaan) kwavo, zvekare vanhu veBhuku pamwe nevatendi kuti vasave nokusagutsikana, uye kuti avo vane chirwere (chehunyengedzi) mumoyo yavo pamwe neavo vasingatendi vataure kuti: “Ko Allah vanodeiko kuburikidza nemuenzaniso uyu?” Saizvozvo Allah vanorasisa uyo wavanoda pamwe nekutungamirira wavanoda (mugwara rakaswatuka). Uye hakuna anoziva mauto aTenzi vako (Allah) kunze kwavo chete. Zvekare (Gehena iri) hapana zvariri kunze kwekuti (iyambiro) iyeuchidzo kune vanhu"
  74,32,Kwete! (Ndinopika) nemwedzi
  74,33,Uyezve (ndinopika) nehusiku kana hwavakuenda
  74,34,Uyezve (ndinopika) nemambakwedza kana kochena
  74,35,"Zvirokwazvo, (Gehena, kana kuti kuramba kwavo Muhammad (SAW), kana kuti zuva rekutongwa) chimwe chezviratidzo zvikuru kuru"
  74,36,Iyambiro kuvanhu
  74,37,"Kune mumwe pakati penyu anenge ada kuenda mberi (achiita mabasa akanaka), kana kusaririra (achiita mabasa akaipa)"
  74,38,Munhu wose atori chitsiidzo kune zvose zvaaiwana
  74,39,Kunze kweavo vari kurudyi (vaiti/vabati vemabasa akanaka)
  74,40,Mumapindu (muParadhiso) vachabvunzana
  74,41,"Maererano nemaMujrimoon (avo vasingatendi, vanonamata zvinhu zvizhinji, vanoita mabasa akaipa). (Uye vachati kwavari)"
  74,42,“Ko chiiko chaita kuti mupinde muGehena?”
  74,43,"Vachati: “Takanga tisiri pamwe nemaMuswalleen (avo vanonamata).”"
  74,44,“Uyezve takanga tisingapewo chikafu kune avo vanotambura.”
  74,45,“Zvekare taitaura manyepo (zvose zvakavengwa naAllah) tiri pamwe neavo vanotaura zvisina maturo (basa).”
  74,46,“Uyezve tairamba (kuti kune) zuva rokutongwa (remugove/remubairo).”
  74,47,“Kusvikira muzvokwadi auya (rufu).”
  74,48,Naizvozvo hapana reverero yevarevereri ichavabatsira
  74,49,Pedzezvo chiiko chinovanetsa (avo vasingatendi) zvokusvika pakufuratira yeuchidzo
  74,50,Sekunge vari madhongi emusango (ari kutya)
  74,51,(MaDhongi) arikutiza muvhimi (kana kuti shumba kana kuti mhuka inowadya)
  74,52,"Asi mumwe nemumwe wavo anoda kuti apihwe mapeji (mashizha) akawaridzwa (achibva kuna Allah akanyorwa kunzi Islaam ndicho chitendero chechokwadi, uye Muhammad (SAW) auya nechokwadi kubva kuna Allah, Tenzi vematenga nenyika"
  74,53,Kwete! Havatombotye Aakhirah (hupenyu hwemangwana – mirango yaAllah)
  74,54,"Kwete! Muzvirokwazvo, (Qur’aan) iri iyeuchidzo"
  74,55,"Naizvozvo uyo anenge ada (musiyei ariverenge), uyezve ave anotambira chirayiro (kubva kwariri)"
  74,56,"Uye havatombotambira rairo kunze kwekuti Allah vada. Ivo (Allah) ndivo voga vanokodzera kityiwa nevanhu (uyezve kunamatwa, uye vanhu havafanire kuvasanganisa nezvimwe zvinhu pakuvanamata), uyezve ndivo voga vanoregerera zvitadzo"
  75,1,Ndinopika nezuva rokumutswa
  75,2,Zvekare ndinopika nemoyo unozvipomera mhaka (mutendi)
  75,3,Asi munhu (asingatendi) anofunga kuti hatizounganidza mapfupa ake
  75,4,Hongu. Tinokwanisa kuunganidza minwe yake zvakarongeka
  75,5,Asi munhu (anoramba chiito chokumutswa kubva kuvafi nekutongwa saka naizvozvo) anoshuwira kuramba achiita zvitadzo
  75,6,"Anobvunza: “Zuva iri rokumutswa richave rinhiko?”"
  75,7,Saka naizvozvo apo maziso paachabatwa nechipapadzungu (paachavhiringidzwa)
  75,8,Zvekare mwedzi pauchadzikatidza (uchaora)
  75,9,Uye apo pachabatanidzwa zuva nemwedzi (pazvichapindana)
  75,10,"Pazuva iroro munhu achati: “Ko ndekupiko kwekutizira?”"
  75,11,Kwete! Hakuna kwekuhwanda
  75,12,Kuna Tenzi vako pazuva iroro ndiko kuchange kune nzvimbo yekuzororera
  75,13,"Pazuva iroro munhu acharondedzerwa (achaudzwa) maererano nezvaakaita zvaakatungamidza (zvakanaka nezvakaipa), zvekare nezvaakasiya (zvakanaka nezvakaipa)"
  75,14,"Asi munhu achazvipupurira (sezvo nhengo dzomuviri wake (maoko, makumbo, ganda nezvimwewo) zvichitaura maererano nemabasa ake"
  75,15,Nyangwe zvazvo anenge achipa maboterero (mirangariro)
  75,16,Usatombofambisa rurimi rwako hako nayo (Qur’aan iwe Muhammad (SAW)) kuti rikurumidze kuuya kwauri
  75,17,"Zvirokwazvo, zviri kwatiri isusu zvekuriunganidza uyezve nekukupa (iwe Muhammad (SAW)) masimba ekuriverenga (Qur’aan)"
  75,18,Naizvozvo kana tichinge takuverengera (Qur’aan iwe Muhammad (SAW)) kuburikidza naJibreel (Gabriel (AS)) saka tevedzera maverengero aro (Qur’aan)
  75,19,"Pedzezvo, zvirokwazvo zviri kwatiri isu kuti tinyatsoritsetsenura (tiri jekese) kwauri"
  75,20,"Kwete! (Semafungiro enyu, kuti imi (vanhu) hamuzomutswe kubva kuvafi uyezve nekutongwa pamwe nekupihwa mibairo yemabasa enyu), asi kuti munoda hupenyu hwepasi pano"
  75,21,"Zvekare, munokanganwa hupenyu hwekuAakhirah (hwamangwana)"
  75,22,Zvimwe zviso pazuva iroro zvichange zviri Naadirah (Zvichipenyerera)
  75,23,Zvakatarisa kuna Tenzi vazvo (zviso izvozvo)
  75,24,"Zvekare zvimwe zviso pazuva iroro zvichange zviri Baasirah (zvakafinyama, zvakatsamwa kwete zvokutamba zviya, zvakasvibirira)"
  75,25,(Zviso izvi) zvichange zvichifunga kuti nhamo yavakuda kuzviwira
  75,26,Kwete! Kana (mweya womunhu) uchinge wasvika pabondo (mapfupa ari pedyo nehuro)
  75,27,"Zvekare zvichanzi: “Ndiani angamurape (uyezve nekumubatsira kubva kurufu)?”"
  75,28,Uyezve iye (uyo avakuda kufa) achatenda kuti yave nguva yekusiyana (rufu)
  75,29,Zvekare rimwe gumbo richabatanidzwa nerimwe (aputirwa mumicheka yeKAFAN)
  75,30,"Pazuva iroro svudzo (kutinhirwa kwevanhu vese vakananga kuna Allah) inenge iri, kuna Tenzi vako (Allah)"
  75,31,"Saka naizvozvo, (uyo asingatendi) haana kutenda (muQur’aan neshoko raMuhammad (SAW)) kana kunamata"
  75,32,Asi akaramba (Qur’aan neshoko raMuhammad (SAW)) pamwe nekufuratira
  75,33,Pedzezvo ndokuenda kune mhuri yake achizvikudza (achizvida chose)
  75,34,Yambiro kwauri (iwe usingatendi)! Uyezve (zvekare) yambiro kwauri
  75,35,Pedzezvo yambiro kwauri (iwe usingatendi)! Uyezve (zvekare) yambiro kwauri
  75,36,Asi munhu anofunga here kuti achangosiiwa (asina kutongeswa kana kuti asina kurangwa pamwe nekupihwa mibairo yake yezvaaiita naTenzi vake Allah)
  75,37,Akanga asiri Nutfah (urete hwababa naamai) here hwehurete hwakaburitswa
  75,38,Pedzezvo akava Alaqah (kagovo – karopa kakagwamba). Naizvozvo (Allah) ndokuzomuumba nekumunatsurudza zvakaenzana
  75,39,"Naizvozvo kubva maari (Allah) vakagadzira zvisikwa zviviri (mhando mbiri), chirume nechikadzi"
  75,40,Havasirivo here (Allah avo) vane simba rokupa hupenyu kuvafi? (Hongu! Allah vane masimba ekuita zvose)
  76,1,Paiva pasina here nguva apo munhu aive chimwe chinhu chaisataurwa
  76,2,"Zvirokwazvo, takasika munhu kubva kuNutfah yakazangana (mvura yepabonde yemurume nemukadzi) kuti tive tino muedza. Saka takamuita kuti ave munzwi nemuoni"
  76,3,"Zvirokwazvo, takamuratidza gwara, kunyangwe akave anotenda kana kusatenda"
  76,4,"Zvirokwazvo, takave tinogadzirira vasingatendi ngetani dzesimbi, zvichangadzo zvesimbi, uye nemoto unovirima"
  76,5,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanotenda vachave vanomwa komichi (yewaini) yakasanganiswa ne (mvura kubva muchitubu chinonzi) Kaafoor"
  76,6,"Chitubu icho varanda vaAllah vachamwa, vochiita kuti chipopome zvakanyanya"
  76,7,"Ndivo (avo) vanozadzikisa mhiko (dzavo), uye vanotya zuva zvakaipa zvaro zvichafararira"
  76,8,"Uye vanopa chikafu, kunyangwe vanerudo nacho (kana kuti vachiratidza rudo kwavari Allah), kune anoshaya, nherera, uye mubatwi"
  76,9,"(Vachiti): “Tinokudyisai kuri kutsvaga Nyasha dzaAllah chete. Hatidi mubairo kana kutendwa kubva kwamuri.”"
  76,10,"“Zvirokwazvo, tinotya kubva kuna Tenzi vedu iro zuva rakaoma uye kushaiwa, richaita kuti zviso zvityise (kubva mukusarida).”"
  76,11,"Naizvozvo Allah vakave vanova nunura kubva muhuipi wezuva racho, uye vakave vanovapa Nadrah (chiedza cherunako) uye mufaro"
  76,12,"Uye mubairo wavo uchave Paradhiso, uye magamenzi esiriki, nemhaka yokuti vaiva vanotsungirira"
  76,13,"Vakatsamhira imomo pamatendamo akakwirira. Havaoni varimo kupisa kwakanyanya, kana kutonhorwa kwakanyanya (sezvo kuParadhiso hakuna zuva kana mwedzi)"
  76,14,"Uye mvuri wemo unenge uri pavari, uye nemapazi emichero achava anorembera pedyo navo"
  76,15,Uye pakati pavo pachava pano fambiswa midziyo yesirivha uye nemakomichi egirazi
  76,16,"Girazi rakachena, rakagadzirwa nesirivha. Vachave vanosarudza huwandu hwawo (nekuda kwavo)"
  76,17,Uye vachapiwa kuti vamwe komichi (yewaini) yakazanganiswa neZanjabeel (Tsangamidzi)
  76,18,Kune chitubu imomo chinonzi Salsabeel
  76,19,"Uye pavari pachave nemajaya (vachiva pakurira) vaine hujaya husingaperi. Kana ukavaona, unofunga kuti matombo akakosha (mapera) akafararira"
  76,20,"Uye ukatarisa imomo (muParadhiso), unoona zvakanaka (izvo zvisingafungirike), uye nenyika huru"
  76,21,"Pavari vanenge vaine hanzu dzegirini dzakapfava dzakanaka uye siriki yakakora. Vanenge vakashongedzwa nejati dzesirivha, uye Tenzi vavo vachavapa kumwa kwakachena"
  76,22,"(Uye zvichanzi kwavari): “Zvirokwazvo mubairo ndewenyu, uye mabasa enyu atambirwa.”"
  76,23,"Zvirokwazvo, tisu takatumidza (Qur’aan) kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)) muzvidimbu"
  76,24,"Saka iva unotsungirira kumirairo ya Tenzi vako, uye usave unoteerera mutadzi kana asingatendi kubva mavari"
  76,25,"Uye rangarira zita raTenzi vako mangwanani uye nemasikati (nekuita minamato yeFajr, Dhuhr neAsr)"
  76,26,"Uye nguva yeusiku, pfugama kwavari (nekuita munamato weMaghrib neIsha), uye varumbidze muhusiku hurefu (Nemunamato weTahajjud)"
  76,27,"Zvirokwazvo, ava (vasingatendi) vanoda upenyu wepano pasi, uye vanosendeka shure zuva rinorema (iro rinenge rakaoma)"
  76,28,"Tisu takavasika, uye tikavaiita zvigwindiri. Kana tichida, zvirokwazvo tinokwanisa kuunza vamwe vanhu vakafanana navo panzvimbo yavo"
  76,29,"Zvirokwazvo iyi (ndima) iyeuchidzo, saka kune uyo anoda, ngaasarudze nzira yekuna Tenzi vake (Allah)"
  76,30,"Asi hamudi, kunze ivo Allah vada. Zvirokwazvo Allah ndivo muzivi wezvose, muchenjeri"
  76,31,Vachaisa mutsitsi dzavo uyo wevaranda wavanoda. Asi avo vanoita zvakaipa vakavagadzirira dambudzo rinorwadza
  77,1,"(Ndinopika) Ne (mhepo kana ngirozi, kana nhumwa dzaAllah) dzakatumwa imwe mushure meimwe"
  77,2,Uye nemhepo dzinovhuvhuta zvine simba
  77,3,Uye nemhepo inopararidza makore nemvura
  77,4,Uye ne (ndima dzemuQur’aan) dzinosiyanisa (zvakanaka nezvakaipa)
  77,5,Uye ne (ngirozi) dzinounza zvidzikiswa (kunhumwa)
  77,6,Kunobvisa zvose zvimhingamupini kana kuyambira
  77,7,"Zvirokwazvo, zvawakavimbiswa zvichadarika"
  77,8,Apo nyenyedzi dzichadzima chiedza chadzo
  77,9,Uye denga richatsemuka
  77,10,Uye nemakomo paachafuridzwa kure
  77,11,Uye nenhumwa padzichaunganidzwa panguva yakatarwa
  77,12,Zuva ripi (zviratidzo izvi) zvirikunonotserwa
  77,13,Zuva resarudzo (avo veParadhiso kubva kune avo vekuGehena)
  77,14,Uye uchaziva sei kuti zuva resarudzo chii
  77,15,Matambudziko pazuva iri kune avo vanoramba (Zuva Rekutongwa)
  77,16,Hatina here kuparadza avo vange vari kumberi kwenyu
  77,17,Uye tichaita vari mumashure mavo vave vanovatevera
  77,18,Nenzira iyi tinoshanda nevapari vemhosva (vasingatendi nevatadzi)
  77,19,Matambudziko kune avo vanoramba (Zuva Rekutongwa)
  77,20,Hatina kukusikai kubva kumvura inoshorwa
  77,21,Uye tikaigadzika munzvimbo yakachengetedzeka (munhumbu)
  77,22,Kwenguva inozivikanwa (yemwana kuti aberekwe)
  77,23,"Saka takaera, uye tisu nyanzvi dzekuera (zvinhu)"
  77,24,Matambudziko kune avo vanoramba (Zuva Rekutongwa)
  77,25,Hatina here kugadzira pasi senzvimbo yokugara
  77,26,Kune vapenyu nevakafa
  77,27,"Uye tikagadzika imomo makomo akasimba nekureba, uye tikakupai mvura yekunwa inonaka"
  77,28,Matambudziko kune avo vanoramba (Zuva Rekutongwa)
  77,29,"(Zvichanzi kune vasingatendi): “Gundumukai kubva kune izvo zvamairamba!”"
  77,30,“Gundumukai kumumvuri (wemoto weGehena hutsi huchikwidza) muzvikwata zvitatu.”
  77,31,"“Pasina mumvuri, kana kubatsira chimwe chinhu kubva murimi remoto.”"
  77,32,"Zvirokwazvo, iro (Gehena) richakanda zvingaimi seAl-Qasr (zidanda rechitsiga)"
  77,33,Sekunge ingamera dzeruvara rwegoride kana tsapo retambo
  77,34,Matambudziko kune avo vanoramba (Zuva Rekutongwa)
  77,35,Iri ndiro zuva ravasingatauri (padzimwe nguva dzaro)
  77,36,Uye havabvumidzwe kupa zvikonzero
  77,37,Matambudziko kune avo vanoramba (Zuva Rekutongwa)
  77,38,Iri izuva resarudzo (remutongo). Takuunzai imi nevanhu vekutanga pamwechete
  77,39,"Saka kana pane zvamakaronga, shandisirai ini (Allah)"
  77,40,Matambudziko kune avo vanoramba (Zuva Rekutongwa)
  77,41,"Zvirokwazvo, vanotya Allah vachave pakati pemimvuri nezvitubu"
  77,42,Uye nemichero iyo vachada
  77,43,“Idyai nekunwa makasununguka nekuda kwezvamaiita.”
  77,44,"Zvirokwazvo, kudaro tinopa mubairo kuvanhu vezvakanaka"
  77,45,Matambudziko kune avo vanoramba (Zuva Rekutongwa)
  77,46,"(Imi\tvasingatendi)! Idyai\tnekufara (muhupenyu\thwepano pasi) kwechinguva\tchidiki. Zvirokwazvo, muri vaiti vezvakaipa"
  77,47,Matambudziko kune avo vanoramba (Zuva Rekutongwa)
  77,48,"Kana zvikanzi kwavari: “Kotamai (mumunamato)! Havakotami (havaite minamato yavo)"
  77,49,Matambudziko kune avo vanoramba (Zuva Rekutongwa)
  77,50,Saka munhaurwa ipi mushure meiri (Qur’aan) vachatenda
  78,1,Vanobvunzana maererano nei
  78,2,"Maererano nenhaurwa huru (Islaam, Qur’aan iri uye Zuva Rekutongwa)"
  78,3,Pamusoro payo vanopokana
  78,4,"Hongu, vachazviziva"
  78,5,"Hongu, vachazviziva zvekare"
  78,6,Hatina here kusika pasi semubhedha
  78,7,Uye makomo sehoko
  78,8,"Zvakare tikave tinokusikai muri vaviri vaviri (murume nemukadzi, akareba neakapfupika, akanaka neakaipa)"
  78,9,Uye tikava tinokupai hope kuti muve munozorora
  78,10,Uye tikave tinosika usiku sehwidibiro
  78,11,Uye takasika masikati kuti muwane raramo
  78,12,Tikava tinovaka pamusoro penyu matenga manomwe
  78,13,Uye tikasika mwenje unopenya (zuva)
  78,14,Uye tikatumira mvura zhinji kubva kumakore
  78,15,Kuti tive tinoburitsa zvirimwa
  78,16,Uye nemapindu ezvirimwa zvakabatana zvakasvibira
  78,17,"Zvirokwazvo, zuva remutongo inguva yakatarwa"
  78,18,"Zuva iro richaridzwa hwamanda, uye muchauya muri muzvikwata"
  78,19,Uye matenga achavhurwa oita segonhi
  78,20,Uye makomo achabviswa munzvimbo dzawo sezvinonzi aiva madzimudzangara
  78,21,"Zvirokwazvo, Gehena inzvimbo yakaipa"
  78,22,Nzvimbo ichapindwa neavo vanotyora mirawo yaAllah
  78,23,Vachapindamo zvachose
  78,24,"Hapana kana chinwiwa chichange chichitonhorera chavachamwa imomo, kana chinwiwa chipi zvacho"
  78,25,"Kusara kwemvura yakwatiswa, uye nezvose zvakaipa zvinobuda pamuviri"
  78,26,Mubairo unoenderana nezvavaiita
  78,27,"Zvirokwazvo, vakange vasingambotarisiri kuzotongwa"
  78,28,Uye vakaramba zviratidzo zvedu zvachose
  78,29,Uye zvinhu zvose takave tinozvinyora muGwaro
  78,30,Saka chiravirai (magumo emabasa enyu akaipa). Hatisi kuzokuwedzerai kusara kwemarwadzo
  78,31,"Muzvokwadi, kune avo vanotya Allah kuchange kune budiriro (Paradhiso)"
  78,32,Yemapindu nemagirepi
  78,33,Uye mhandara dzezera rimwe dzakanaka
  78,34,Uye komichi izere newaini
  78,35,Havambonzwi imomo nhaurwa dzakaipa kana manyepo
  78,36,"Mubairo kubva kuna Tenzi vako, chipo chakaverengwa (chinoenderana nezvakanaka zvavaiita)"
  78,37,"Kubva kuna Tenzi vematenga nepasi rino uye zvose zviri mukati mavo, vane ngoni zhinji, avo vasingakwanise kutaura navo (kunze kwekuti vavapa mvumo)"
  78,38,"Pazuva iro Ar-Rooh (Gabriel kana imwe ngirozi) nengirozi dzichange dzakamira mumitsara, hapana achataura kana nani kusara kweuyo Allah vavanopa mvumo, uye achitaura zvinhu zvakanaka"
  78,39,"(Pasina kana kusagutsikana) Iri ndiro zuva rechokwadi. Saka, uyo anoda ngaave anotsvaga nzvimbo yakanaka (kana nzira yakanaka ye) kuna Tenzi vake (nekuvateerera pasi rino)"
  78,40,"Zvirokwazvo, takakuyambirai pamusoro pemarwadzo epadyo epazuva iro munhu wese achange achiona zvose zvakatungamidzwa nemaoko ake (zvaaita), uye uyo akange asingatendi achati: “Ndinokungura kuti ndingadai ndaiva ivhu.”"
  79,1,Ndinopika neidzo (ngirozi) dzinotora (upenyu hweuyo asingatendi) nechisimba
  79,2,Neidzo (ngirozi) dzinobvisa zvinyoro-nyoro (mweya wevatendi)
  79,3,Uye neidzo dzinopeperuka
  79,4,Uye neidzo dzinoenderera mberi nekumhanyidzana (ngirozi kana nyenyedzi kana mabhiza)
  79,5,"Uye idzo (ngirozi) dzinoronga kutevedzera mirairo yaTenzi vadzo, (saka zvirokwazvo imi vasingatendi muchabvunzwa)"
  79,6,"Pazuva iro pasi rino nemakomo paachandengendeka zvakanyanya (uye wese achafa, hwamanda yekutanga yaridzwa)"
  79,7,Hwamanda yepiri paichaitevera (uye wese achamutswa)
  79,8,(Mimwe) moyo zuva racho ichandengendeka nekutya
  79,9,Maziso avo achange akatsikitsira
  79,10,"Vanoti: “Tichadzoserwa zvirokwazvo here pahupenyu hwedu hwekare?”"
  79,11,“Mushure mekunge tava mabhonzo akatsetseka?”
  79,12,"Vanoti: “Nokudaro kuchava kudzokera kwekurasikirwa!”"
  79,13,"Asi zvirokwazvo icharidzwa (hwamanda) kamwechete (kuridzwa kechipiri, Surah)"
  79,14,Apo vachazoona vava pamusoro pevhu (vari vapenyu mushure mekufa)
  79,15,Hakuna here kuuya nhaurwa yaMusa kwauri
  79,16,Apo Tenzi vake vakamushevedza munzvimbo inoera yeTuwaa
  79,17,"(Vakati kwaari): “Enda kuna Farawo, zvirokwazvo arikufurikidza mwero (nekusatenda nekuita zvakaipa).”"
  79,18,"Omutaurira kuti: “Ungazvichenure here (kubva mukusatenda)?”"
  79,19,"“Uye kuti ndive ndinokutungamira kuna Tenzi vako, kuti uve unovatya?”"
  79,20,Uye Musa akamuratidza chiratidzo chihombe
  79,21,Asi (Farawo) akaramba uye haana kuteerera
  79,22,"Uye akapfuratira, akashingirira (achipokana naAllah)"
  79,23,Uye akaunganidza (vanhu vake) ndokushevedzera
  79,24,"Achiti: “Ndini Tenzi venyu mukuru”"
  79,25,Saka Allah vakamukweva nemutongo wekubva kwekutanga nekupedzisira kwekuraudzira kwake
  79,26,"Zvirokwazvo, mune izvi mune chidzidzo kune uyo anotya Allah"
  79,27,Munonetsa kusika here kana kuti denga ravakagadzira
  79,28,Vakarisimudza vakarinatsurudza
  79,29,Husiku hwaro vakaufukidza nerima uye vakaburitsamo chiedza
  79,30,Uye mushure mezvo ndokubva vawaridza nyika
  79,31,Vakaunza kubvamo mvura uye nemafuro
  79,32,Uye nemakomo vakaiisa zvakasimba
  79,33,(Kuitira kuti) mubatsirikane nekudya kwenyu nemombe dzenyu
  79,34,Asi kana kukauya dambudziko guru (zuva rekutongwa)
  79,35,Zuva iro munhu acharangarira zvaaiita
  79,36,Uye moto weGehena uchava pachena kune (wese) anoona
  79,37,Kune uyo aityora mitemo yese (nekusatenda nekusateerera Allah)
  79,38,Uye akasarudza upenyu hwepasi pano (achiita zvido zvake)
  79,39,"Zvirokwazvo, Gehena ndiyo nzvimbo (yake) yokugara"
  79,40,"Asi uyo aitya kumira pamberi paTenzi vake, uye akazvidzora kubva kuhuipi hwakasviba uye nemakaro"
  79,41,"Zvirokwazvo, Paradhiso ndokwaachagara"
  79,42,"Vanokubvunza (Muhammad (SAW)) pamusoro penguva yekutongwa, kuti zuva racho ndirinhi"
  79,43,Hauna ruzivo kutaura chimwe chinhu pamusoro payo
  79,44,Kuna Tenzi vako ndiko kune ruzivo rwenguva yacho
  79,45,Zvirokwazvo iwe (Muhammad (SAW)) uri muyambiri kune avo vanoritya
  79,46,Zuva ravachaiona kuchava sekunge havana kugara (pano panyika) kusiya kwemasikati kana mangwanani
  80,1,Akafinyama (Muhammad (SAW)) uye akafuratira
  80,2,Apo bofu (Abdullah Ibn Umm Maktoom) rakanga rauya kwaari (Muhammad (SAW) achiparidzira mukuru kana vakuru vemaQuraish
  80,3,Uye unoziva sei pamwe anogona kuzvichenura (kubva kuzvitadzo)
  80,4,"Kana kuti anogona kuyeuka, uyezve yeuchidzo yobva yamubatsira"
  80,5,Asi kune uyo akapfuma
  80,6,Kwaari unoenda
  80,7,Hapana mhosva kwauri kana iye asina kuzvichenura (kubva mukusatenda)
  80,8,Asi kune uyo anouya kwauri achimhanya (nechido)
  80,9,Uye achitya (Allah)
  80,10,Kwaari ndiko kwausingaendi (kwausingaratidzi hanya)
  80,11,"Kwete! Zvirokwazvo, iri Qur’aan irangaridzo"
  80,12,"Naizvozvo uyo anoda, ngaarangarire"
  80,13,(Zviri) muMagwaro anoremekedzwa (Al-Lauh Al-Mahfoodh)
  80,14,"Akasimudzirwa, akachenurwa"
  80,15,Mumaoko evanyori (ngirozi)
  80,16,Vanoremekedzeka uye vanoteerera
  80,17,Ngaashorwe munhu (asingatendi)! Nekusatenda kwake uku
  80,18,Kubva pai (munhu) vakamusika
  80,19,Kubva kuNutfah (Mvura yemurume nemukadzi) vakamusika uye vakanyatsomugadzira zvakanaka
  80,20,Uye vanomuitira kuti nzira imuitire nyore
  80,21,Uye vanomuita kuti afe uye vomuisa muguva
  80,22,"Uye nekuda kwavo, vachamumutsa (zvekare)"
  80,23,Kwete! Asi (munhu) haana kuita zvaakaudzwa (zvaakakomekedzwa)
  80,24,Naizvozvo rega munhu atarise chikafu chake
  80,25,Tinonaisa mvura yakawanda
  80,26,Uye zvirokwazvo tinopatsanura ivhu
  80,27,Uye tinoita kuti zvirimwa zvikure imomo
  80,28,Nemagirepi uye nechikafu chemombe
  80,29,Nema Orivhi uye miti yemadheti
  80,30,Nemapindu akasvibira akazara nemiti
  80,31,Uye michero nehuswa
  80,32,(Kuti zvive) rubatsiro (chikafu) kwamuri nezvipfuyo zvenyu
  80,33,Uye apo zuva rekutongwa parichauya (Hwamanda paicharidzwa kechipiri)
  80,34,Zuva iri murume achatiza mukoma wake
  80,35,Uye amai nababa vake
  80,36,Uye mukadzi nevana vake
  80,37,Munhu wese zuva iri achange anezvinomukwanira zvichamuita kuti ashaye hanya nevamwe
  80,38,Zvimwe zviso zuva iroro zvichave zvakajeka (vatendi vechokwadi muIslaam)
  80,39,"Zvichiseka, zvichifara nemhaka yenhaurwa yakanaka (yeParadhiso)"
  80,40,Uye zvimwe zviso zuva iroro zvichange zvakasuwa
  80,41,Rima richava kwidibira
  80,42,Ava vanhu vange vasingatendi (kunaAllah) uye vachiita mabasa akaipa
  81,1,"Apo zuva parichaputirwa, uye chiedza charo chobva"
  81,2,Uye apo nyeredzi padzichadonha
  81,3,Uye apo makomo paachaitwa kuti afambe (achibva panzvimbo dzawo)
  81,4,Uye apo ngamera dzakazvitakura dzichasiiwa dzisina muchengeti
  81,5,Uye apo zvikara zvesango pazvichaunganidzwa
  81,6,Uye apo makungwa paachatungidzwa ova moto (kana paachapfachukira)
  81,7,Uye apo mweya ichabatanidzwa nemitumbi yayo (yakanaka neyakanaka uye yakaipa neyakaipa)
  81,8,Uye apo mwanasikana akavigwa ari mupenyu (sezvaiitwa nemaArabhu vasati vave maMuslim) paachabvunzwa
  81,9,Kuti chitadzo chei chaakaurairwa
  81,10,Uye apo mabhuku (emabasa akanaka neakaipa) achavhurwa
  81,11,Uye denga richasiiwa pachena robviswa panzvimbo paro
  81,12,Uye apo Gehena richatungidzwa
  81,13,Uye apo Paradhiso richaiswa pedyo
  81,14,Munhu wese achaziva zvaakatungamidza (mabasa akanaka neakaipa)
  81,15,"Naizvozvo, ndinopika nepasi pose panotaramuka (zvisikwa zvomudenga zvinonyangarika masikati zvobudikira usiku)"
  81,16,Uyezve (ndinopika) nepasi pose panofamba nekukurumidza nekuzvihwandisa
  81,17,Uye neusiku paunoenda
  81,18,Uyezve nemambakwedza pakunochena
  81,19,"Zvirokwazvo, iri (Qur’aan) ishoko (rakaunzwa) nemutumwa anoremekedzeka (Gabriel, kubva kuna Allah richienda kuna Mutumwa Muhammad (SAW)"
  81,20,"Anemasimba kuna (Allah), Tenzi vechigaro (chepamusoro)"
  81,21,Anoteererwa (nengirozi kudenga) uye akavimbika
  81,22,Uye (Imi vanhu) mumwe wenyu (Muhammad (SAW)) haapengi
  81,23,Uye zvirokwazvo iye (Muhammad (SAW)) akamuona (Jibreel – Gabriel (AS)) mudenga makachena (kumabhazuva)
  81,24,Uye iye (Muhammad (SAW)) haavigi ruzivo rwezvakavanzika
  81,25,Uye iri (Qur’aan) harisi shoko raShaitwaan (satani) akarasirirwa
  81,26,Naizvozvo murikunanga kupi
  81,27,"Zvirokwazvo, harisi chimwe chinhu kunze kweyeuchidzo kunyika dzose (Vanhu nemaJinn)"
  81,28,Kune wese kwamuri anoshuvira kutora nzira yakatwasuka
  81,29,"Uye hapana chamunoshuvira kusara kweizvo zvinoshuvirwa naAllah, Tenzi venyika dzose"
  82,1,Apo denga parichapatsanurwa
  82,2,Uye apo nyeredzi padzichadonha dzakamwararira (dzakafararira)
  82,3,Uye apo nzizi padzichazarisa (padzichapfachukira)
  82,4,Uye apo makuva paachashandurwa (achiburitsa zvinenge zviri maari)
  82,5,(Ipapo) Munhu achaziva zvaakaita uye zvaakasiya (zvaasina kuita)
  82,6,"Iwe munhu! Chii chakuita kuti ushaye hanya nezvaTenzi vako, vanoremekedzwa"
  82,7,"Avo vakakusika, vakakupa chimiro chakanaka, uye vakakupa zvakaenzanirana"
  82,8,"Mune ipi nzira yavaida, vakakuisa (vakakuunza) pamwechete"
  82,9,Asi munoramba Ad-Deen (zuva rekutongwa)
  82,10,Uye zvirokwazvo pamusoro penyu (pane ngirozi dzakasarudzwa) kuti dzikutarisei
  82,11,Kiraaman (dzinoremekedzeka) Kaatibeen dzichinyora pasi (mabasa enyu)
  82,12,Dzinoziva zvose zvamunoita
  82,13,"Zvirokwazvo, Al-Abraar (vatendi vatsvene) vachava mumufaro (Paradhiso)"
  82,14,"Uye zvirokwazvo, Al-Fujjaar (vatadzi) vachava mumoto unopisa"
  82,15,"Vachapindamo, voravira marimi awo (moto) anopisa pazuva rekutongwa"
  82,16,Uye imomo havazomboshaikwi
  82,17,Uye chii chichaita kuti uzive chinonzi zuva rekutongwa
  82,18,"Zvakare, chii chichaita kuti uzive zuva rekutongwa"
  82,19,"Zuva iro hapana munhu achange aine simba rekuiitira mumwe chii zvacho, uye mutongo, zuva iroro uchange uina Allah"
  83,1,"Matambudziko kune Al-Mutwaffifoon (avo vanobiridzira, vanopa zvishoma pakuera nepauremu)"
  83,2,Avo kana vachitambira mupimo kubva kuvanhu vanoda mupimo wakazara
  83,3,Uye kana vachipa nemupimo kana huremu kune (vamwe) vanhu vanopa zvishoma
  83,4,Havafungi here kuti vachamutswa
  83,5,Pazuva guru
  83,6,Zuva iro vanhu vachamira pamberi paTenzi vepasi rose
  83,7,"Kwete! Zvirokwazvo, zvinyorwa zvemabasa evatadzi zviri muSijjeen"
  83,8,Uye chii chinoita kuti uzive kuti Sijjeen chii
  83,9,Ibhuku rakanyorwa
  83,10,Matambudziko pazuva iroro kune avo vanoramba
  83,11,Avo vanoramba zuva rekutongwa
  83,12,"Uye hapana anoriramba kusara kweuyo anopfurikidza miganhu (pakusatenda, pakudzvinyirira uye pakusateerera Allah), mutadzi"
  83,13,"Kana ndima dzedu dzichiverengwa kwaari anoti: “Inyaya dzevanhu vakare!”"
  83,14,Kwete! Asi pamoyo yavo pane Raan (chivharo chezvitadzo nemabasa akaipa) avaiwana
  83,15,"Kwete! Zvirokwazvo, (vatadzi) vachavharidzirwa kuona Tenzi vavo pazuva iroro"
  83,16,Uye zvirokwazvo vachava vanopinda murima remoto weGehena
  83,17,"Uye zvichanzi kwavari: “Izvi ndizvo zvamairamba!”"
  83,18,"Kwete! Zvirokwazvo, zvinyorwa zvemabasa evatendi zviri muIlliyyoon"
  83,19,Uye chii chinoita kuti uzive kuti Illiyyoon chii
  83,20,Ibhuku rakanyorwa
  83,21,Iro rinoitirwa uchapupu nevaripedyo (ngirozi)
  83,22,"Zvirokwazvo, vatendi (muIslaam) vachange vari mumafaro (Paradhiso)"
  83,23,"Pazvigaro, vachitarisa (zvinhu zvose)"
  83,24,Uchaona pazviso zvavo kubwinya kwemufaro
  83,25,Vachapihwa waini yakavharwa kuti vamwe
  83,26,Kwekupedzisira kwayo (waini) kuchange kuine munhuwi weMasiki (wakanaka)
  83,27,Ichange (waini) yakasanganiswa neTasneem
  83,28,"Chitubu, chichange chichinwirwa nevari pedyo naAllah"
  83,29,"Zvirokwazvo, (panyika) avo vaiita mabasa akaipa vaiseka avo vaitenda"
  83,30,"Uye, pose pavaipfuura nepavari vaitsonyana"
  83,31,"Uye pose pavaidzokera kuvanhu vavo, vaidzoka vachiseka vachifara"
  83,32,"Uye pavaivaona vaiti: “Zvirokwazvo, ava ndivo vakarasika!”"
  83,33,"Asi avo (vasingatendi, vatadzi) havana kutumwa sevachengetedzi (vevanotenda)"
  83,34,Asi zuva ranhasi (zuva rekutongwa) avo vanotenda vachange vachiseka vasingatendi
  83,35,"Vari pazvigaro, vachitarisa (zvinhu zvose)"
  83,36,Ko vasingatendi havana here kupihwa mubairo wavo (zvizere) wezvavaiita
  84,1,Apo denga parichapatsanurwa
  84,2,Uye roteerera Tenzi waro – uye rinofanira kudaro
  84,3,Uye apo pasi richatambanudzwa
  84,4,Uye parichabuditsa zvose zvaiva mariri rosara risina chinhu
  84,5,Uye roteerera Tenzi waro - uye rinofanira kudaro
  84,6,"Iwe munhu! Zvirokwazvo, uchadzokera kuna Tenzi vako nemabasa ako (akanaka neakaipa) kudzokera kwechokwadi, uye uchasangana nawo (mabasa awaiita)"
  84,7,Kune uyo achapihwa gwaro (bhuku) rake kuruoko rwake rwekurudyi
  84,8,Chokwadi achawana mutongo wakareruka
  84,9,Uye achadzokera kumhuri yake aine mufaro
  84,10,Asi uyo achapihwa gwaro rake nekumashure kwake
  84,11,Achava anodaidzira matambudziko (kuparadzwa kwake)
  84,12,Uye achava anopinda moto unopisa
  84,13,"Zvirokwazvo, aiva pakati pevanhu vake aine mufaro"
  84,14,"Zvirokwazvo, aifunga kuti haazombodzokeri (kwatiri)"
  84,15,"Hongu! Zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vake vaimuona"
  84,16,Saka ndinopika nemadeukazuva (nguva dzerubvunzavaeni)
  84,17,Uye neusiku nezvose zvaunofukidza nerima
  84,18,Uye nemwedzi apo paunenge wakazara
  84,19,Muchava munofamba kubva kune chimwe chikamu kuenda kune chimwe chikamu (paupenyu hwepano pasi nehwuchatevera)
  84,20,Dambudziko ravo nderei rekuti havatendi
  84,21,"Uye kana Qur’aan richiverengwa kwavari, havaisi zviso zvavo pasi"
  84,22,"Asi, avo vasingatendi vanoramba (Muhammad (SAW) nezvose zvaakauya nazvo, Qur’aan iri nekutenda muhumwechete waAllah"
  84,23,Uye Allah vanoziva zvikuru zvavanounganidza (zvakanaka nezvakaipa)
  84,24,Saka vaudze nezvemutongo unorwadza
  84,25,"Kusara kweavo vanotenda vachiita mabasa akanaka, vachava nemugove\rusingazombofa wakasvika kumagumo (Paradhiso)"
  85,1,(Ndinopika) nedenga rakabata nyenyedzi dzihombe
  85,2,Uye nezuva rakatsidzwa (zuva rekutongwa)
  85,3,Uye nechinopupura (zuva rechishanu) uye chinopupurirwa (musi weArafah mumwedzi we Dhul- Hijjah)
  85,4,Vakatukwa (vakarengerwa) vanhu veAl-Ukhdood (Gomba) (Panyaya yemukomana na mambo)
  85,5,(Vanhu) vemoto wakakuchidzirwa nebvavi (mafuta)
  85,6,Apo pavakagara pawaiva uri (moto)
  85,7,Uye vakapupura izvo zvavaiita vakanangana nevatendi (kuvapisa)
  85,8,"Uye vakange vasina mhosva kusara kwekuti vakatenda muna Allah, mukuru wazvose, vane kurumbidzwa kwose"
  85,9,Avo vane humambo hwekudenga nepasi! Uye Allah mupupuri wezvose
  85,10,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanoedza vanhurume nevanhukadzi vanotenda (nokuvarwadzisa nekuvapisa), uye voregerera kukumbira ruregerero (kuna Allah), vachave nemutongo weGehena, uye vachave nomutongo wemoto unopisa"
  85,11,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanotenda nokuita mabasa akanaka, vachave neminda iyo nzizi dzichange dzichierera muzasi mayo (Paradhiso). Uku ndiko kubudirira kukuru"
  85,12,"Zvirokwazvo, (Iwe Muhammad (SAW)) mutongo waTenzi vako wakaomarara"
  85,13,"Zvirokwazvo, ndivo vanotanga (mutongo) uye vanodzokorora (mutongo pazuva rekutongwa). (Kana kuti ndivo vanotanga kusika zvinhu zvese, uye vachadzokorora kusika pazuva rekutongwa)"
  85,14,"Uye ndivo muregereri, vane rudo rwose (kune vatsvene vanotenda muIslaam)"
  85,15,"Muridzi wechigaro chehumambo, murumbidzwi"
  85,16,Muiti wechose chavada
  85,17,Yakasvika here kwauri nyaya yemauto
  85,18,A Farawo uye nemaThamood
  85,19,"Asi, avo vasingatendi vakashingirira mukuramba (Muhammad (SAW) neshoko rake reIslaam"
  85,20,Uye Allah vanovakomberedza kubva kumashure kwavo (Allah vanoziva mabasa avo ese uye vachavapa mubhadharo wavo)
  85,21,Asi iri iQur’aan rinorumbidzwa
  85,22,(Rakanyorwa) Mugwaro rakachengetedzwa (Al-Lauh Al-Mahfoodh)
  86,1,"(Ndinopika) nedenga, neAt-Twaariq (nyenyedzi inouya usiku)"
  86,2,Uye chii chichakuita kuti uzive kuti At-Twaariq chii
  86,3,Inyenyedzi inopenya zvikuru
  86,4,"Munhu wose ane muchengetedzi pamusoro pake (ngirozi dzinoona kumuchengetedza, kunyora mabasa ake akanaka neakaipa).\rnezvemunhu wose"
  86,5,Naizvozvo munhu ngaatarise kuti akasikwa kubva pai
  86,6,Akasikwa kubva mumvura inobuda nesimba
  86,7,Inobva pakati pemuzongoza nembabvu
  86,8,"Zvirokwazvo, (Allah) vane simba rekumudzora (kuhupenyu)"
  86,9,"Zuva\tzvakavanzika\t(mabasa,\tminamato,\tkutsanya,\tnezvimwewo)\tzvichaongororwa (zvichaburitswa)"
  86,10,Naizvozvo achange asina simba kana mubatsiri
  86,11,"(Ndinopika) nedenga (rine makore emvura) rinopa mvura, nguva nenguva"
  86,12,Uye nepasi rinotsemuka (nekukura kwemiti nezvirimwa)
  86,13,"Zvirokwazvo, (Qur’aan) iri ishoko rinopatsanura (chokwadi kubva kumanyepo)"
  86,14,Uye harisi chinhu chedambe
  86,15,"Zvirokwazvo, vari kuronga hurongwa (hwekukuvhiringidza Muhammad (SAW)"
  86,16,Uye ini (wo) ndiri kuronga hurongwa
  86,17,"Naizvozvo chimbononotsa vasingatendi, wovasiya kwekanguva"
  87,1,"Kudza Zita raTenzi vako, vepamusoro-soro"
  87,2,Avo vakasika (zvinhu zvose) vakazvishongedza
  87,3,"Uye avo vakaronga (mafambiro ezvinhu zvese), uye vakatungamira (vakaratidza vanhu nzira yakanaka kubva kune yakaipa, uye vakaratidza mhuka mafuro adzo)"
  87,4,Uye avo vanobuditsa mafuro
  87,5,"Uye vomaita (mafuro) kuti aome, oita ruvara rwakasvibira"
  87,6,"Tichakuita kuti uverenge (Qur’aan), saka (Muhammad (SAW)) hauzombokanganwi"
  87,7,"Kunze kweizvo Allah zvavanoda. Zvirokwazvo, (Allah) vanoziva zviri pachena nezvakavanzika"
  87,8,Uye tichakurerutsira nzira iri nyore (kuita mabasa akanaka)
  87,9,Naizvozvo yeuchidza (vanhu) kana yeuchidzo ichibatsira
  87,10,Rangaridzo ichatambirwa neuyo anotya (Allah)
  87,11,Asi icharambwa nemuipi
  87,12,Uyo achapinda moto mukuru
  87,13,Zvakare imomo haazombofi (kuti azorore) kana kurarama (hupenyu hwakanaka)
  87,14,Zvirokwazvo uyo anozvichenesa (kubva mukusatenda uye otambira Islaam) achava anobudirira
  87,15,"Uye achirangarira zita raTenzi vake, uye achinamata (kashanu pazuva uye achiita minamato isina kukomekedzwa)"
  87,16,Asi munoshuvira upenyu wepano pasi
  87,17,Kunyangwe upenyu uchatevera uri nani uye haugumi
  87,18,"Zvirokwazvo, izvi zviri muMagwaro ekutanga"
  87,19,Magwaro aAbrahamu naMusa
  88,1,Ko mashoko ezuva remukomberedzo (rekutongwa) akasvika kwauri here
  88,2,"Zvimwe zviso pazuva iroro zvichadupukiswa (mumoto, zviso zvevasingatendi)"
  88,3,"Kusevenza (zvakanyanya muhupenyu hwepano pasi nekunamata zvimwe kunze kwaAllah), kunetseka (muhupenyu hwamangwa nekushorwa)"
  88,4,Vachapinda mumoto unopisa
  88,5,Vachapihwa kunwa kubva muchitubu chinokwata (fashaira)
  88,6,Vachange vasina chekudya kusara kwemuti weminzwa une muchetura
  88,7,Usingavagutsi kana kuvadzivirira kubva kunzara
  88,8,(Zvimwe) zviso pazuva iroro zvichange zvichifara
  88,9,Vachifadzwa nemabasa avo (akanaka nekutenda kwavo muIslaam)
  88,10,Mubindu (Paradhiso) repamusoro
  88,11,Uko kwavasinganzwi manyepo
  88,12,Mariri (bindu) muchange muine chitubu chinoerera
  88,13,Mariri (bindu) muchange muine mibhedha yakareba (zvigaro zvakasimudzwa zviri pamusoro)
  88,14,Uye makomichi akarongedzwa
  88,15,Uye mapiro akarongwa mumitsara
  88,16,Uye makapeti epamusoro (ose) akawaridzwa
  88,17,Havatarisi here ngamera masikirwo ayakaitwa
  88,18,Uye denga masimudzirwo arakaitwa
  88,19,Uye makomo kuti akamiswa sei (zvakasimba)
  88,20,Uye pasi kuti rakatambanudzwa sei
  88,21,"Naizvozvo yeuchidza (Muhammad (SAW)), zvirokwazvo uri muyeuchidzi"
  88,22,Hausi muchengetedzi wavo (Hauna masimba pamusoro pavo)
  88,23,Kusara kweuyo anopikisa uye osiya kutenda
  88,24,Uye Allah vachamutonga nemutongo wakakurisisa
  88,25,"Zvirokwazvo, kwatiri ndiko kune kudzokera kwavo"
  88,26,"Uye zvirokwazvo, kwatiri ndiko kune kutongwa kwavo"
  89,1,(Ndinopika) nemambakwedza
  89,2,Neusiku gumi (mazuva gumi ekutanga kwemwedzi weDhul-Hijjah)
  89,3,Uye nezvinhu zvinofambidzana muuviri uye zvakapfunda
  89,4,Neusiku apo paunopfuura
  89,5,Zvirokwazvo mazviri mune humboo kuvanhu vanonzwisisa
  89,6,Hauoni here (Iwe Muhammad (SAW)) kuti Tenzi vako vakaita sei nemaAad
  89,7,VeIram (vaive vakareba) kunge mapango
  89,8,Vasina vamwe vakasikwa saivo panyika
  89,9,"Uye maThamood, avo vaiveza matombo mumupata (vachigadzira dzimba)"
  89,10,Uye (na)Farawo muridzi wehoko (dzaaishandisa kurwadzisa vanhu)
  89,11,Avo vaipfurikidza mwero panyika
  89,12,Uye vachikonzera nyonga nyonga zvakanyanya mairi (nyika)
  89,13,Naizvozvo Tenzi vako vakaisa pavari (vanhu) mitongo yakasiyana siyana yakaoma
  89,14,"Zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vako vanoona"
  89,15,"Kana munhu, Tenzi vake kana vachinge vamuedza nekumupa chiremera nemakomborero, ipapo anobva ati: “Tenzi vangu vandipa chiremera!”"
  89,16,"Asi kana (Allah) vakamuedza nekushomesa (kutambura) raramo yake anoti: “Tenzi vangu vandidzikisira!”"
  89,17,Kwete! Asi hamubati nherera zvakanaka (uye hamudzipi nhaka yadzo yakakwana)
  89,18,Uye hamukurudzirani kupa chikafu kuAl-Miskeen (anoshaya)
  89,19,Uye munodya nhaka nemakaro
  89,20,Uye munoda hupfumi nerudo rwakanyanya
  89,21,Kwete! Apo nyika paichakuiwa kuita huruva
  89,22,Uye Tenzi vako vouya nengirozi dziri mumitsara
  89,23,"Uye Gehena richaunzwa pedyo musi uyu. Pazuva iroro munhu acharangarira, asi kurangarira (kwake) kuchamubatsirei"
  89,24,"Achati: “Matambudziko kwandiri! Dai ndakatungamidza (mabasa akanaka) paupenyu hwangu!”"
  89,25,Saka pazuva iri hapana achatonga sematongero avachaita (Allah)
  89,26,Uye hapana achasunga (vasingatendi nevaiti vemabasa akashata) semasungiro avo (Allah)
  89,27,"(Zvichanzi kuvatsvene): “Iwe mweya uri pazororo"
  89,28,"Dzoka kunaTenzi vako, uchifadzwa (navo) uye vachifadzwa newe"
  89,29,"Naizvozvo, pinda pakati pevaranda vangu (vanoremekedzeka)"
  89,30,Uye pinda muParadhiso rangu!”
  90,1,Ndinopika neguta iri (Makkah)
  90,2,Uyezve hauna mhosva neguta iri (Wakasununguka muGuta iri)
  90,3,Uyezve nemubereki (Adam (AS)) nezvaakabereka (vana vake)
  90,4,"Zvirokwazvo, tave tinosika munhu mumatambudziko"
  90,5,Anofunga here kuti hapana anomukurira
  90,6,"Anoti (mukuzvikudza): “Ndave ndinorasa hupfumi hwakawanda!”"
  90,7,Anofunga here kuti hapana anomuona
  90,8,Hatina here kumugadzirira maziso maviri
  90,9,Uye rurimi nemiromo (wezasi newepamusoro)
  90,10,Uye tikamuratidza nzira mbiri (yakanaka neyakaipa)
  90,11,Asi haana kumboedza kupfuura nenzira yakatevenuka (yakareruka)
  90,12,Uye chii chichakuita kuti uzive kuti nzira yakatevenuka chii
  90,13,Kusunungura muranda (musungwa)
  90,14,Kana kupa chikafu muzuva renzara
  90,15,Kunherera yepedyo
  90,16,Kana kune murombo akarara muvhu (nokuda kweurombo)
  90,17,"Uye akazove umwe weavo vanotenda (muIslaam), uye vakakomekedzana kutsungirira, uye vakakomekedzana kunzwira tsitsi"
  90,18,Ndivo avo veruoko rwerudyi (vanhu veParadhiso)
  90,19,"Asi avo vasina kutenda muzviratidzo zvedu, ndeavo veruoko rweruboshwe (vanhu vekumoto)"
  90,20,Vachave vanovharirwa nemoto (Moto uchavakomberedza kubva kumativi ese)
  91,1,(Ndinopika) nezuva nekubwinya kwaro
  91,2,Nemwedzi paunoritevera (zuva)
  91,3,(Ndinopika) nemasikati paanoratidza (kubwinya kwezuva)
  91,4,Neusiku paunorivhara (zuva)
  91,5,Nedenga neavo vakarivaka
  91,6,(Ndinopika) nepasi neavo vakari tambanudza
  91,7,Nemoyo (munhu) neavo vakamugadzira mune zvakanaka
  91,8,Uye vakamuratidza zvakaipa kwaari nezvakanaka kwaari
  91,9,"Zvirokwazvo, anobudirira uyo anozvichenesa (anotevedzera Islaam)"
  91,10,Uye zvirokwazvo anokundikana uyo anozvikanganisira pachake (anoramba Islaam)
  91,11,"(Vanhu) veThamud vakaramba kuburikidza nekudarikidza kwavo mitemo (vairamba chitendero chechokwadi, Islaam, uye vachiita mabasa akaipa)"
  91,12,Apo muipi wavo akaenda mberi (kuti auraye ngamera)
  91,13,"Asi mutumwa waAllah (Swaalih (AS)) akati kwavari: “Iyi ingamera yaAllah (musaikuvadze), uye (musairambidze) kunwa kwayo!”"
  91,14,"Naizvozvo vakamuramba uye vakaiuraya. Naizvozvo Tenzi vavo vakavaparadza nekuda kwechitadzo chavo, uye vakavaenzanisa mukuparadzwa (vanhu vose, vapfumi, nevarombo, vane simba nevasina simba)"
  91,15,Uye ivo (Allah) havana kutya zvichaitika mumashure mazvo
  92,1,(Ndinopika) neusiku apo paunosvika
  92,2,Nemasikati apo paanobwinya
  92,3,Neavo vakasika chirume nechikadzi
  92,4,"Zvirokwazvo, simba nemabasa enyu akasiyana siyana"
  92,5,Kune uyo anopa (zvipo) uye achitya Allah
  92,6,Uye achitenda mune zvakanaka (Laa ilaaha illallaah – Hakuna ane kodzero yokunamatwa kunze kwaAllah; kana kuti mubairo kubva kuna Allah)
  92,7,Tichava tinomurerutsira nzira yakanaka
  92,8,"Asi uyo asingapi (anonyima), uye achifunga kuti mupfumi (haana chaanoda kubva kune umwe munhu)"
  92,9,"Uye achiramba Al-Husna (zvakanaka: Laa ilaaha illallaah, kana kuti mubairo kubva kunaAllah)"
  92,10,Tichava tinomurerutsira nzira yakaipa
  92,11,Uye hupfumi hwake huchamubatsira chii paachawira pasi (mumatambudziko)
  92,12,"Zvirokwazvo, kwatiri ndiko kune nhungamiro"
  92,13,Uye zvirokwazvo kwatiri ndiko kune magumo nemavambo (upenyu hwepano pasi neuchatevera)
  92,14,Naizvozvo ndinokuyambirai nezvemoto unopisa (Gehena)
  92,15,Hapana achaupinda kunze kweavo vachange vasina mufaro
  92,16,Avo vanoramba vofuratira
  92,17,"Uye Al-Muttaqoon (vatsvene, vanhu vanotya Allah) vachaiswa kure nawo (moto weGehena)"
  92,18,Uye anopa hupfumi hwake kuti azvichenese
  92,19,Uye uyo asiri kuripa chakanaka chaakaitirwa naani zvake
  92,20,Kunze kwekuti achitsvaga chiso (kufadza) chaTenzi vake vepamusoro-soro
  92,21,"Uye zvirokwazvo mushure maizvozvo, achava anofara (paachapinda Paradhiso)"
  93,1,(Ndinopika) nenguva yemangwanani (zuva richangobuda)
  93,2,(Ndinopika) nenguva yemanheru apo painoita rima
  93,3,Tenzi vako (Iwe Muhammad (SAW)) havana kukurasirira kana kukuvenga
  93,4,Uye zvirokwazvo hupenyu hwemangwana hwakanaka kwauri kukunda hupenyu hwenyika ino
  93,5,"Uye zvirokwazvo, Tenzi vako vachakupa (zvakanaka) naizvozvo ugofara"
  93,6,Havana here kukuwana (Muhammad (SAW)) uri nherera ndokubva vakuchengetedza
  93,7,Uye vakakuwana wakarasika ndokubva vakutungamirira
  93,8,Uye vakakuwana uri murombo ndokubva vakuita mupfumi (mugutsikani nezvaunazvo)
  93,9,"Naizvozvo, usachengete nherera nehudzvanyiriri"
  93,10,Uye usadzinge uyo anokumbira (mupe)
  93,11,"Uyezve taura pamusoro pemakomborero aTenzi vako (awakapiwa, Huporofita nemamwewo)"
  94,1,Hatina here kukuvhura chipfuva chako (Iwe Muhammad (SAW)
  94,2,Uye tikabvisa kubva kwauri misengwa yako
  94,3,Iyo yairemera musana wako (yaidzikisira chimiro chako)
  94,4,Uye tikasimudzira kuzivikanwa kwako
  94,5,"Zvirokwazvo, pane matambudziko pane kugarika"
  94,6,"Zvirokwazvo, pane matambudziko pane kugarika"
  94,7,"Naizvozvo kana wapedza (basa rako), zvipire (kuna Allah uchivanamata)"
  94,8,Uye kuna Tenzi vako zvipire nekuvimba kwako kwose
  95,1,"(Ndinopika) nemuonde, uye nemu orivhi"
  95,2,Negomo reSinai
  95,3,Neguta iri (Makkah) rakachengetedzeka
  95,4,"Zvirokwazvo, takasika munhu ane chimiro chakanaka"
  95,5,Ndokubva tamudzikisira kusvika pakupedzisira
  95,6,Kusara kweavo vanotenda (muIslaam) uye vachiita mabasa akanaka. Vachawana mubairo usingaperi (Paradhiso)
  95,7,Nokudaro chii chinoita (iwe asingatendi) kuti urambe zuva rekutongwa
  95,8,Havasi here Allah mutongi vanoziva pamusoro pevatongi vose
  96,1,Verenga! Muzita raTenzi vako avo vakasika (zvinhu zvese)
  96,2,Vakasika munhu kubva mubumbu reropa
  96,3,Verenga! Uye Tenzi vako ndivo mukomboreri mukuru
  96,4,Avo vakadzidzisa (kunyora) nechinyoreso
  96,5,Vakadzidzisa munhu izvo zvaakanga asingazivi
  96,6,"Asi, zvirokwazvo, munhu anodarika mirairo"
  96,7,Nokuda kwekuti anozviona sekunge akapfuma
  96,8,"Zvirokazvo, kuna Tenzi vako ndiko kune kudzokera"
  96,9,Wakamuona here (Muhammad (SAW)) uyo anodzivirira (anorambidza - Abu Jahl)
  96,10,Muranda (Muhammad (SAW)) kana achinamata
  96,11,Wakamboona here kana iye (Muhammad (SAW)) ari kutungamirwa (naAllah)
  96,12,Kana ari kukomekedza kutya (Allah)
  96,13,Wakamboona here kana iye (Abu Jahl) achiramba chokwadi (Qur’aan) uye achifuratira
  96,14,Haazivi here kuti Allah vanoona (zvose)
  96,15,"Asi, kana asina kusiya (Abu Jahl), tichamubata nebvudzi rekumberi"
  96,16,Bvudzi repamberi (pemusoro) rinonyepa nekukanganisa
  96,17,Naizvozvo chimusiyai adaidze dare rake (revabetseri)
  96,18,Isu tichadaidza vachengeti veGehena (kuti vaone chekuita naye)
  96,19,Kwete! (Muhammad (SAW)) usamuteerera (Abu Jahl). Pfugama uye uswedere pedyo (naAllah)
  97,1,"Zvirokwazvo, takaridzikisa (Qur’an iri) muusiku hwechisungo"
  97,2,Uye chii chichaita kuti uzive kuti usiku hwechisungo chii
  97,3,"Usiku hwechisungo huri nani kukunda churu chemwedzi (kunamata Allah mauri kuri nani kupfuura kunamata churu chemwedzi (makore makumi masere nematatu, nemwedzi mina)"
  97,4,Mauri munodzika ngirozi nemweya mutsvene (Gabriel) nemvumo yaTenzi vavo nezvisungo zvose
  97,5,(Usiku hwese) Pane runyararo (uye zvakanaka kubva kuna Allah zvichienda kuvaranda vavo vanotenda) kusvikira nguva yemambakwedza
  98,1,"Avo vasingatendi kubva kuvanhu veBhuku (maJudha nemaKristu) nemaMushrikoon (avo vanonamata zvidori, kana kuti Allah vachivasanganisa nezvimwe zvinhu), vakanga vasingazosiyi (kusatenda) kusvikira humboo huri pachena hwauya kwavari"
  98,2,"Mutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)) kubva kuna Allah, achiverenga bhuku rakachenurwa (Qur’aan rakachenurwa kubva kumanyepo)"
  98,3,Mariri mune mitemo yakatwasuka (kubva kuna Allah)
  98,4,Uye vanhu veBhuku (maJudha nemaKristu) havana kusiyana asi mushure mokunge humboo hwakajeka hwauya kwavari
  98,5,"Uye havana kukomekedzwa asi kunamata Allah, uye kunamata Allah chete voga, uye kuita Swalaah (Munamato), uye kupa Zvipo (Zakaah), uye ichi ndicho chitendero chakatwasuka"
  98,6,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vasingatendi kubva muvanhu veBhuku (maJudha nemaKristu) nemaMushrikoon (avo vanonamata zvidori, kana kuti Allah vachivasanganisa nezvimwe zvinhu) vachange vari mumoto weGehena vachigara imomo. Vanhu vakadaro ndivo zvisikwa zvakashata"
  98,7,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanotenda (muIslaam), uye vachiita mabasa akanaka, vanhu vakadaro ndivo zvisikwa zvakanaka"
  98,8,"Mubairo wavo unaTenzi vavo, Paradhiso rine nzizi dzinoerera pasi paro.Vachagara imomo zvachose. Allah vachafadzwa navo uye ivo vachafadzwa navo (Allah). Izvi ndezve uyo anotya Tenzi vake"
  99,1,Kana nyika yodengenyetswa nekudengenyeka kwayo
  99,2,Uye kana nyika yoburitsa misengwa yayo (zvayakaviga)
  99,3,"Uye munhu achati: “Chii chiri kunetsa pairi?”"
  99,4,Nezuva iroro ichataura mashoko ayo (zvaiitika pamusoro payo zvakanaka nezvakaipa)
  99,5,Nokuda kwekuti Tenzi vako vanenge vaiudza izvozvo
  99,6,Nezuva iroro vanhu vachaenda muzvikwata kuitira kuti vagotaridzwa mabasa avo
  99,7,Naizvozvo uyo anenge aita chakanaka chakafanana nehuremu hwekasvosve kamwechete achachiona
  99,8,Uye uyo anenge aita chakaipa chakafanana nehuremu hwekasvosve kamwechete achachiona
  100,1,Ndinopika nemabhiza anomhanya achifemereka
  100,2,Achiburitsa zvimvari zvemoto (nemakumbo awo)
  100,3,Uye achimhanyira kunorwa mambakwedza
  100,4,Uye achipfumbura huruva nawo
  100,5,Uye achipinda nawo mukati (memuvengi)
  100,6,"Zvirokwazvo, munhu haatendi Tenzi vake"
  100,7,Uye zvirokwazvo iye ichapupu kune izvozvo (nemabasa ake)
  100,8,Uye zvirokwazvo anosimbirira mukuda zvakanaka (hupfumi)
  100,9,Haazivi here kuti apo zviri mumakuva zvichaburitswa
  100,10,Uye izvo zviri muzvipfuva pazvichaitwa kuti zvizivikanwe
  100,11,"Zvirokwazvo, nezuva iroro Tenzi vavo vachange vachinyatsoziva nezvavo (mabasa avo uye vovapa mubairo wavo)"
  101,1,Nguva yokuparadzwa (zuva rokumutswa)
  101,2,Chii chinonzi nguva yokuparadzwa
  101,3,Uye chii chichakuita kuti uzive kuti nguva yokuparadzwa chii
  101,4,Izuva iro vachange vakaita sokunge shave-shave dzakapararira
  101,5,Uye makomo achaita sokunge shinda (wuru) yakaparadzirwa
  101,6,Asi kune uyo huremu hwemabasa ake (akanaka) huchange huchirema
  101,7,Achagara hupenyu hunofadza (kuJannah)
  101,8,Asi kune uyo huremu hwemabasa ake achange asingaremi
  101,9,"Achawana imba yake iri Haawiya (gomba, Gehena)"
  101,10,Uye chii chichakuita kuti uzive kuti chii
  101,11,Imoto unovirima (viriri remoto)
  102,1,Kuunganidza (zvenyika) kunokuitai kuti murivare
  102,2,Kusvikira mashanyira makuva (mafa)
  102,3,Kwete! Muchasvika pakuziva
  102,4,Zvakare kwete! Muchasvika pakuziva
  102,5,"Kwete! Dai maiziva noruzivo rwechokwadi (magumo ekuunganidza, maisadaro)"
  102,6,"Zvirokwazvo, muchaona viriri remoto (weGehena)"
  102,7,"Uye zvakare, muchauona (iwo moto) nemeso akajeka"
  102,8,Uye nezuva iroro zvirokwazvo muchabvunzwa nezvemafaro (zvamaiita panyika)
  103,1,(Ndinopika) nenguva
  103,2,Zvirokwazvo munhu akarasika
  103,3,"Kusara kweavo vanotenda (muhumwechete hwaAllah), uye vachiita mabasa akanaka, uye vachikurudzirana chokwadi (kuita mabasa akanaka akatarwa naAllah nekusiya akaipa), uye vachikurudzirana kuva netariro (kutsungirira kubva kumatambudziko anovawana munzira yaAllah)"
  104,1,Matambudziko kune wese anonyepera vamwe uye anonyeya
  104,2,Uyo akaunganidza hupfumi uye akahuverenga
  104,3,Anofunga kuti hupfumi hwake huchamuita kuti agare nokusingaperi
  104,4,Kwete! Achakandwa mumoto unoparadza
  104,5,Uye chii chichaita kuti uzive kuiti moto unoparadza chii
  104,6,Moto waAllah wakatungidzwa
  104,7,Uyo unopisa pamusoro pemoyo
  104,8,"Zvirokwazvo, uchavharwa pamusoro pavo"
  104,9,Mumitsigo yakatambanudzwa (kuti vacharangwa mumoto une mitsigo)
  105,1,Hauna kuona (Iwe Muhammad (SAW)) here zvakaitwa naTenzi vako kuvaridzi venzou? (Mauto ane nzou akabva kuYemen achitungamirirwa na Abrahah Al-Ashram vane chinangwa chekuparadza Ka’bah kuMakkah)
  105,2,Havana kuita here kuti hurongwa hwavo hurasike (hushaye basa)
  105,3,Uye vakavatumira shiri muzvikwata
  105,4,Dzichivatema nematombo akaumbirwa (Sijjeel)
  105,5,Uye vakavaita sokunge munda (usina chunhu) wakadyiwa (nemombe)
  106,1,(Mufaro mukuru kubva kuna Allah) nechengetedzo kumaQuraish
  106,2,Kuchengetedzwa kwavo pakufamba (vachienda kunotengesa) munguva yechando nenguva yekupisa
  106,3,"Naizvozvo, ngavanamate (Allah) Tenzi ve imba iyi (Ka’bah ku Makkah)"
  106,4,"Avo vanovapa chikafu kubva munzara, uye vanovachengetedza kubva mukutya"
  107,1,Wakambomuona here uyo anoramba zuva rekutongwa (rekuwana mubairo)
  107,2,Ndeuyo anobata nherera zvakashata (nehasha)
  107,3,Uye haakurudziri kupa anoshaya chikafu
  107,4,"Naizvozvo, matambudziko kune vanamati (vanyengedzi)"
  107,5,Avo vasingakoshesi (vano nonoka kuita) Swalaah (munamato kubva kunguva yayo yakatarwa)
  107,6,Avo vanoita mabasa akanaka kuti vaonekwe
  107,7,"Uye vanonyima Al-Maa’uoon (rubatsiro diki nemunyu, shuga, mvura, nezvimwe zvakadaro)"
  108,1,"Zvirokwazvo, takakupa (Muhammad (SAW)) Al-Kauthar (Rwizi rwekuParadhiso)"
  108,2,Naizvozvo namata Tenzi vako uye vopira (kwavari chete)
  108,3,"Zvirokwazvo, uyo anokuvenga (Iwe Muhammad (SAW)) ndiye achaparadzwa"
  109,1,"Iti (Iwe Muhammad (SAW)): “Imi vasingatendi (muna Allah, muhumwechete wavo, ngirozi dzavo, Mabhuku avo, vatumwa vavo, muzuva rekutongwa, uye kuti zvose zvinoitika nokuda kwavo (Allah)"
  109,2,Ini handinamati izvo zvamunonamata
  109,3,Uye imi hamunamati zvandinonamata
  109,4,Uye ini handizombonamati zvamunonamata
  109,5,Uye imi hamuzombonamati izvo zvandinonamata
  109,6,"Kwamuri mune chitendero chenyu, uye ini kwandiri ndine chitendero changu.”"
  110,1,Kana rubatsiro rwaAllah rwauya nekukunda
  110,2,Uye kana ukaona vanhu vachipinda vakawanda muchitendero chaAllah (Islaam)
  110,3,"Nokudaro kudza kurumbidzwa kwaTenzi vako, uye vakumbire ruregerero.Zvirokwazvo ndivo vanoregerera"
  111,1,Ngaaparadzwe maoko aAbu Lahab uye ngaaparadzwe
  111,2,Upfumi hwake nevana vake hazvisi kana kuzomubetsera
  111,3,Achapiswa mumoto uye une viriri rinobvira
  111,4,Uye mukadzi wake achange akatakura huni
  111,5,Muhuro make muchange muine tambo yemadheti yakakoswa yegavi nemurara
  112,1,"Iti (Iwe Muhammad (SAW)): “NdiAllah, Vamwechete"
  112,2,Allah vanodiwa nezvisikwa zvose (asi ivo hapana chavanoda)
  112,3,"Havabereki vana, kuti ivo havana kuberekwa"
  112,4,Hakuna mumwe akafanana navo kana kuti kuenzaniswa navo.”
  113,1,"Iti: “Ndinotsvaga chengetedzo muna (Allah), Tenzi vekubuda kwezuva (mangwanani)"
  113,2,Kubva kune zvakaipa zvavakasika
  113,3,Uye kubva kune zvakaipa zverima (usiku kana hwauya nerima)
  113,4,Uye kubva mune zvakaipa zveavo vanoita huroi kana vachifuridza chishwe (funda)
  113,5,Uye kubva kune zvakaipa zveuyo ane shanje kana achiita shanje.”
  114,1,"Iti: “Ndinotsvaga kuchengetedzwa na(Allah), Tenzi wevanhu"
  114,2,Mambo wevanhu
  114,3,Mwari wevanhu
  114,4,"Kubva kuhuipi hwemuzevezeri (Satani anozevezera mumoyo yevanhu), uye obva (kubva mukuzevezera kwake mumoyo wemunhu mushure mokunge afunga Allah)"
  114,5,Uyo anozevezera muzvipfuva zvevanhu
  114,6,Kubva kumaJinn (Zvisikwa zvakasikwa nemoto) nevanhu.”